\id JHN - Uare
\h Ioane
\toc3 Ioa
\toc2 Ioane
\toc1 Iesu Keriso Hari Manoḡa Ioaneꞌa Mirihiro
\mt1 Ioane
\mt2 Iesu Keriso Hari Manoḡa Ioaneꞌa Mirihiro
\imt1 Ihore Ḡoeꞌa
\ip Buka ꞌahiꞌe Ioaneꞌa mirihiro. Aniꞌe Iesu tahiꞌa gaubanana aheu fare boꞌaḡano tahiꞌa ꞌahoga, ebu ani aneꞌa bare Iesuꞌa zamare borofiroteꞌe tahiꞌaḡa rae huniro. Aniꞌe haba niduꞌa azaḡa veize Iesu hariḡa manoḡa mirihiro. Buka ꞌahiꞌe Iesu hari mirihiroteꞌe bukaḡa ꞌahogaꞌahoga teite mene tiba, rehano ufeta riḡa. Ani Iesuꞌe Badiꞌa Ubuga rae fureniro zu Vine Zaḡoḡa moneo ḡoeriro. Aniꞌe vaze niduꞌa Iesuꞌe Keriso rae mae ḡihinoga veize ebu ḡabone hugano radoga veize buka ꞌahi mirihiro. Eꞌanoꞌo Ioaneꞌe Iesuꞌa haḡainuteꞌe gauḡa moneo mene ufeta mirihiro, rehano Iesuꞌa reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa moneo ufeta mirihiro.
\c 1
\s1 Ḡoereꞌa Vazeo Reiro
\p 
\v 1 Ḡadaheḡano Ḡoere rae huneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa radiunu. Ḡoere aꞌe Badiꞌa teite radiunu ebu Ḡoere eꞌe Badiꞌa.
\v 2 Aniꞌe ꞌizema raha zu adure ꞌadi haḡaogano Badiꞌa teite radiunu.
\v 3 Badiꞌaꞌa anionoꞌo ḡau niduꞌa haḡairo. Anionoꞌo mene haḡairoteꞌe ḡauḡa ꞌahogaꞌe oꞌoꞌa.
\v 4 Ani zamaḡano ḡaboneḡeta. Ḡabone eꞌeꞌa vaze agazeꞌeteꞌe agaḡa.
\v 5 Agaḡaꞌe uzabo zamaḡano agaruꞌohe, u uzaboꞌe agaḡa vinoga mene idararo.
\p 
\v 6 Badiꞌaꞌa vaze ꞌahoga tuḡuniro. Ani niꞌe Ioane.
\v 7 Aniꞌe agaḡa eꞌe moneo vaze ihozifine ebu ze ani ḡoere egadu agaḡa mazao fifine ariro.
\v 8 Ioaneꞌe mene eꞌe agaḡa, rehano agaḡa eꞌe moneo ihozoga veize ariro.
\v 9 Agaḡaꞌe raha ꞌada ariro. Aniꞌe agaḡa huga ebu vaze niduꞌa agaziro.
\p 
\v 10 Aniꞌe raha ꞌahao radiro ebu raha ꞌadiꞌe ani mazaonoꞌo haḡairo. Rehano raha azaḡaniꞌa ani mene ederiro.
\v 11 Aniꞌe ane haba ariro, rehano ani haba azaḡaniꞌa mene mae ḡihiniro.
\v 12 U iniuꞌa ani mae ḡihinadu ani mazao fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe Badiꞌa ubugaubuga reiteꞌe gigiꞌaḡa ziniro.
\v 13 Ze Badiꞌa ubugaubuga raꞌetaꞌaꞌe mene vouḡaze ruonoꞌo, ga mene vaze uraonoꞌo, ga mene vazeꞌa toganiroteꞌe uꞌano, rehano Badiꞌa urao zeꞌe ane ubugaubuga rae reiro.
\p 
\v 14 Ḡoereꞌe vazeo reiro ebu emeḡe boꞌaḡano radiro. Eme aniꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune rae ederiro. Aniꞌe Badiꞌa Ubuga Tibuhuga, ḡihiꞌa hune rae reiro. Aniꞌe vaze zamare borofiro zu ḡoere huga reiro.
\p 
\v 15 Ioaneꞌa ani moneo rae fureneꞌenaꞌa, ḡihau ḡoeriro, “E ibite ꞌahige rae reiro, 'Eḡe ḡaruna ariteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe vitihoga ḡihiꞌaḡa, mazaḡa e ꞌizema fureranogano aniꞌe amahi radiro.' Eḡeꞌa ꞌouge ziroteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ꞌadi eꞌe.”
\v 16 Aniꞌe eme zamare borofeꞌe ꞌahine, emeḡe niduꞌa manohuga rifiꞌohe, ebu emeꞌa barebare manohuga hideꞌohe.
\v 17 Badiꞌa goro ḡoeꞌaꞌe Moseonoꞌo rifiro, u Badiꞌaꞌa Iesu Keriso uꞌano, emeḡe mazao manoḡa fureniro zu ḡoere huga ihofiro.
\v 18 Badiꞌaꞌe vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa mene horoniro. Rehano Ubuga tibuhuga, Moga uhiḡano radiuꞌeteꞌeꞌa Badiꞌa moneo vaze ihoziro. Aniꞌe Badiꞌa.
\s1 Ioaneꞌe Mene Keriso
\r (Mataio 3:1-12; Mareko 1:2-8; Luka 3:15-17)
\p 
\v 19 Iuda azaḡa boroboroꞌa dibuꞌo azaḡa zu Levi urabo azaḡa Ierusalemaonoꞌo Ioane vaḡe tuḡuziro. Ebu zeḡeꞌa Ioane ḡadiniro, “Ḡaꞌe iniu?” ꞌOugadu Ioaneꞌa ꞌahige rae fureniro.
\v 20 Aniꞌe ḡau ꞌahoga zu mene ꞌuꞌuru ḡoeriro ebu huga daꞌo deheru rae fureniro, “Eꞌe mene Keriso.”\f + \fr 1:20 \fqa Mesia \f*
\v 21 Ebu zeḡeꞌa ḡadiniro, “Tena ḡa iniu? Ḡa Eliahe?” Aniꞌa naenaeziro, “E mene.” Ze bare ḡadiniro, “Peroveta vazeḡa boro ꞌahoganiꞌa ariꞌuma rae ibite rae fureniro. Ḡaꞌe peroveta vazeḡa eꞌehe?” Aniꞌa naenaeziro, “Mene.”
\v 22 Ḡonagano zeḡeꞌa niro, “Ḡaꞌe iniu? Ihofoꞌi, ꞌougine eme baradu emeḡe tuḡufateꞌe azaḡa mazao ḡaꞌe iniu rae ziꞌuma. Ḡa ḡae bare moneo nouge rae raꞌohe?”
\v 23 Ioaneꞌa peroveta vazeḡa Isaiaꞌa reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa hina naenaeziro,
\q1 “Eꞌe haba bohaꞌano huauꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa, raenaꞌa,
\q1 'Zuhiꞌa Boro veize ibi mae dudunoꞌi.'”\x + \xo 1:23 \xt Isaia 40:3\x*
\p 
\v 24 Ioane ḡadiniroteꞌe azaḡa boꞌaḡano nuꞌe Farisea azaḡaniꞌa tuḡuziroteꞌe azaḡa.
\v 25 Zeꞌa Ioane ḡadiniro, “Ḡaꞌe mene Keriso, mene Elia zu mene peroveta vazeḡa eꞌe reine, nougadu vaze babatisoziꞌohe?”
\v 26 Ioaneꞌa naenaeziro, “Eꞌe vu hina babatisoziꞌohe. Rehano zae boꞌaḡano zaeꞌa mene edereꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa edauꞌohe.
\v 27 Aniꞌe eḡe ḡaruna areꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa zu eḡe vitihoga. Eḡe'a ani tamaka miniḡa fuhiꞌeꞌeteꞌe tuḡureḡa vazeḡa rae rouga zuni mene idaḡa.”
\v 28 ꞌAhi niduꞌa Ioridana vuḡa moneafa Betania habaꞌano fureraro. Deꞌea Ioaneꞌa babatisozinu.
\s1 Badiꞌa Mamoe Ubuga
\p 
\v 29 Irarirotene, Ioaneꞌe Iesuꞌa ani vaḡe ariroteꞌe horonadu reiro, “Badiꞌa Mamoe Ubuga ḡianoꞌi! Aniꞌe raha ꞌada haḡai sauꞌa niduꞌa odohe onameꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa.
\v 30 Ibite e ani moneo ꞌahige rae reiro, 'Eḡe ḡaruna ariteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe vitihoga ḡihiꞌaḡa, mazaḡa e ꞌizema fureranogano aniꞌe amahi radiunu.'
\v 31 E aniꞌe mene ederiro. Rehano Isaraela azaḡaniꞌa ani ederifine, e aradu vu hina babatisoziꞌohe.”
\p 
\v 32 Ebu Ioaneꞌa bare rae fureniro, “E Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa Tubugo niniḡa teige adureonoꞌo ovadu ani rana kame radiuꞌeteꞌe horoniro.
\v 33 E aniꞌe mene ederiro. Rehano e vu hina babatisozoga veize tuḡuhiroteꞌe Badiꞌaḡaniꞌa ꞌahige rae ihohiro, 'Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa adureonoꞌo ovadu vaze ꞌahoga rana kame radoga horonoꞌidene, aniꞌe Vine Zaḡoḡa hina babatisoziteꞌe vazeḡa rae ederoꞌi.'
\v 34 E hube hune ꞌouge horonadu aniꞌe Badiꞌa Ubuga rae fureneꞌohe.”
\s1 Iesu Tahiꞌa Ibiꞌa
\p 
\v 35 Irarirotene, Ioaneꞌe ane tahiꞌa aheu teite eꞌe habaꞌano bare edau radiunu.
\v 36 Ebu Iesuꞌa eꞌea vitau onamoga horonirotene, aniꞌa reiro, “Badiꞌa Mamoe Ubuga ḡianoꞌi!”
\v 37 Ioane tahiꞌa aheuꞌa ani ḡoere egadu Iesu hegotiro.
\v 38 Ebu Iesuꞌa tehadu ze ani hegoteꞌeteꞌe horozadu ziro, “Za nagini urateꞌohe?” Zeḡeꞌa naenaeniro, “Rabi, ḡa nouma radiuꞌohe?” (Rabi hugaꞌe Ihore Vazeḡa.)
\v 39 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Eḡe teite onamine, horoniꞌuma.” Ebu ze onamadu Iesuꞌa radiuꞌeteꞌe habaꞌa horoniro, ebu eꞌe mada niduga eꞌea ane teite radiro. Aꞌe ḡorava mone mada ḡazaḡa reiro. \fig Ioaneꞌa Iesu moneo rae fureniro|src="WA03813b.tif" size="col" ref="1:35-36"\fig*
\p 
\v 40 Ioane ḡoere egadu Iesu hegotiroteꞌe vazeḡa aheu boꞌaḡano ꞌahogaꞌe Anderea. Aniꞌe Simona Petero negoḡa.
\v 41 Ani ibite negoḡa Simona vaḡe onamadu niro, “Eme Mesia horoneha.” (Mesia ḡoere ꞌahogaꞌe Keriso.)
\v 42 Ebu Andereaꞌa Simona Iesu vaḡe zamahu onamiro. Iesuꞌa ani ḡianadu niro, “Ḡaꞌe Ioane ubuga, Simona. Rehano Kefa rae huḡadiꞌuma.” (Kefa, ni ꞌahogaꞌe Petero.\f + \fr 1:42 \ft Eꞌe hugaꞌe Vatava. \f*)
\s1 Filipi zu Natanaela Huziro
\p 
\v 43 Irarirotene, Iesuꞌe Galilea habaꞌa onamihi reiro. Ani ꞌizema onamogano Filipi vaḡe onamadu niro, “Eḡe hegotoꞌi.”
\v 44 Filipiꞌe Betesaida vazeḡa, ebu Anderea zu Petero teite ne tiba.
\v 45 Ebu Filipiꞌa Natanaela vaḡe onamadu niro, “Eme Moseꞌa goro ḡoeꞌa zamaḡano mirihiroteꞌe, zu peroveta azaḡaniꞌa zeḡe buka zamaḡano mirihiroteꞌe vazeḡa horoneha. Aniꞌe Iosefa ubuga, Nazareta vazeḡa Iesu.”
\v 46 Ebu Natanaelaꞌa naenaeniro, “Nazaretaꞌe ne komeꞌa! Eꞌea nagini manoḡaniꞌa fureraꞌuma?” Filipiꞌa niro, “Aradu ḡianoꞌi.”
\p 
\v 47 Ebu Iesuꞌe Natanaelaꞌa ani vaḡe areꞌeteꞌe horonirotene, Natanaela moneo ḡoeriro, “Vaze ꞌadiꞌe hube hune Isaraela vazeḡa. Ani mazaoꞌe ḡuriro ꞌahoga oꞌoꞌa.”
\v 48 Natanaelaꞌa ḡadiniro, “Ḡaꞌe e nougenouge edereꞌohe?” Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Filipiꞌa ꞌizema huḡadogano, ḡa figi ireḡa ꞌuꞌuḡano radiuꞌenogano horoꞌeha.”
\v 49 Ebu Natanaelaꞌa niro, “Rabi, ḡaꞌe Badiꞌa Ubuga! Isaraela azaḡa kini!”
\v 50 Iesuꞌa niro, “Eḡeꞌa ḡaꞌe figi ireḡa ꞌuꞌuḡano radateꞌea horoꞌeha rae radu ḡa eḡe mazao fieꞌehe? Rehano ḡa ꞌahi ufeta vitinoga ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa horoniꞌuma.”
\v 51 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, za adureꞌa bohatanadu Badiꞌa tuḡure viganiꞌa Vaze Ubuga rana iteꞌeteꞌe zu ovoeꞌeteꞌe horoniꞌuma.”
\c 2
\s1 Vu hina Vaini Vuḡa Haḡairo
\p 
\v 1 Mada uḡiduḡano Galilea habaꞌano Kana neḡano hahu muiḡa ꞌahoga haḡairo, ebu Iesu viꞌaꞌe mui eꞌe zamaḡano radiro.
\v 2 Mui vazeḡaniꞌa Iesu zu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa zuni huziro.
\v 3 Muio vaini vuḡaniꞌa hauḡirotene, viꞌaniꞌa Iesu niro, “Ze vaini vuḡaꞌe hauḡeha.”
\v 4 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Roḡae boro, ḡa nougadu eḡe mazao ꞌouge raꞌohe? Eḡe gau madaḡaꞌe ꞌize mene maha.”
\v 5 Rehano viꞌaniꞌa mui tuḡure azaḡa ziro, “Aniꞌa nouge rae zoꞌidene, ꞌouge haḡaoꞌi.”
\p 
\v 6 Ebu hadi hina haḡairoteꞌe vu ḡoḡoreḡa fuꞌo tiba fareꞌe deꞌea. Aꞌe Iuda azaḡa goro idunaḡano, ze zu ḡauze dehenoga veize tiro.\f + \fr 2:6 \ft Aꞌe Badiꞌa mazao kuranoga veize ga ogomu anoga veize tiro. \f* Hadi vu ḡoḡoreḡa tibatibano vu 20 gareni onamo 30 gareni iriꞌavonoga idararo.
\v 7 Iesuꞌa tuḡure azaḡa ziro, “Ḡoḡore niduꞌa vu iriꞌavonoꞌi.” ꞌOugadu ze vu beuꞌe ite hebeꞌano iri'avoniro.
\v 8 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Vu nu iḡi vaḡinadu mui ibitohauꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ha onamoꞌi.” Eꞌanoꞌo ze ꞌouge haḡairo.
\p 
\v 9 Ebu mui ibitohauꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa vu eꞌe vaini vuḡano reiroteꞌe gage nuriro. Aniꞌe vaini vuḡa eꞌe noumanoꞌo mae arirotaꞌaꞌe aḡuꞌa, u vu iḡi vaḡiniroteꞌe tuḡure azaḡaꞌe edeḡa. Ebu mui ibitohauꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa hahu iziga ohozeḡa huniro.
\v 10 Ebu ani matuꞌeꞌenaꞌa, hahu iziga ohozeḡa niro, “Vaze niduꞌa vaini vuḡa manoḡa tauḡi ibite oma mae fureneꞌohe. Ebu mui azaḡaniꞌa gage sautuꞌetuꞌu hena tahiḡa manoḡa mae fureneꞌohe. Rehano ḡaeꞌa onao izidi vaini vuḡa manoḡa tauḡi vazevaze veize modeha.”
\v 11 Iesuꞌa haḡai nu badeḡa ibiꞌaꞌe Galilea habaꞌano Kana neḡano ꞌahige haḡairo. ꞌOugadu ani ane ni mae ḡihiniro, ebu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa ani mazao firo.
\p 
\v 12 Mui ḡarugano Iesuꞌe viꞌa, negoḡa duḡuru zu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa teite Kaperanauma ovoiro. Ebu eꞌea mada nu radiro. \fig Vu hina vaini vuḡa haḡairo|src="WA03814b.tif" size="col" ref="2:1-11"\fig*
\s1 Kuru Neḡa Deheniro
\r (Mataio 21:12-13; Mareko 11:15-17; Luka 19:45-46)
\p 
\v 13 Iuda azaḡa Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa madaḡaniꞌa hanitirotene, Iesuꞌe Ierusalema itiro.
\v 14 Ebu ani vaze nuꞌe kuru neḡa habaꞌano boromakau, mamoe zu Tubugo niniḡa seronoga horoziro, ebu nuꞌe fataze babaḡano ehoradu hadi seniso zenoga\f + \fr 2:14 \ft kuru neḡa takesi veize. \f* horoziro.
\v 15 ꞌOugadu ani mini hina masizeꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa haḡadu eꞌe hina zeḡe niduꞌa ebu mamoe zu boromakau niduꞌa kuru neḡa habaꞌanonoꞌo masize ḡururuziro. Ebu hadi seniso ziniꞌeteꞌe azaḡa hadize beuꞌe ḡuzuhiro, zu fataze mae ḡihuniro.
\v 16 Ebu Tubugo niniḡa seroneꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ziro, “Ḡau ꞌahi niduꞌa ꞌadanoꞌo mae vaḡinoꞌi! Mamahe neꞌe maketi habaꞌano ago haḡaoꞌi!”
\v 17 Ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe Buka Zaḡoḡano ḡoere ꞌahi zamariro, “E Badiꞌa ne zamare borofeꞌohe.”\x + \xo 2:17 \xt Salamo 69:9\x*
\p 
\v 18 Ebu Iuda azaḡaniꞌa ḡadiniro, “Ḡa nagi gigiꞌaḡa hina ꞌahiguḡa haḡaeꞌohe? Ḡae gigiꞌaꞌe Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo roꞌidene, haḡai nu badeḡa ihofoꞌi.”
\v 19 Ebu Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Kuru neḡa ꞌadi fahoꞌi, ꞌougine eḡeꞌa mada uḡidu zamaḡano bare ohoniꞌuma.”
\v 20 Zeḡeꞌa niro, “Kuru neḡa ꞌadi ogorarotene muri 46 madu hauḡiro. U ḡaꞌe mada uḡidu zamaḡano ohoniꞌuma rae raꞌehe?”
\v 21 Rehano Iesuꞌa kuru neḡa reirotaꞌaꞌe ane ahiri moneo reiro.
\v 22 Iesuꞌe runeonoꞌo bare iḡuniroteꞌe ḡarugano, ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa ani ḡoere zamariro. Ebu ze Buka Zaḡoḡano mirihiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa ebu Iesuꞌa reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa mae ḡihiniro.
\p 
\v 23 Iesuꞌe Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa madaḡano Ierusalemao radiunu. Ebu vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa aneꞌa haḡai nu badeḡa haḡairoteꞌe horonadu ani mazao firo.
\v 24 Rehano aniꞌe ze mene mae ḡihiziro, mazaḡa vaze niduꞌa zamaze ederiro.
\v 25 Vaze zamao naginiꞌa radiuꞌetaꞌaꞌe zuni Iesuꞌa ederiroteꞌe uꞌano, aniꞌe vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa vaze ꞌahoga moneo ani ihonoga mene uratiro.
\c 3
\s1 Nikodemo Ihoniro
\p 
\v 1 Farisea vazeḡa ꞌahoga, niḡa Nikodemoꞌa radiunu. Aniꞌe Iuda azaḡa ibitoziꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahoga.
\v 2 Ohere ꞌahogano ani Iesu vaḡe aradu niro, “Rabi, emeꞌe edeḡa, ḡaꞌe Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo ariroteꞌe ihore vazeḡa. Mazaḡa iniuꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa ani teite mene radiune, ani ḡaꞌa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa nu badeḡa haḡaoga mene idaḡa.”
\v 3 Ebu Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ḡaꞌohe, iniuꞌa mene bare fureraune\f + \fr 3:3 \fqa hitanaonoꞌo mene fureraune \f*, Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe horonoga mene idaḡa.”
\v 4 Ebu Nikodemoꞌa niro, “Vaze boroꞌe nougenouge bare fureranoga idaḡa? Aniꞌe viꞌa isi zamaḡano bare diuḡadu fureranoga mene idaḡa.”
\p 
\v 5 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ḡaꞌohe, iniuꞌa vu zu Vine Zaḡoḡa hina mene bare fureraune, aniꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaniꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa rouga mene idaḡa.
\v 6 Vazeꞌe nanu mama ahirionoꞌo ahirio fureruꞌohe. U vineꞌe Badiꞌa Vigaonoꞌo fureruꞌohe.
\v 7 Eḡeꞌa zinaꞌa, 'Zaꞌe bare fureranoꞌi,' rae rateꞌe uꞌano, ago zaguzaganoꞌi.
\v 8 Zaizaiꞌa ane edeḡano zaiduꞌohe. Ḡaꞌe zaizai igiꞌohe, rehano aniꞌa noumanoꞌo areꞌeteꞌe zu noꞌe onameꞌetaꞌaꞌe aḡuꞌa. Eꞌe teige, Vine Zaḡoḡaonoꞌo fureraroteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa zuni ꞌouge fureruꞌohe.”
\p 
\v 9 Ebu Nikodemoꞌa ḡadiniro, “Nougenouge ꞌahiguḡaniꞌa fureruꞌohe?”
\v 10 Iesuꞌa niro, “Ḡaꞌe Isaraela azaḡa ihozeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa, rehano nougadu ꞌahiguḡaꞌe aḡuꞌa?
\v 11 E hube hune ḡaꞌohe. Eme nagini edere ḡauḡa ḡoereꞌohe, zu nagini horoniroteꞌe ḡauḡa rae fureneꞌohe. Rehano za emeꞌa rae fureneꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌaꞌe mene mae ḡihineꞌohe.
\v 12 Eꞌa raha ꞌadao fureruꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa moneo ziro, rehano zaꞌe mene mae ḡihineꞌohe. ꞌOugadu adureo fureruꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa moneo zine, nougenouge mae ḡihiniꞌuma?
\v 13 Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa adure ꞌize mene itiro, rehano Vaze Ubuga, adureonoꞌo ovairoteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa daꞌo itiro.
\v 14 Ibite madaḡano Moseꞌa haba bohaꞌano mohe iraḡa haḡadu somori faḡa rana teadu mae ḡihiniro.\x + \xo 3:14 \xt Naba 21:9\x* Eꞌe teige, Vaze Ubuga zuni vazeꞌa satauro rana mae ḡihiniꞌuma.
\v 15 Aꞌe ani mazao fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidifine raꞌohe. \fig Mose ebu mohe|src="cn01671b.TIF" size="col" ref="3:14-15"\fig*
\p 
\v 16 Badiꞌaꞌa raha ꞌadi azaḡa ufeta zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, ani Ubuga tibuhuga ziniro. Aꞌe, iniu ani mazao fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe mene rudanadu ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidifine raꞌohe.
\v 17 Badiꞌaꞌa raha ꞌadi azaḡa kotazoga veize ani Ubuga mene tuḡuniro, rehano ani uꞌano ze ḡabozoga veize tuḡuniro.
\v 18 Iniu ani mazao fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe mene kotazeꞌohe. Rehano mene fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe amahi kotaziro, mazaḡa ze Badiꞌa Ubuga tibuhuga mazao mene firo.
\v 19 Agaḡaꞌe rahao ariro, rehano vazeꞌa agaḡa mene zamariro ebu haḡaize sauꞌa uꞌano, ze uzabo ufeta zamariro. Eꞌanoꞌo Badiꞌaꞌa kotao ohoziro.
\v 20 Haḡai sauꞌa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe agaḡa heꞌeheꞌenadu agaḡa vaḡe mene areꞌohe, mazaḡa haḡaize sauꞌa rae fureniꞌuma radu rihauꞌohe.
\v 21 Rehano ḡoere huga hegoteꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe agaḡa vaḡe areꞌohe. Aꞌe, ze Badiꞌa ḡoere hegotadu haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡa deheru ihozifine raꞌohe.”
\s1 Ioane Babatisoꞌa Iesu moneo rae Fureniro
\p 
\v 22 Eꞌe ḡarugano Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa teite Iudea habaꞌa onamiro, ebu eꞌea zeḡe teite mada nu radiuꞌenaꞌa, vaze babatisoziro.
\v 23 Ioane Babatiso zuni Salema neḡa uhiḡano Enoni neḡano babatisozinu, mazaḡa eꞌe habaꞌaꞌe vu boro. Vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa babatiso mouga radu ani vaḡe arinu.
\v 24 Eꞌe madaḡano Ioaneꞌe ꞌizema ḡuꞌa neḡano ohoniro.
\p 
\v 25 Ioane tahiꞌaḡa nuꞌa Iuda vazeḡa ꞌahoga teite ahiri ga ḡau faifaine vuzuꞌeꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa moneo taꞌirotitiro.
\v 26 Ebu Ioane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa Ioane vaḡe aradu niro, “Rabi, Ioridana vuḡa moneafa ꞌoma ḡae teite radateꞌe zu ḡaeꞌa rae furenateꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa babatisoziꞌohe, ebu vaze niduꞌa ane vaḡe onameꞌohe.”
\v 27 Ebu Ioaneꞌa naenaeziro, “Badiꞌaꞌa inaraḡa mene haune, vazeni ꞌahoga ꞌouge gauoga mene idaḡa.
\v 28 Eḡeꞌa ꞌahige rae ziro, 'Eꞌe mene Keriso, rehano e ani veize ibite tuḡuhiro.' Eꞌanoꞌo za eḡe ḡoere ꞌahi vaze niduꞌa mazao rae fureniꞌuma.
\v 29 E hari ꞌahoga idane ziꞌohe. Hahu roḡaeḡa izigaꞌe hahu ohozeḡa iziganiꞌa maꞌohe. U hahu ohozeḡa iziga nabugaꞌe edauꞌenaꞌa, hahu ohozeḡa iziga ḡoere igiꞌohe. Igiꞌetene, aniꞌe matuꞌe rudauꞌohe. Hari eꞌe teige, eꞌe hahu ohozeḡa iziga nabuga heuḡa. E zae mazaonoꞌo ani hari egadu matuꞌe rudauꞌohe.
\v 30 Aniꞌe ufeta ḡihiꞌa reꞌuma, u eꞌe ufeta ovoroga reꞌuma.”
\s1 Adureonoꞌo Ovaeꞌeteꞌe Vazeḡa
\p 
\v 31 “Hitanaonoꞌo ovaeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune. Aniꞌe ḡau niduꞌa vitinoga. U rahaonoꞌo areꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe raha ꞌadi vazeḡa, zu rahao fureruꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa moneo ḡoereꞌohe. Adureonoꞌo ovaeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡau niduꞌa vitinoga.
\v 32 Aniꞌa horoniroteꞌe zu igiroteꞌe ḡauḡa rae fureneꞌohe, rehano vazeni ꞌahogaꞌe ani ḡoere mene mae ḡihineꞌohe.
\v 33 Ani ḡoere mae ḡihineꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe Badiꞌa ḡoereꞌe hube hune rae raꞌohe.
\v 34 Badiꞌaꞌa tuḡuniroteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe Badiꞌa ḡoere ziꞌohe, mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa Vine Zaḡoḡa hanadu Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa iḡaiḡa ani teite radiuꞌohe.
\v 35 Moganiꞌa Ubuga zamare borofadu ḡau niduꞌa ani ꞌevora riꞌiniro.
\v 36 Iniu Ubuga mazao fieꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidiro. U iniu Ubuga hezahohauꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡabone mene hidiꞌuma, rehano Badiꞌa zama ḡugiꞌaniꞌa ani ragano reꞌuma.”
\c 4
\s1 Iesu ebu Samaria Roḡaeḡa
\p 
\v 1 Iesuꞌa Ioane vitine ani tahiꞌatahiꞌa ufeta ḡehaḡa zamazadu babatisoziꞌeteꞌe hariḡa Farisea azaḡaniꞌa igiro.
\v 2 Aꞌe Iesuꞌa mene babatisoziro, rehano ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa babatisoziro.
\v 3 Aniꞌe Farisea azaḡaniꞌa ani moneo ḡoereꞌeteꞌe ederirotene, Iudea habaꞌa modadu bare Galilea habaꞌa onamiro.
\p 
\v 4 Galilea habaꞌa onameꞌeteꞌe ibiḡano aniꞌe Samaria habaꞌa vitine onamiro.
\v 5 ꞌOugadu Samaria habaꞌano ne boro ꞌahoga, niḡa Sukao feuriro. Eꞌe neḡaꞌe Iakoboꞌa ubuga Iosefa haroteꞌe habaꞌa uhiḡano,
\v 6 ebu Iakobo idu vuḡa zuni eꞌea. Iesuꞌa ibi faḡa aradu fuḡone runiro ꞌahine, idu vuḡa genaḡano ehore radiro. Aꞌe madai kirikiri.
\p 
\v 7 Samaria roḡaeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa vu abi ariro. Iesuꞌa ani horonadu niro, “Vu gagifine nu iniꞌumahe?”
\v 8 Eꞌe madaḡano Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe ogomu hoitoga veize ne onamadu ani teite mene radiro.
\v 9 Ebu Samaria roḡaeḡaniꞌa niro, “Ḡaꞌe Iuda vazeḡa, u eꞌe Samaria roḡaeḡa. Nougadu ḡa eḡe mazao vu umideꞌohe?” Iuda azaḡaꞌe Samaria azaḡa teite mene tiburuꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, ani ꞌouge rae reiro.
\v 10 Ebu Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Ḡa Badiꞌaꞌa nagi ḡahunoneḡa ḡanihi rae ederifone zu ḡae mazao vu umiꞌeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe iniu rae ederifone, ḡa umihadu eḡeꞌa ḡabone vuḡa ḡanifo.”
\v 11 Roḡae eꞌeꞌa niro, “Vaze boro, ḡae mazao vu abeꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡaꞌe oꞌoꞌa zu idu vuḡa ꞌahiꞌe vo hutuna. Ḡabone vuḡaꞌe nouma meꞌuma?
\v 12 Emeḡe vouḡa Iakoboꞌa idu vuḡa ꞌahi rifiro. Ani idu ꞌahi vuḡanonoꞌo vu gagiro, ebu ani ubuga duḡuru zu aneꞌa ḡubuziroteꞌe ḡauḡa zuni vu ꞌahi gagiro. Ḡaꞌe ani ufeta vitine ḡihiꞌaḡahe?”
\p 
\v 13 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Iniuꞌa vu ꞌadi gageꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe iriganiꞌa bare moꞌoniꞌuma.
\v 14 Rehano iniu eḡeꞌa hauꞌeteꞌe vuḡa gageꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe iriga mene bare moꞌoniꞌuma. Eḡeꞌa hauꞌeteꞌe vuḡaꞌe ane zamao sore iteꞌeteꞌe iduḡa vuḡa teigiꞌuma ebu ḡabone tuḡutuḡu haꞌuma.”
\v 15 Roḡae eꞌeꞌa niro, “Vaze boro, eꞌe vuḡaꞌe eḡe enoꞌi. ꞌOugine, irinehe mene bare moꞌohiꞌuma zu vu aboḡa veize e ꞌahi mene bare ariꞌuma.”
\v 16 Iesuꞌa niro, “Ḡa onamadu iꞌu hune aroꞌi.”
\v 17 Roḡae eꞌeꞌa naenaeniro, “E ihe oꞌoꞌa.” Iesuꞌa niro, “Ḡaꞌa iꞌu oꞌoꞌa raꞌetaꞌaꞌe hube.
\v 18 Ḡaꞌe ibite iꞌu fuꞌo meiro, ebu izidi ḡae teite radiuꞌeteꞌe ohozeḡa zuni ḡae mene iꞌu. Ḡaꞌa rataꞌaꞌe hube.”
\p 
\v 19 Ebu roḡae eꞌeꞌa niro, “Vaze boro, e ḡaꞌe peroveta vazeḡa rae edereha.
\v 20 Vouḡafe, Samaria azaḡaniꞌa Gerizimi maḡa ꞌada kuraro. Rehano za, Iuda azaḡaꞌe, 'Kuru habaꞌaꞌe Ierusalema daꞌo,' rae raꞌohe.”
\v 21 Iesuꞌa niro, “Roḡae, eḡe ḡoere ꞌahi mae ḡihinoꞌi. Mada ꞌahoganiꞌa arine, za Mama mazao kurauꞌeteꞌe habaꞌaꞌe mene maḡa ꞌada ga mene Ierusalemao reꞌuma.
\v 22 Za, Samaria azaḡaꞌe iniu mazao kurauꞌetaꞌaꞌe aḡuꞌa. U eme, Iuda azaḡaꞌe iniu mazao kurauꞌetaꞌaꞌe edeḡa, mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa vaze ḡaboziteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe Iuda azaḡa mazaonoꞌo tuḡuniro.
\v 23 Rehano hube hune kurauꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa Badiꞌa Vine inaraḡa hina zu ḡoere huga hina Mama mazao kuratiteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa ariꞌuma, ebu izidiꞌe eꞌe madaḡa raꞌohe. Mamaꞌa ani mazao ꞌouge kurauꞌeteꞌe azaḡa vaḡeꞌohe.
\v 24 Badiꞌaꞌe vine, eꞌanoꞌo iniuꞌa ani mazao kurauꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe Badiꞌa Vine inaraḡa hina zu ḡoere huga hina kuraꞌuma.”
\v 25 Roḡae eꞌeꞌa niro, “Eḡe edeḡa, Mesia, Keriso rae huneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ariꞌuma. Aniꞌa arine, ḡau niduꞌa ihofiꞌuma.”
\v 26 Iesuꞌa niro, “Izidi ḡaꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe Keriso, eḡe.”
\s1 Iesu Tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa Bariro
\p 
\v 27 Iesuꞌa ꞌouge ḡoerirotene, ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa feuri ariro. Ebu ze zaguzagaro, mazaḡa aniꞌe roḡae ꞌahoga teite ḡoere radiro. Rehano vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa Iesu mazao ninaꞌa, “Ḡa nougihi raꞌohe?” ga “Ḡa nougadu ani teite ḡoereꞌohe?” rae mene ḡadiniro.
\p 
\v 28 Ebu roḡae eꞌeꞌa vu ḡoḡoreḡa modadu ne onamiro, ebu ne azaḡa ziro,
\v 29 “Aradu vaze ꞌadi ḡianoꞌi! Ani eḡeꞌa haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡa niduꞌa eheha. Aniꞌe Keriso gaogi!”
\v 30 Ebu ze neze modadu Iesu vaḡe onamiro.
\s1 Hiriveꞌeteꞌe Azaḡa
\p 
\v 31 Eꞌe zamaḡano Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa Iesu uminiro, “Rabi, ḡa ogomu nu anoꞌi.”
\v 32 Rehano aniꞌa ziro, “Ogomuꞌe eḡe mazao eꞌe, rehano zaꞌe ogomu eꞌe moneoꞌe aḡuꞌa.”
\v 33 Ebu ze zeḡeꞌa bare ḡadimutitiro, “Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa ogomu hanahe?”
\v 34 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Eḡe ogomuꞌe eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe vazeḡa ura haḡaeꞌeteꞌe zu ane gau haḡae huneꞌeteꞌe raꞌohe.
\v 35 Zaꞌe, 'Bato ḡazaḡa enogano hiriviteꞌe madaḡa meꞌuma,' rae raꞌohe. Rehano eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, ubumaze raꞌanadu meba faine ḡianoꞌi. Meba ogomuḡaniꞌa hudanadu hiriveꞌeteꞌe madaḡa ꞌai maha.
\v 36 Hiriveꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe gauḡa naeḡa hideꞌohe, ebu ane hirivadu ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hideꞌeteꞌe huga nuꞌoneꞌohe. ꞌOugine, ḡorauꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa zu hiriveꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa, anianine matuꞌe tiburaꞌuma.
\v 37 Ḡoere ꞌahiꞌe hube, 'Vaze ꞌahogaꞌe ḡorauꞌohe ebu ꞌahogaꞌe hiriveꞌohe.'
\v 38 Zaeꞌa mene ḡoraroteꞌe ogomuḡa hirivoga veize e za tuḡuziro. Vaze ꞌahogaꞌahogaꞌe gau boro haḡairo, u zaꞌe zeḡe gauonoꞌo huga maꞌohe.”
\s1 Samaria Azaḡaniꞌa Iesu mazao Firo
\p 
\v 39 Ne beꞌanoꞌo Samaria azaḡa ḡehaḡaniꞌa Iesu mazao firo, mazaḡa roḡae eꞌeꞌa ꞌahige rae fureniro, “Ani eꞌa haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡa niduꞌa eheha.”
\v 40 Ze ani vaḡe aradu uminiro, “Emeḡe teite mada nu radoꞌi.” ꞌOugadu aniꞌe zeḡe teite mada aheu eꞌea radiro.
\v 41 Ebu Iesu ḡoere uꞌano, vaze ufeta ḡehaḡaniꞌa ani mazao firo.
\v 42 Ebu zeḡeꞌa roḡae eꞌe niro, “Emeꞌe mene ḡae ḡoere uꞌano, rehano eme emeḡeꞌa bare ani ḡoere egateꞌe uꞌano ani mazao fieꞌohe. Mazaḡa eme edereha, vaze ꞌadiꞌe hube hune raha ꞌadi azaḡa niduꞌa ḡabozeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa.” \fig Samaria roḡaeḡa|src="CN01674B.TIF" size="col" ref="4:7-26"\fig*
\s1 Kini Gau Vazeḡa Ubuga Fainiro
\r (Mataio 8:5-13; Luka 7:1-10)
\p 
\v 43 Mada aheu enogano Iesuꞌe eꞌea iḡunadu Galilea habaꞌa onamiro.
\v 44 Mazaḡa ani aneꞌa bare ꞌahige rae reiro, “Peroveta vazeḡaꞌe ane haba azaḡaniꞌa mene gubaneꞌohe.”
\v 45 Ani Galilea habaꞌano feurirotene, Galilea azaḡaniꞌa ani mae zouniro, mazaḡa ze Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa madaḡano Ierusalemao radiuꞌenaꞌa, Iesuꞌa Mui eꞌe zamaḡano haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡa niduꞌa horoniro.
\p 
\v 46 Ebu Iesuꞌa Galilea habaꞌano Kana neḡa bare onamiro. Aꞌe vu ḡihune vaini vuḡano haḡairoteꞌe neḡa. Eꞌea kini gau vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa radiunu, ebu ani ubugaꞌe ugiꞌa madu Kaperanauma zamaḡano radiunu.
\v 47 Aniꞌe Iesuꞌa Iudea habaꞌanonoꞌo Galilea habaꞌano feuri ariroteꞌe igirotene, ani vaḡe onamadu uminiro, “Ubudeheꞌe ugiꞌa madu nariga rudauꞌohe. Ḡa eḡe teite Kaperanauma ovoadu ani fainoꞌi.”
\v 48 Ebu Iesuꞌa niro, “Zaꞌe haḡai nu badeḡa zu zaguzagatiteꞌe haḡaiḡa mene horonine, eḡe mazao mene fiꞌuma.”
\v 49 Kini gau vazeḡaniꞌa niro, “Vaze boro, ubudehe ꞌizema rudanogano, aro ovoihi.”
\v 50 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Onamoꞌi. Ubugoꞌe ḡabodiꞌuma.” ꞌOuge reirotene, ani Iesu ḡoere mae ḡihiniro ebu ani ne ovoiro.
\p 
\v 51 Ani ibio ovoeꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano, ane tuḡure azaḡaniꞌa ani hidadu ihoniro, “Ubugoꞌe ḡabodeha!”
\v 52 Ebu aniꞌa ḡadiziro, “Ubudeheꞌe naniꞌa manoreha?” Zeḡeꞌa niro, “Ohoḡore ḡorava mone mada tiba zamaḡano gigiꞌaniꞌa hauḡeha.”
\v 53 ꞌOugadu mogaꞌe ederiro, eꞌe madaḡaꞌe Iesuꞌa, “Ubugoꞌe ḡabodiꞌuma,” rae reiroteꞌe madaḡa. Eꞌanoꞌo ani zu ane neo tiburu radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe Iesu mazao firo.
\v 54 Aꞌe Iesuꞌa Iudea habaꞌanonoꞌo Galilea habaꞌa ariroteꞌe enogano haḡairoteꞌe haḡai nu badeḡa aheuḡa.
\c 5
\s1 Betesaida Duꞌura Genaḡano Ugi Vazeḡa Fainiro
\p 
\v 1 Eꞌe enogano Iuda azaḡa mui madaḡa ꞌahoga meirotene, Iesuꞌe Ierusalema itiro.
\v 2 Ierusalema zamaḡano ibiheta ꞌahoga niḡaꞌe Mamoe Ibiheta. Ibiheta eꞌe uhiḡano Heberu ḡoeꞌano Betesaida rae huneꞌeteꞌe duꞌuraḡa komeꞌa ꞌahogaꞌe eꞌe, ebu eꞌe duꞌuraḡa genaḡano ibi zauhaḡaꞌe fuꞌo.
\v 3 Ebu ugi azaḡa ḡehaḡaniꞌa mada niduꞌa eꞌea baze baninu. Zeꞌe ubuma kuruḡa azaḡa, oda sauꞌa azaḡa zu ahiꞌa mene haganeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa.\f + \fr 5:3 \fqa ebu ze vu hagaroga guhininu. \fv 4 \fqa Mazaḡa mada tibatiba Zuhiꞌa Boro tuḡure viganiꞌa ovadu vuḡa mirunido. Vu hagariroteꞌe enogano iniu ugi vazeḡa ibite vuo diuḡirotaꞌaꞌe ugizeꞌa manorido. \f*
\p 
\v 5 Zeḡe boꞌaḡano muri 38 zamaḡano uginiroteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa radiunu.
\v 6 Iesuꞌa ani deꞌea baze radiuꞌeteꞌe horonadu ani faḡa hune uginirotaꞌaꞌe ederiro. ꞌOugadu aneꞌa ugi vazeḡa niro, “Ḡa manoroga urateꞌehe?”
\v 7 Ugi vazeḡaniꞌa naenaeniro, “Vaze boro, vuꞌa hagareꞌetene, vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa duꞌura zamaḡano e mene danahe ohoheꞌohe. Ebu e eḡeꞌa bare diuḡi onameꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa ibite diuḡeꞌohe.”
\v 8 Ebu Iesuꞌa niro, “Iḡunoꞌi, ebu farataḡo madu onamoꞌi.”
\v 9 Eꞌebone ugi vazeḡa ꞌai zogone manoriro ebu farataḡa madu onamiro.
\p Eꞌe madaḡaꞌe Bana Madaḡa.
\v 10 Eꞌanoꞌo Iuda azaḡa ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ugionoꞌo manoriroteꞌe vazeḡa niro, “Izidiꞌe Bana Madaḡa. Ḡaꞌa farataḡo odoheꞌetaꞌaꞌe Mose goro ḡoeꞌa variꞌeꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa.”
\v 11 Rehano aniꞌa naenaeziro, “Faihateꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa, 'Farataḡo madu onamoꞌi,' rae eheha.”
\v 12 Zeḡeꞌa ḡadiniro, “Iniu vazeꞌa, 'Farataḡo madu onamoꞌi,' rae ḡaha?”
\v 13 Rehano manoriroteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe iniuꞌa ani fainirotaꞌaꞌe aḡuꞌa, mazaḡa Iesuꞌa eꞌea radiroteꞌe azaḡa ḡunuḡano dauḡiro.
\p 
\v 14 Eꞌe enogano Iesuꞌa kuru neḡa habaꞌano ani hidadu niro, “Ḡianoꞌi, ḡa ꞌai manoreha. Eꞌanoꞌo ufeta sauꞌaniꞌa ḡae mazao mene fureranoga veize, haḡai sauꞌa ago bare haḡaoꞌi.”
\v 15 Ebu vaze eꞌeꞌa onamadu Iuda azaḡa boroboro ziro, “Faihateꞌe vazeḡaꞌe Iesu.” \fig Iesuꞌa ugi vazeḡa fainiro|src="WA03828b.tif" size="col" ref="5:5-9"\fig*
\s1 Badiꞌa Ubuga
\p 
\v 16 Iesuꞌa ugi vazeḡa Bana Madaḡano fainiroteꞌe uꞌano, Iuda azaḡa ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa Iesu rae sausauniro.
\v 17 Rehano Iesuꞌa ziro, “Eḡe Mamaꞌa mada niduꞌa gaueꞌohe onao izidi, eꞌanoꞌo eḡe zuni gaueꞌohe.”
\v 18 Iesuꞌa ꞌouge reiro ꞌahine, Iuda azaḡa ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ani matihi radu ufeta inariro. Aꞌe mene mazaḡa Iesuꞌa Bana Madaḡa goroḡa variꞌiroteꞌe daꞌo, rehano mazaḡa ani aneꞌa bare, “Badiꞌaꞌe eḡe Mama,” radu aneꞌa bare Badiꞌa teite idaniro.
\p 
\v 19 Ebu Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, Badiꞌa Ubugaꞌe ane daꞌo ḡau ꞌahoga haḡaogaꞌe mene idaḡa, rehano Moganiꞌa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa horonadu eꞌe hegote haḡaeꞌohe. Mazaḡa Moganiꞌa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa Badiꞌa Ubuga zuni haḡaeꞌohe.
\v 20 Mogaꞌe ani Ubuga zamare borofeꞌohe, ebu aniꞌa nagini haḡaeꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa niduꞌa Ubuga ihoneꞌohe. Ebu ꞌahiguḡa ufeta vitineꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa Ubuga ihonadu zae mae zaguzaguziꞌuma.
\v 21 Moganiꞌa rune azaḡa mae ḡihizadu ḡabozeꞌeteꞌe teige, Ubuga zuni aneꞌa urateꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ḡabone ziniꞌohe.
\v 22 Ebu Moganiꞌa vaze ꞌahoga mene kotazeꞌohe, rehano kota gauḡa niduꞌaꞌe Ubuga ꞌevora tiro.
\v 23 Eꞌanoꞌo vaze niduꞌaꞌe Moga gubaneꞌeteꞌe teige, Ubuga zuni gubaniꞌuma. Iniu Ubuga mene gubaneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ani tuḡuniroteꞌe Moga mene gubaneꞌohe.
\p 
\v 24 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, iniu eḡe ḡoere igiꞌeteꞌe zu eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe vazeḡa mazao fieꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidiro. Badiꞌaꞌa ani mene kotaneꞌohe ebu aniꞌe runeonoꞌo ḡabone meiro.
\v 25 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, rune azaḡaniꞌa Baidꞌa Ubuga ago igiteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa ariꞌuma, ebu izidi feureha. Ani ago igiꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe ḡabodiꞌuma.
\v 26 Mogaꞌe vaze ḡabozeꞌeteꞌe ḡaboneḡa meiroteꞌe teige, Ubuga zuni hanadu Ubugaꞌe ḡabozeꞌeteꞌe ḡaboneḡa meiro.
\v 27 Ebu aniꞌe Vaze Ubuga radu Moganiꞌa vaze kotazeꞌeteꞌe gigiꞌaḡa haro.
\p 
\v 28 Eꞌe moneo ago zaguzaganoꞌi, mazaḡa mada ꞌahoganiꞌa arine, rune azaḡa niduꞌa iduonoꞌo Ubuga ago igiꞌuma,
\v 29 ebu ze bare ḡabodiꞌuma. Manoḡa haḡairoteꞌe azaḡaꞌe ḡabone veize bare ḡabodiꞌuma, u sauꞌa haḡairoteꞌe azaḡaꞌe kotazoga veize bare ḡabodiꞌuma.
\v 30 E ḡau ꞌahoga eḡeꞌa bare haḡaogaꞌe mene idaḡa. Mamaꞌa ihiꞌeteꞌe idunaḡano, e vaze kotazeꞌohe. Eḡe kotaꞌe duduḡa, mazaḡa e eḡe urao mene haḡaeꞌohe, rehano eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe vazeḡa urao haḡaeꞌohe.”
\s1 Iesu moneo rae Fureniro
\p 
\v 31 “E eḡeꞌa bare eḡe moneo rae furenine, za mene mae ḡihihiꞌuma.
\v 32 Rehano Mamaꞌa eḡe veize rae fureneꞌohe. E edeḡa, ane eḡe moneo rae fureneꞌetaꞌaꞌe hube.
\p 
\v 33 Zaꞌa vaze nu Ioane vaḡe tuḡuzirotene, ani eḡe moneo ḡoere huga rae fureniro.
\v 34 E vazeꞌa eḡe moneo rae furenoga mene urateꞌohe. Rehano e Ioane ḡoereꞌe hube rae ziꞌetaꞌaꞌe zaꞌa ani ḡoere egadu ḡabone hidoga veize raꞌohe.
\v 35 Ioaneꞌe ihure duhuḡa teige zamaze aganiro, ebu za mada tahiḡa ani agaḡano matuꞌihi reiro.
\p 
\v 36 Rehano eḡe moneo rae fureneꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa ꞌahogaꞌe eḡe mazao eꞌe. Aꞌe Ioaneꞌa eḡe moneo rae fureniroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa vitinoga. Mamaꞌa eḡe mazao gau nu enadu 'Haḡae hauḡoꞌi,' reiro, ebu e izidi eꞌe gauḡa niduꞌa haḡaeꞌohe. Eꞌe gauḡa niduꞌa Mamaꞌa eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe rae fureneꞌohe.
\v 37 Ebu Mamaꞌa eḡe tuḡuhadu ani aneꞌa bare eḡe moneo rae fureniro. Rehano za ani ago mene hune igiro zu iraḡa mene hune horoniro.
\v 38 Za aniꞌa tuḡuniroteꞌe vazeḡa mazao mene fieꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, ani ḡoereꞌe zae zamao mene radiuꞌohe.
\v 39 Zaꞌe Buka Zaḡoḡa faifaine ḡianeꞌohe, mazaḡa eꞌe ḡianine, ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidiꞌuma rae zamareꞌohe. Buka Zaḡoḡaniꞌa eḡe moneo rae fureneꞌohe.
\v 40 Rehano za eḡe vaḡe aradu ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidoga hezahohauꞌohe.
\p 
\v 41 E vazeꞌa niguheꞌeteꞌe mene mae ḡihineꞌohe.
\v 42 E edeḡa, za zamaze niduꞌa hina Badiꞌa mene zamareꞌohe.
\v 43 Eꞌe Mamahe niḡano ariro, rehano za e mene mae ḡihiheꞌohe. U vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa ane niḡano arine, za ani mae ḡihiniꞌuma.
\v 44 Za zaeꞌa bare nigutiteꞌohe, rehano Badiꞌa tibuhuganiꞌa za niguzoga mene uratadu eꞌe veizeꞌe mene inareꞌohe. Eꞌanoꞌo zaꞌa eḡe mazao fioga zuni mene idaḡa.
\p 
\v 45 Eḡeꞌa Mama ubumao za kotao ohoziꞌuma rae ago zamaroꞌi. Za kotao ohozeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe Mose. Zaꞌe Mose goro ḡoeꞌa hegotadu ḡabone hidiꞌuma rae zamareꞌohe.
\v 46 Zaeꞌa Mose mae ḡihinifone, eḡe mazao fifo, mazaḡa aniꞌe Buka Zaḡoḡano eḡe moneo mirihiro.
\v 47 Rehano za Moseꞌa mirihiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaꞌe mene mae ḡihineꞌohe. Tena nougenouge eḡe ḡoere mae ḡihiniꞌuma?”
\c 6
\s1 Vaze 5,000 Ḡubuziro
\r (Mataio 14:13-21; Mareko 6:30-44; Luka 9:10-17)
\p 
\v 1 Eꞌe enogano Iesuꞌe Galilea duꞌuraḡa, niḡa ꞌahogaꞌe Tiberia, moneafa fare onamiro.
\v 2 Ebu vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa ani hegotiro, mazaḡa ze aniꞌa ugi azaḡa mazao haḡairoteꞌe haḡai nu badeḡa horoniro.
\v 3 Ebu Iesuꞌa maḡa itadu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa teite eꞌea ehoriro.
\v 4 Iuda azaḡa Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡaꞌe hanitiro.
\p 
\v 5 Iesuꞌa dude ehamanadu vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa ane vaḡe areꞌeteꞌe horonirotene, Filipi ḡadiniro, “Eme vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa ꞌadi ḡubuzoga veize ꞌuvahu odogaꞌe nouma hoitiꞌuma?”
\v 6 Ani Filipi tuhune nurihi radu ꞌouge rae ḡadimaro, mazaḡa ani aneꞌa bare nagini haḡaiꞌuma rae ederiro.
\v 7 Ebu Filipiꞌa naenaeniro, “Bato fuꞌo uḡidu fare gauḡa hadiḡa\f + \fr 6:7 \fqa Denari 200. \ft Denari tibaꞌe mada tiba gau naeḡa. \f* hina ꞌuvahu odoga hoitadu, ze tibatiba anoga veize tahitahe zinine zuni mene idaraꞌuma.”
\v 8 Ebu Iesu tahiꞌa ꞌahoga, Simona Petero negoḡa, Andereaꞌa niro,
\v 9 “ꞌAdao tahiꞌa ohozeḡa ꞌahoga mazaoꞌe ꞌuvahu odoga\f + \fr 6:9 \fqa bali ꞌuvahu odoga \f* fuꞌo zu ḡozone aheu eꞌe, rehano vaze ufeta ḡehaḡa uꞌano mene idaraꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 10 Ebu Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ziro, “Vaze niduꞌa ehoroꞌi rae zoꞌi.” Aꞌe ve ḡunuḡa habaꞌa uꞌano, zeḡe niduꞌa eꞌe rana ehoriro. Zeḡe boꞌaḡano ohoze niduꞌaꞌe 5,000 heuḡa.
\v 11 Ebu Iesuꞌa ꞌuvahu odoga madu Badiꞌa mazao manoḡa tauḡi reiro, ebu eꞌea ehore radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ḡahugiro. Ebu ḡozone zuni ꞌouge haḡadu zeḡe urao borofe aro.
\v 12 Vaze niduꞌa au ubararotene, Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ziro, “Ogomu ḡahaꞌaḡahaꞌa ago mode tauḡoꞌi, rehano niduꞌa nuꞌonoꞌi.”
\v 13 Eꞌanoꞌo ꞌuvahu odoga fuꞌo hina vaze niduꞌa borofe aroteꞌe enogano modiroteꞌe ogomuḡa nuꞌonirotene, tunahu niduꞌa gaubanana aheu fare iri'avoniro.
\p 
\v 14 Iesuꞌa haḡai nu badeḡa haḡairoteꞌe vaze niduꞌa horonadu ꞌahige ḡadahe ḡoeriro, “Hube hune vaze ꞌadiꞌe raha ꞌahao ariꞌuma rae reiroteꞌe peroveta vazeḡa!”
\v 15 Iesuꞌe zeꞌa aradu inaraze hina ani obone kinio ohonihi rae ederiro. ꞌOugadu ane daꞌo maḡa bare itiro. \fig ꞌUvahu odoga fuꞌo zu ḡozone aheu|src="43_Luke9:13-17_Loaves&Fish.jpg" size="col" ref="6:8-13"\fig*
\s1 Vu rana Onamiro
\r (Mataio 14:22-27; Mareko 6:45-52)
\p 
\v 16 Ḡoravararotene, Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe Galilea duꞌuraḡa ovoiro.
\v 17 Uzaborarotene, Iesuꞌa zeḡe vaḡe mene ariroteꞌe uꞌano, ze ḡasio tiriro ebu duꞌura moneafa faradu Kaperanauma onamiro.
\v 18 Ebu zavara boroꞌa feuradu saꞌuꞌa vu kafeniro.
\v 19 Ze fuꞌo ga fuꞌo tiba fare kilomita reve onamirotene, Iesuꞌa vu rana onamadu ḡasize hanitiroteꞌe horoniro. ꞌOugadu ze rihau rudaro.
\v 20 Rehano aneꞌa ziro, “ꞌAdiꞌe eḡe. Ago rihanoꞌi.”
\v 21 Eꞌebone ze ani ḡasio mae zouniro ebu ḡasiꞌe zeḡeꞌa onameꞌeteꞌe habaꞌano zogone hebetiro.
\p 
\v 22 Irarirotene, duꞌura moneafao radiuꞌeteꞌe vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa ederiro, ohoḡoreꞌe ḡasi tiba daꞌo eꞌea radiro, ebu Iesuꞌe ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa teite ḡasio mene tiradu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa daꞌo onamiro.
\v 23 Eꞌe madaḡano ḡasi nuꞌe Tiberiaonoꞌo ariro, ebu Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa kuranadu vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa ꞌuvahu odoga hina ḡubuziroteꞌe habaꞌano hebetiro.
\v 24 Ebu Vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa ehamanadu Iesu zu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe deꞌea mene horozirotene, ḡasizeo tiradu Iesu vaḡe Kaperanauma onamiro.
\s1 Iesuꞌe Ḡabone Ziniꞌeteꞌe Ogomuḡa
\p 
\v 25 Ze Iesu duꞌura moneafao horonadu ḡadiniro, “Rabi, ḡa naniꞌa ꞌaha feureha?”
\v 26 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, za eḡe vaḡeꞌetaꞌaꞌe, mene mazaḡa eḡeꞌa haḡairoteꞌe haḡai nu badeḡa horoneha, rehano mazaḡa ꞌuvahu odoga au idaraneha.
\v 27 Ruhuruꞌeteꞌe ogomuḡa veize ago gauoꞌi, rehano ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidifine mene hauḡeꞌeteꞌe ogomuḡa veize gauoꞌi. Eꞌe ogomuḡaꞌe Vaze Ubuganiꞌa ziniꞌuma, mazaḡa aniꞌe ꞌouge haḡaoga veize Moga Badiꞌaꞌa ohoniro.”
\p 
\v 28 Ebu zeḡeꞌa ḡadiniro, “Badiꞌa gauḡa haḡaifine eme nougiꞌuma?”
\v 29 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Badiꞌa gauḡaꞌe aneꞌa tuḡuniroteꞌe vazeḡa mazao fieꞌeteꞌe raꞌohe.”
\v 30 Zeḡeꞌa niro, “Eme horonadu ḡae mazao fioga veize, ḡa haḡai nu badeḡa ꞌahoga haḡaoꞌi. Ḡa nagi haḡai nu badeḡa haḡaiꞌuma?
\v 31 Buka Zaḡoḡano Moseꞌa haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡa moneo ꞌahige rae mirihiro, 'Vaze niduꞌa anoga veize aniꞌa adureonoꞌo ogomu ziniro.' Eꞌe teige, eme vouḡaꞌe haba bohaꞌano onamiroteꞌe zamaḡano mana aro.”
\v 32 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, adureonoꞌo ogomu ziniroteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe mene Mose, rehano eḡe Mama. Aniꞌa adureonoꞌo ogomu huga ziniꞌohe.
\v 33 Badiꞌaꞌa ziniꞌeteꞌe ogomuḡaꞌe adureonoꞌo ovadu raha ꞌadi azaḡa ḡabone ziniꞌohe.”
\v 34 Zeḡeꞌa niro, “Vaze boro, eꞌe ogomuḡaꞌe mada niduꞌa rifoꞌi.”
\p 
\v 35 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Eꞌe ḡabone ziniꞌeteꞌe ogomuḡa. Iniu eḡe vaḡe areꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe mene hune vininiꞌuma, ebu iniu eḡe mazao fieꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe iriga mene hune moꞌoniꞌuma.
\v 36 Rehano e ibite ziroteꞌe teige, zaꞌe e horoheha rehano, eḡe mazao mene fieꞌohe.
\v 37 Mamaꞌa iniꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe eḡe vaḡe ariꞌuma, ebu iniu eḡe vaḡe areꞌeteꞌe vazaḡaꞌe eḡeꞌa mene hune hegone vaḡiniꞌuma.
\v 38 Eḡeꞌa eḡe ura haḡaoga veize adureonoꞌo mene ovairo, rehano eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe vazeḡa ura haḡaoga veize ovairo.
\v 39 Ebu eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe vazeḡa uraꞌe, aniꞌa iniroteꞌe azaḡa boꞌaḡano tiba zuni eḡeꞌa mene daunadu, mada ḡonagano zeḡe niduꞌa bare ḡabozeꞌeteꞌe raꞌohe.
\v 40 Eḡe Mamaꞌe iniu Ubuga horonadu ane mazao fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidoga urateꞌohe. E mada ḡonagano ze bare ḡaboziꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 41 Ebu Iuda azaḡaniꞌa Iesu moneo gumude ḡoeriro, mazaḡa ani aneꞌa bare adureonoꞌo ovairoteꞌe ogomuḡa rae reiro.
\v 42 Ebu ze ꞌahige rae reiro, “Vaze ꞌahiꞌe Iosefa ubuga Iesu. Eme ani viꞌa zu moga edeḡa. Ani nougadu, 'Eꞌe adureonoꞌo ovairo,' rae raꞌohe?”
\v 43 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Za eḡe moneo ago gumude ḡoeroꞌi.
\v 44 Mamaheꞌa eḡe tuḡuhiro. Eꞌanoꞌo aniꞌa vaze mene ibitohaune, vazeni ꞌahoganiꞌa eḡe vaḡe aroga mene idaḡa. Eḡe vaḡe areꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe mada ḡonagano eḡeꞌa bare ḡaboniꞌuma.
\p 
\v 45 Buka Zaḡoḡano peroveta azaḡaniꞌa ꞌahige rae mirihiro, 'Badiꞌaꞌa zeḡe niduꞌa ihoziꞌuma.'\x + \xo 6:45 \xt Isaia 54:13\x* Iniu Mama ḡoere egohuꞌeteꞌe zu ani mazaonoꞌo edeḡa maꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe eḡe vaḡe areꞌohe.
\v 46 Vazeni ꞌahoganiꞌa Mama mene horoniro, rehano Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo ariroteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa daꞌo Mama horoniro.
\v 47 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, iniu eḡe mazao fieꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidiro.
\v 48 Eꞌe ḡabone ziniꞌeteꞌe ogomuḡa.
\v 49 Zae vouḡaꞌe haba bohaꞌano mana aro, rehano ze rudaro.
\v 50 U ogomu ꞌadiꞌe adureonoꞌo ovadu iniuꞌa eꞌe aune, ani mene rudaꞌuma.
\v 51 Eꞌe adureonoꞌo ovadu ḡabone ziniꞌeteꞌe ogomuḡa. Iniu ogomu ꞌahi aune, radiu tuḡutuḡiꞌuma. Eꞌe ogomuḡaꞌe eḡe ahiri. Raha ꞌadi azaḡa ḡabozifine, eḡeꞌa ahirihe ziniꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 52 Ebu Iuda azaḡaniꞌa zeḡeꞌa bare taꞌirotiteꞌenaꞌa, ꞌahige rae reiro, “Vaze ꞌadiꞌe nougenouge ahiꞌa rifadu eme aꞌuma?”
\v 53 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, za Vaze Ubuga ahiri mene aune zu ruḡa mene gagine, zamazeo ḡaboneꞌe oꞌoꞌa.
\v 54 Iniu eḡe ahiri auꞌeteꞌe zu ruhe gageꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidiro, ebu mada ḡonagano eḡeꞌa ani bare ḡaboniꞌuma.
\v 55 Mazaḡa eḡe ahiriꞌe ogomu huga zu eḡe ruꞌe vu huga.
\v 56 Iniu eḡe ahiri auꞌeteꞌe zu eḡe ru gageꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe teite tiburanadu radiuꞌohe, ebu eḡe zuni ani teite tiburanadu radiuꞌohe.
\v 57 Mama ḡabode radiuꞌeteꞌeꞌa tuḡuhiro, zu ani uꞌano eḡe zuni ḡabodeꞌohe. Eꞌe teige, iniu eḡe ahiri auꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe uꞌano ḡabodiꞌuma.
\v 58 Eꞌe adureonoꞌo ovairoteꞌe ogomuḡa huga. Ogomu ꞌahiꞌe mene vouḡazeꞌa aroteꞌe ogomuḡa heuḡa. Ze oganadu vesuꞌu rudaro. U ogomu ꞌahi auꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidiꞌuma.”
\v 59 Iesuꞌa ꞌadi ḡoeꞌa Kaperanauma nu'onu'o neḡano ihoziroteꞌe zamaḡano ziro.
\s1 Iesu Tahiꞌa Ḡehaḡaniꞌa Iesu Muhiniro
\p 
\v 60 Iesu tahiꞌa ḡehaḡaniꞌa ani ḡoere eꞌe egadu ꞌahige rae reiro, “Ani ihoreꞌe riḡa. Iniuꞌa eꞌe mae ḡihiniꞌuma?”
\v 61 Iesuꞌe ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa ḡoere eꞌe uꞌano gumudeꞌeteꞌe ederadu ziro, “Ḡoere eꞌe uꞌano zamaze aduduꞌehe?
\v 62 Tena za Vaze Ubuganiꞌa ibite radiroteꞌe habaꞌa bare itoga horonine, nougiꞌuma?
\v 63 Badiꞌa Vineꞌe ḡabone ziniꞌohe. Vaze inaraonoꞌo ḡabone hidoga mene idaḡa. Eḡeꞌa zeateꞌe ḡoeꞌanonoꞌo za Badiꞌa Vine maꞌohe zu ḡabone hideꞌohe.
\v 64 Rehano zae boꞌaḡano nuꞌe eḡe mazao mene fieꞌohe.” Iesuꞌe ḡadaheḡanonoꞌo iniuꞌa ani mazao mene firotaꞌaꞌe zu iniuꞌa revohatitaꞌaꞌe ederiro ꞌahine, ꞌouge reiro.
\v 65 Ebu aniꞌa ziro, “Eꞌe uꞌano, e ibite ꞌahige rae reiro, 'Mamaꞌa iniu eḡe vaḡe aroga gararine, vazeni ꞌahoga zuni eḡe vaḡe arogaꞌe mene idaḡa.'”
\p 
\v 66 Eꞌe madaḡanonoꞌo ane tahiꞌa ḡehaḡaniꞌa ani modadu mene bare hegotiro.
\v 67 Ebu Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌa gaubanana aheu fare ḡadiziro, “Zae zuni eḡe modihi raꞌehe?”
\v 68 Simona Peteroꞌa naenaeniro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, ḡabone tuḡutuḡu rifiꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌaꞌe ḡae mazao, eꞌanoꞌo eme ḡa mene modiꞌuma.
\v 69 Eme ḡaꞌe Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo ariroteꞌe Vazeḡa Zaḡoḡa rae fieꞌohe zu edereꞌohe.”
\v 70 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “E za, gaubanana aheu fare ohoziro, rehano zae boꞌaḡano vaze tibaꞌe Diaboloꞌa ragano reiro.”
\v 71 Iesuꞌa Isakariota vazeḡa Simona ubuga, Iuda moneo ꞌouge reiro. Ani zuni Iesu tahiꞌa gaubanana aheu fare boꞌaḡano tahiꞌa ꞌahoga, rehano vesuꞌu Iesu revohatiteꞌe vazeḡa reiro.
\c 7
\s1 Taruha Muiḡa Onamiro
\p 
\v 1 Eꞌe enogano Iesuꞌa Galilea habaꞌano ragave onamiro. Ani Iudea habaꞌano ragavoga mene uratiro, mazaḡa eꞌea Iuda azaḡa ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ani matihi radu guhine radiro.
\v 2 Ebu Iuda azaḡa mui ꞌahoga, Taruha Muiḡaniꞌa hanitiro.
\v 3 ꞌOugadu Iesu negoḡa duḡuruꞌa Iesu niro, “Ḡa haba ꞌahi modadu Iudea habaꞌa onamoꞌi. ꞌOugine ḡa hegoteꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ḡaeꞌa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe haḡai gigiꞌaḡa horoniꞌuma.
\v 4 Iniu ane bare vaze mazao furenihi raꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe gau ꞌahoga mene sifu haḡaeꞌohe. Ḡa haḡai ꞌahiguḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, raha ꞌadi azaḡa niduꞌa mazao ḡaeꞌa bare fureꞌoꞌi.”
\v 5 Iesu negoḡa duḡuruꞌa ꞌouge nirotaꞌaꞌe mazaḡa zeḡe zuni ani mene mae ḡihiniro.
\p 
\v 6 Ebu Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Izidiꞌe eḡeꞌa mene onamiteꞌe madaḡa, rehano za zae ura madaḡano onamogaꞌe idaḡa.
\v 7 Raha ꞌadi azaḡaꞌe za mene heꞌeheꞌezeꞌohe, u eꞌe heꞌeheꞌeheꞌohe, mazaḡa e haḡaizeꞌe sauꞌa rae fureneꞌohe.
\v 8 Za mui eꞌe veize onamoꞌi. E izidiꞌe mui eꞌe veize mene onamiꞌuma, mazaḡa eḡe madaꞌe ꞌize mene feureha.”
\v 9 Ani ꞌouge rae zeadu Galilea habaꞌano radiro.
\p 
\v 10 Iesu negoḡa duḡuruꞌe mui eꞌe uꞌa itiroteꞌe enogano ani vazeꞌa mene ederifine vesuꞌu sifu itiro.
\v 11 Ebu Iuda azaḡa ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa mui madaḡano Iesu vaḡe ragaveꞌenaꞌa, vaze eꞌea ḡadimaro, “Vaze aꞌe noumao?”
\v 12 Ebu vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa Iesu moneo gumudiro. Nuꞌe raenaꞌa, “Aniꞌe vaze manoḡa,” ebu nuꞌe raenaꞌa, “Mene, ani vaze soꞌozeꞌohe,” rae reiro.
\v 13 Rehano ze Iuda azaḡa boroboro rihoziro ꞌahine, Iesu moneo hunio mene rae fureniro.
\s1 Kuru Neḡano Ihoziro
\p 
\v 14 Mui eꞌe ḡahaꞌa hauḡirotene, Iesuꞌa kuru neḡa habaꞌa itadu vaze ḡadahe ihoziro.
\v 15 ꞌOugadu Iuda azaḡa ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe zaguzaganadu ꞌahige rae reiro, “Vaze ꞌadiꞌe mene hune mirihiro, rehano ani edeḡa ꞌahiguḡaꞌe nougenouge meiro?”
\v 16 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Eḡe ihoreꞌe mene eḡe mazaonoꞌo, rehano eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe vazeḡa mazaonoꞌo ariro.
\v 17 Iniu Badiꞌa ura haḡaihi raꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ederiꞌuma, eḡe ihoreꞌe Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo ariro ga eḡe edeḡanonoꞌo ariro.
\v 18 Iniu ane edeḡano ḡoereꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe vazeꞌa ani nigunoga urateꞌohe. U ani tuḡuniroteꞌe vazeḡa nigunoga urateꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡoere huga raꞌohe zu ani mazao veꞌoḡa oꞌoꞌa.
\v 19 Moseꞌa goro ḡoeꞌa za ziniro, rehano zae boꞌaḡano vaze ꞌahoga zuni eꞌe mene hegoteꞌohe. Nougadu za e uḡuhe ruhihi raꞌohe?”
\p 
\v 20 Vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa naenaeniro, “Vine sauꞌaniꞌa ḡa ragano reiro! Ḡa ḡame nuriꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe oꞌoꞌa.”
\v 21 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Eḡeꞌa Bana Madaḡano haḡai gigiꞌa ꞌahoga haḡadu zae niduꞌa zaguzagauꞌohe.
\v 22 Moseꞌa ahiri rana iḡuri haḡaeꞌeteꞌe goroḡa ḡoeꞌa ziniro. (Ahiri rana iḡuri haḡaeꞌeteꞌe goroḡa ḡoeꞌaꞌe mene Moseonoꞌo, rehano ꞌizema Moseꞌa fureranogano vouḡazeonoꞌo ariro.) Eꞌanoꞌo za Bana Madaḡano zuni tahiꞌa komeꞌa ahiri rana iḡuri haḡaeꞌohe.
\v 23 Za Mose goro ḡoeꞌa mene variꞌoga veize, mada tibatiba Bana Madaḡano zuni tahiꞌa komeꞌa ahiri rana iḡuri haḡaeꞌohe. Tena eḡeꞌa Bana Madaḡano vaze ꞌahoga ahiri niduꞌa fainiroteꞌe uꞌano, za nougadu eḡe mazao maḡuneꞌohe?
\v 24 Zaꞌe vaze enona daꞌo ḡianadu veꞌoḡa rae ago roꞌi. Rehano huga ḡianadu duduḡa ga veꞌoḡa rae roꞌi.”
\s1 Iesuꞌe Kerisohe?
\p 
\v 25 Eꞌe madaḡano Ierusalemao radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ḡadimutitiro, “Vaze ꞌadiꞌe zeꞌa matihi rae inareꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa.
\v 26 Ani hunio ḡoereꞌohe, rehano ze ani rana ḡoere ꞌahoga mene raꞌohe. Iuda azaḡa boroboroꞌa zuni aniꞌe hube hune Keriso raꞌeteꞌe mae ḡihineꞌehe?
\v 27 Rehano aniꞌe mene Keriso, mazaḡa eme vaze ꞌadi noumanoꞌo arirotaꞌaꞌe edeḡa. Kerisoꞌa arine, vazeni ꞌahoga zuni ani noumanoꞌo ariroteꞌe mene ederiꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 28 Ebu Iesu ꞌize kuru neḡa habaꞌano ihozeꞌeteꞌea, ani ḡihau ḡoeriro, “Oꞌe, za e edeḡa ebu e noumanoꞌo arirotaꞌaꞌe edeḡa. Rehano e eḡe edeḡano mene ariro. Eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe Badiꞌaꞌe hube hune. Za ani aḡuꞌa.
\v 29 U e ani edeḡa, mazaḡa eꞌe ani mazaonoꞌo ariro zu aniꞌa eḡe tuḡuhiro.”
\v 30 ꞌOuge reirotene, ze Iesu obone ti nuriro, rehano vaze ꞌahoga ꞌevoꞌa hina mene oboniro, mazaḡa ani madaḡaniꞌa ꞌize mene feuriro.
\v 31 Rehano vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa boꞌaḡano vaze ḡehaḡaꞌe Iesu mazao fiadu reiro, “Kerisoꞌa aradu haḡai nu badeḡa haḡaine zuni, vaze ꞌadi mene ufeta vitine haḡaiꞌuma!”
\p 
\v 32 Farisea azaḡaꞌe vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa Iesu moneo ꞌouge gumude ḡoeriroteꞌe igiro. Eꞌanoꞌo dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu Farisea azaḡaniꞌa Iesu obone tihi radu kuru neḡa uti azaḡa tuḡuziro.
\v 33 ꞌOugadu Iesuꞌa ziro, “E zae teite mada tahiḡa daꞌo radadu eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe vazeḡa vaḡe onamiꞌuma.
\v 34 Za eḡe vaḡiꞌuma, rehano mene horohiꞌuma. Ebu zaꞌe eḡeꞌa radiuꞌeteꞌe habaꞌa onamogaꞌe mene idaḡa.”
\v 35 Ebu Iuda azaḡa ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe zeḡeꞌa bare ḡadimutitiro, “Ani noꞌe onamiꞌuma ꞌahine, eme ani mene horoniꞌuma raꞌohe? Ani Iuda azaḡaniꞌa radiuꞌeteꞌe Giriki azaḡa haba onamadu Giriki azaḡa ihoziꞌumahe?
\v 36 Aniꞌa ꞌahige raꞌohe, 'Za eḡe vaḡiꞌuma, rehano mene horohiꞌuma, ebu eḡeꞌa radiuꞌeteꞌe habaꞌa aroga zuni mene idaḡa.' Eꞌe hugaꞌe nagini?”
\s1 Ḡabone Vuḡa
\p 
\v 37 Mui ḡonaga madaḡaꞌe mada boro hune. Iesuꞌa edau iḡunadu vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa huze ziro, “Iniu iriga moꞌoneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe vaḡe aroꞌi ebu gagoꞌi.
\v 38 Buka Zaḡoḡano reiroteꞌe teige, iniu eḡe mazao fieꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡabone vuḡaniꞌa vu boro teige ane zamaḡanonoꞌo sore buaꞌuma.”
\v 39 Aneꞌa ḡabone vuḡa reirotaꞌaꞌe Vine Zaḡoḡa moneo rae radu iniu ani mazao fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe eꞌe hidiꞌuma rae reiro. Rehano eꞌe madaḡano Vine Zaḡoḡaꞌe ze ꞌize mene hidiro, mazaḡa Iesuꞌe ꞌize satauro rana mene rudanadu ani niꞌe mene mae ḡihiniro.
\p 
\v 40 Vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa ḡoere eꞌe igirotene, nuꞌe ꞌahige rae reiro, “Vaze ꞌadiꞌe hube hune peroveta vazeḡa. Aꞌe emeḡeꞌa guhineꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa.”
\v 41 U vaze nuꞌe raenaꞌa, “Aniꞌe Keriso,” ebu nuꞌe raenaꞌa, “Mene, Kerisoꞌe Galilea habaꞌanonoꞌo mene ariꞌuma.
\v 42 Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae reiro, 'Kerisoꞌe kini Davida mariganonoꞌo zu Davida ne Betelehemaonoꞌo ariꞌuma.'\x + \xo 7:42 \xt Mika 5:2\x*”
\v 43 Eꞌanoꞌo vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaꞌe Iesu uꞌano aꞌadaro.
\v 44 Vaze nuꞌe ani obone tihi reiro, rehano vazeni ꞌahoganiꞌa ani rana ꞌevore mene tiro.
\s1 Vaze Boroboroꞌa Iesu mazao Mene Firo
\p 
\v 45 Ebu kuru neḡa uti azaḡaniꞌa dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu Farisea azaḡa vaḡe bare onamiro. Ebu zeꞌa uti azaḡa ḡadiziro, “Za nougadu ani mene obone teadu tutune areha?”
\v 46 Zeḡeꞌa naenaeziro, “Vaze ꞌadi teige ḡoere manoḡa ḡoeriroteꞌe vazaḡaꞌe oꞌoꞌa!”
\v 47 Farisea azaḡaniꞌa ziro, “Zae zuni aniꞌa soꞌozahe?
\v 48 Vaze ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ga Farisea azaḡa boꞌaḡano ani mazao fieꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahoga eꞌehe? Mene!
\v 49 Vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa ꞌahiꞌe Mose goro ḡoeꞌa aḡuꞌa ꞌahine, ani mazao fieꞌohe. Eꞌanoꞌo ze radiu tuḡutuḡu adugaḡa hidiꞌuma!”
\p 
\v 50 Ibite Iesu vaḡe onamiroteꞌe vazeḡa, Nikodemo zuni Iuda azaḡa ibitoziꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahoga. Aniꞌa ḡadiziro,
\v 51 “Emeḡe goro idunaḡano, emeꞌe vaze ḡoere egadu aniꞌa nagini haḡaeꞌeteꞌe ꞌizema ederogano aniꞌe veꞌoḡa rae mene raꞌohe.”
\v 52 ꞌOugadu zeḡeꞌa naenaeniro, “Ḡae zuni Galilea vazeḡahe? Buka Zaḡoḡa bare meꞌodoꞌi, ꞌougine peroveta vazeḡani ꞌahoga Galilea habaꞌano mene fureruꞌetaꞌaꞌe ederiꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 53 Ebu ze zeḡezeḡe ne oname ḡouriro.
\c 8
\s1 Ubuma Ḡezo Roḡaeḡa
\p 
\v 1 Ebu Iesuꞌa Olivi Maḡa onamiro.
\v 2 Irarirotene, oherebau uzeuze ani kuru neḡa habaꞌa onamiro. Ebu vaze niduꞌa ani vaḡe onamirotene, ani ehoradu ihoziro.
\v 3 Ebu Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu Farisea azaḡaniꞌa ubuma ḡezo roḡaeḡa ꞌahoga obone teadu vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa zamao ohone tiro.
\v 4 Ebu ze Iesu niro, “Ihore vazeḡa, roḡae ꞌadaꞌa ubuma ḡezo haḡaeꞌeteꞌe emeḡeꞌa horonadu obone teha.
\v 5 Mose goro ḡoeꞌano Moseꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro, ꞌRoḡae ꞌuguḡaꞌe hadi hina mau runoꞌi.' Ḡaꞌe nouge rae zamareꞌohe?”
\v 6 Ze ani tuhune nurihi radu ꞌouge rae ḡadimaro, mazaḡa aniꞌa veꞌore naenaezine ani kotao mae ohonihi reiro.
\p Rehano Iesuꞌa ḡuḡuradu ꞌevoꞌa hina rahao mirihiro.
\v 7 Ze Iesu barebare ḡadinirotene, aniꞌa iḡune edanadu ziro, “Zae boꞌaḡano iniu mazao haḡai sauꞌa oꞌoꞌa vazeḡaniꞌa ibite geno hadi hina ani mau bohinoꞌi.”
\v 8 Ebu ani bare ḡuḡuradu ꞌevoꞌa hina rahao mirihiro.
\v 9 Ze Iesu ḡoere igirotene, ze tibatiba iḡune ḡouriro. Vaze boroboroꞌa ibitiro ebu komeꞌakomeꞌaꞌe vesuꞌu iḡuniro. Ebu Iesu ane daꞌo roḡae edauꞌeteꞌe teite eꞌea radiro.
\v 10 Ebu Iesuꞌa bare iḡune edanadu roḡae eꞌe ḡadiniro, “Roḡae, ze noumao? Ḡaꞌe veꞌoḡa rae raꞌeteꞌe vazeḡani ꞌahogaꞌe oꞌoꞌahe?”
\v 11 Aneꞌa naenaeniro, “Vazeni ꞌahoga oꞌoꞌa, vaze boro.” Iesuꞌa niro, “Eḡe zuni ḡaꞌe veꞌoḡa rae mene raꞌohe. Onamoꞌi, ebu izidionoꞌo zama moneo haḡai sauꞌa ago bare haḡaoꞌi.”
\s1 Iesuꞌe Raha ꞌAdi Agaḡa
\p 
\v 12 Iesuꞌa bare ḡoeriro, “Eꞌe raha ꞌadi agaḡa. Iniu eḡe hegoteꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe uzabo zamaḡano mene hune ragaviꞌuma, rehano ḡabone hideꞌeteꞌe agaḡa meꞌuma.”
\v 13 Farisea azaḡaniꞌa niro, “Ḡa ḡaeꞌa bare ḡae moneo rae fureneꞌohe. Aꞌe huga oꞌoꞌa!”
\v 14 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “E eḡeꞌa bare eḡe moneo rae fureneꞌohe, rehano eḡe ḡoereꞌe huga, mazaḡa e noumanoꞌo ariroteꞌe zu noꞌe onamitaꞌaꞌe edeḡa. U zaꞌe eḡeꞌa noumanoꞌo ariroteꞌe zu noꞌe onamitaꞌaꞌe aḡuꞌa.
\v 15 Za raha azaḡa zamarone idunaḡano iniuꞌe duduḡa ga veꞌoḡa rae raꞌohe. Rehano e vaze ꞌahoga mazao duduḡa ga veꞌoḡa rae mene raꞌohe.
\v 16 Rehano eḡeꞌa vaze mazao duduḡa ga veꞌoḡa rae reine zuni, aꞌe duduga, mazaḡa mene eḡe daꞌo, rehano eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe Mamaheꞌa eḡe teite radiuꞌohe.
\v 17 Zae goro ḡoeꞌano ꞌahige rae mirihiro, 'Vaze aheuꞌe ḡoere tiba reine, aꞌe hube.'\x + \xo 8:17 \xt Goro 17:6\x*
\v 18 E eḡeꞌa bare eḡe moneo rae fureneꞌohe, ebu eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe Mamahe zuni eḡe moneo rae fureneꞌohe.”
\p 
\v 19 Ebu zeḡeꞌa ḡadiniro, “ꞌOugadu mogoꞌe noumao?” Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Za eḡe zu Mamaꞌe aḡuꞌa. Zaeꞌa eḡe ederifone, eḡe Mama zuni ederifo.”
\v 20 Iesuꞌa kuru neḡa habaꞌano ḡahunone hadiḡa ufeꞌeteꞌe maḡuḡa uhiḡano ihozeꞌeteꞌea, ḡoere ꞌadi ziro. Rehano ani madaꞌe ꞌize mene feuriro ꞌahine, ze ani mene obone tiro.
\s1 Iesuꞌa Ane Rune moneo Ihoziro
\p 
\v 21 Iesuꞌa bare ziro, “Eꞌe oname dauḡiꞌuma, u zaꞌe eḡe vaḡiꞌuma, rehano za haḡaize sauꞌa zamaḡano rudaꞌuma. Ebu eḡeꞌa onamiteꞌe habaꞌaꞌe zaꞌa aroga mene idaḡa.”
\v 22 Iuda azaḡa boroboroꞌe zeḡeꞌa bare ḡadimutitiro, “Ani aneꞌa bare maꞌumahe? Mazaḡa aniꞌa onamiteꞌe habaꞌaꞌe emeḡeꞌa onamogaꞌe mene idaḡa rae raꞌohe.”
\v 23 Rehano Iesuꞌa ziro, “Zaꞌe ꞌuꞌuḡanonoꞌo ariro, u eꞌe hitanaonoꞌo ariro. Zaꞌe raha ꞌadi azaḡa, u eꞌe raha ꞌadi mene vazeḡa.
\v 24 Eꞌanoꞌo e zeha, 'Za haḡaize sauꞌa zamaḡano rudaꞌuma.' Za eḡeꞌa eḡe moneo iniu rae raꞌeteꞌe mene mae ḡihinine, za haḡaize sauꞌa zamaḡano rudaꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 25 Zeḡeꞌa ḡadiniro, “Tena ḡa iniu?” Iesuꞌa ziro, “E ḡadaheḡanonoꞌo eꞌe iniu rae ziꞌohe.
\v 26 E zae moneo zihi raꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌaꞌe ḡehaḡa ebu zaꞌe veꞌoḡa raꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa zuni ḡehaḡa. Rehano eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe huga radu e ani mazaonoꞌo igiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa daꞌo raha azaḡa ziꞌohe.”
\v 27 Rehano ze Iesuꞌa Moga moneo zirotaꞌaꞌe mene ederiro.
\v 28 Eꞌanoꞌo Iesuꞌa ziro, “Vaze Ubugaꞌe zaeꞌa satauro rana mae ḡihiniteꞌe madaḡano, za eḡeꞌa ziꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe rae ederiꞌuma. Ebu e eḡe edeḡano ḡau ꞌahoga mene haḡaeꞌeteꞌe, rehano Mamaꞌa ihohiroteꞌe ḡauḡa daꞌo ḡoereꞌetaꞌaꞌe ederiꞌuma.
\v 29 Eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe teite radiuꞌohe. Aniꞌe eḡe daꞌo mene mode tauḡiro, mazaḡa e iḡaiḡa aniꞌa matuꞌeꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa daꞌo haḡaeꞌohe.”
\v 30 Iesuꞌa ꞌouge reirotene, vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa ani mazao firo.
\s1 Aberahamo Mariga
\p 
\v 31 Ebu Iesuꞌa Iuda azaḡa ani mazao fieꞌeteꞌe ziro, “Za eḡe ihore hegotine, hube hune eḡe tahiꞌatahiꞌa reꞌuma.
\v 32 Ebu za ḡoere huga ederiꞌuma. Zaꞌe tuḡure azaḡa teigeꞌohe, rehano ḡoere huga eꞌeꞌa tuḡure azaḡanonoꞌo za bohaze buziꞌuma.”
\v 33 Zeḡeꞌa naenaeniro, “Emeꞌe Aberahamo mariga. Eme vaze ꞌahoga tuḡure azaḡa mene hune reiro. Ḡa nougadu emeꞌe tuḡure azaḡanonoꞌo bohafe bufiꞌuma raꞌohe?”
\p 
\v 34 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, iniu haḡai sauꞌa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe haḡai sauꞌa tuḡure vazeḡa raꞌohe.
\v 35 Ebu tuḡure vazeḡaꞌe ani teite ne tibano radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa teite iḡaiḡa mene radiuꞌohe. U ubugaꞌe ani teite ne tibano radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa teite iḡaiḡa radiuꞌohe onamo tuḡutuḡu.
\v 36 Eꞌanoꞌo Ubuganiꞌa za haḡaize sauꞌanonoꞌo bohaze buzine, zaꞌe hube hune haḡaize sauꞌanonoꞌo buau radiꞌuma.
\v 37 E edeḡa, zaꞌe Aberahamo mariga. Rehano eḡe ḡoereꞌe zae zamao oꞌoꞌa uꞌano, za eḡe uḡuhe ruhihi raꞌohe.
\v 38 E Mamaꞌa ihohiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa ziꞌohe. Rehano zaꞌe moze mazaonoꞌo igiroteꞌe haḡaeꞌohe.”
\p 
\v 39 Zeꞌa naenaeniro, “Aberahamoꞌe emeḡe mama.” Iesuꞌa ziro, “Zaꞌe Aberahamo ubugaubuga reifone, Aberahamoꞌa haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡa haḡaifo.
\v 40 Eꞌe Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo igiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa huga ziro, rehano za e uḡuhe ruhihi raꞌohe. Aberahamoꞌe mene ꞌougiro.
\v 41 Zaꞌe zae mozeꞌa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa haḡaeꞌohe.”
\p Ebu zeḡeꞌa niro, “Emeꞌe mene butu ega. Badiꞌa ane daꞌoꞌe emeḡe Mama.”
\v 42 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Badiꞌaꞌe Moze reifone, za e zamare borofifo, mazaḡa e Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo aradu izidi ꞌaha radiuꞌohe. E eḡeꞌa bare mene ariro, rehano aniꞌa tuḡuhadu ariro.
\v 43 Za nougadu eḡeꞌa raꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa mene edereꞌohe? Mazaḡa zaꞌe eḡe ḡoere egoga mene urateꞌohe.
\v 44 Mozeꞌe Diabolo, ebu zaꞌe moze ura haḡaihi raꞌohe. Aniꞌe ḡadaheḡanonoꞌo vaze maro zu hugano mene haḡaeꞌohe, mazaḡa ani zamaoꞌe huga oꞌoꞌa. Aniꞌa ḡurireꞌetaꞌaꞌe ane haḡai, mazaḡa aniꞌe ḡuriro vazeḡa, zu ḡuriro niduꞌaꞌe ani mazaonoꞌo fureruꞌohe.
\v 45 Eḡeꞌa ḡoere huga ziꞌe ꞌahine, za eḡe mazao mene fieꞌohe.
\v 46 Zae boꞌaḡano iniuꞌa eḡe mazao sauꞌa ꞌahoga horonadu eꞌe veꞌoḡa rae reꞌuma? E ḡoere huga raꞌohe, rehano nougadu zaꞌe eḡe mazao mene fieꞌohe?
\v 47 Iniu Badiꞌa mone vazeḡaꞌe Badiꞌa ḡoere igiꞌohe. Zaꞌe Badiꞌa ḡoere mene igiꞌohe, mazaḡa zaꞌe Badiꞌa mene mone azaḡa.”
\s1 Iesu zu Aberahamo
\p 
\v 48 Ebu Iuda azaḡa boroboroꞌa Iesu naenaeniro, “Ḡa Samaria vazeḡa teige veꞌore ḡoereꞌohe, zu vine sauꞌaniꞌa ḡae ragano reiro. Emeḡe ḡoere ꞌahiꞌe mene duduḡahe?”
\v 49 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “E mene vine sauꞌaheta, rehano Mamahe gubaneꞌohe. U zaꞌe e mene gubaheꞌohe.
\v 50 E vazeꞌa nihe mae ḡihinoga mene umizeꞌohe. Rehano vazeꞌa nihe mae ḡihinoga urateꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe teite radiuꞌohe, ebu aniꞌe kota vazeḡa.
\v 51 Rehano eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, iniuꞌa eḡe ḡoere hegotine, aniꞌe mene hune rudaꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 52 Iuda azaḡa boroboroꞌa niro, “Izidi eme edereha, ḡaꞌe vine sauꞌaḡota! Aberahamo zu peroveta azaḡa zuni rudaro, rehano ḡa raenaꞌa, 'Iniu eḡe ḡoere hegoteꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe mene hune rudaꞌuma,' rae raꞌohe.
\v 53 Ḡaꞌe emeḡe vouḡa Aberahamo ufeta vitinogahe? Aniꞌe rudaro ebu peroveta azaḡa zuni rudaro. Ḡa ḡaeꞌa bare iniu rae zamareꞌohe?”
\v 54 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “E eḡeꞌa bare nihe mae ḡihinine, aꞌe huga oꞌoꞌa. Nihe mae ḡihineꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe Mama. Aniꞌe zaeꞌa zae Badiꞌa rae huneꞌohe.
\v 55 Zaꞌe ani aḡuꞌa, u eꞌe ani edeḡa. E ani aḡuꞌa rae reifone, e zae teige ḡuriro vazeḡa reifo. Rehano e ani edeḡa zu ani ḡoere hegoteꞌohe.
\v 56 Zae vouḡa Aberahamoꞌe e raha ꞌada areꞌeteꞌe madaḡa horoniꞌuma rae zamaradu matuꞌe rudaro. Ebu aniꞌe eꞌe madaḡa horonadu matuꞌiro.”
\v 57 Iuda azaḡa boroboroꞌa niro, “Ḡa muriḡo 50 ꞌize mene maha. Nougenouge hena Aberahamo horoniro?”
\v 58 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, Aberahamoꞌe ꞌizema fureranogano, eꞌe radiro.”
\v 59 Eꞌebone ze hadi mae ḡihinadu Iesu mau runihi reiro. Rehano ani kuru neḡa habaꞌanonoꞌo ꞌuꞌuru buanadu dauḡiro.
\c 9
\s1 Ubuma Kuruḡa Vazeḡa Fainiro
\p 
\v 1 Iesuꞌa onamiroteꞌea, fureraroteꞌe madaḡanonoꞌo ubuma kuruḡa vazeḡa ꞌahoga horoniro.
\v 2 Ebu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa ḡadiniro, “Rabi, aniꞌa ubumaḡa kuruḡano furerarotaꞌaꞌe ane haḡai sauꞌa uꞌano ga viꞌa moga haḡai sauꞌa uꞌano?”
\v 3 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Aꞌe ani mene haḡai sauꞌa ga viꞌa moga haḡai sauꞌa uꞌano, rehano ani ḡabone zamaḡano Badiꞌaꞌa nougenouge gaueꞌeteꞌe vaze ihozoga veize ani ubumaḡa kuruḡano fureraro.
\v 4 Madaꞌa agaruꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano emeḡeꞌa eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe vazeḡa gau haḡaiꞌuma. Ohereꞌa arine, vazeni ꞌahogaꞌe gauoga mene idaḡa.
\v 5 E ꞌize raha ꞌada radiuꞌeteꞌe zamaḡanoꞌe eꞌe raha ꞌadi agaḡa.”
\p 
\v 6 Iesuꞌa ꞌouge reiroteꞌe enogano aneꞌa rahao soꞌabidiro, ebu soꞌareḡa hina taḡora haḡadu vaze eꞌe ubuma rana ase ḡuzuhiro.
\v 7 Ebu aniꞌa niro, “Siloami duꞌura komeꞌa onamadu vuzuꞌoꞌi.” (Siloami hugaꞌe Tuḡuniro.) Ebu vaze eꞌeꞌa onamadu eꞌe vuḡano vuzuꞌirotene, ubumaḡaniꞌa raꞌanadu bare ariro.
\p 
\v 8 ꞌOugadu ane nabudi zu aneꞌa umididoteꞌe ibite horoniroteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ḡadimutitiro, “Vaze ꞌadiꞌe ehoradu umide banidoteꞌe vazeḡa, oꞌehe?”
\v 9 Vaze nuꞌe raenaꞌa, “Oꞌe, aniꞌe vaze eꞌe,” u nuꞌe raenaꞌa, “Mene, ꞌadiꞌe ani heuḡa,” rae reiro. Rehano ani aneꞌa bare ꞌahige rae reiro, “Oꞌe, vaze aꞌe eḡe.”
\v 10 Zeḡeꞌa ḡadiniro, “Ubumaḡo nougenouge raꞌaneha?”
\v 11 Aniꞌa naenaeziro, “Iesu rae huneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa taḡora haḡadu ubumahe rana ase ḡuzuheha. Ebu aniꞌa, 'Siloami duꞌura komeꞌa onamadu vuzuꞌoꞌi,' rae eheha. Eꞌanoꞌo e onamadu eꞌea vuzuꞌeha ebu ehamanogaꞌe idaraneha.”
\v 12 Zeḡeꞌa ḡadiniro, “Vaze aꞌe noumao?” Aneꞌa ziro, “E aḡuꞌa.”
\s1 Farisea Azaḡaꞌe Ubuma Kuruḡa Vazeḡaniꞌa Manoriroteꞌe moneo Udahiro
\p 
\v 13 Ebu ze ibite ubuma kuruḡa reiroteꞌe vazeḡa zamahanadu Farisea azaḡa vaḡe onamiro.
\v 14 Iesuꞌa taḡora haḡadu vaze eꞌe ubuma fainiroteꞌe madaḡaꞌe Bana Madaḡa.
\v 15 Eꞌanoꞌo Farisea azaḡaniꞌa zu ḡadiniro, “Ḡa nougenouge ehamanogaꞌe idaraneha?” Aniꞌa naenaeziro, “Aneꞌa taḡora haḡadu ubumahe rana ase ḡuzuheha. Ebu e vuzuꞌadu izidi ehamuꞌohe.”
\p 
\v 16 Ebu Farisea azaḡa nuꞌa reiro, “Vaze aꞌe mene Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo ariroteꞌe vazeḡa, mazaḡa ani Bana Madaḡa goro ḡoeꞌa mene hegoteꞌohe.” U nuꞌe reiro, “Aniꞌe haḡai sauꞌa vazeḡa reine, haḡai nu badeḡa ꞌahiguḡa haḡaogaꞌe mene idaḡa.” ꞌOugadu ze zeḡeꞌa bare rovotiro.
\v 17 Eꞌanoꞌo ze ubuma kuruḡa reiroteꞌe vazeḡa bare ḡadiniro, “Ani ubumaḡo faineha. Ḡaꞌe ani iniu rae zamareꞌohe?” Aniꞌa naenaeziro, “Aniꞌe peroveta vazeḡa.”
\p 
\v 18 Iuda azaḡa boroboroꞌa ani ibite ubuma kuruḡa reiroteꞌe zu izidi ehamanoga idararoteꞌe mene mae ḡihiniro. Eꞌanoꞌo ze ani viꞌa moga huze zouziro.
\v 19 Ebu zeḡeꞌa ḡadiziro, “ꞌAhiꞌe zae ubudehe? Aniꞌe hube ubumaḡa kuruḡano furerarohe? Ani nougadu izidiꞌe hena ehamuꞌohe?”
\v 20 Viꞌa moganiꞌa naenaeziro, “Oꞌe, aniꞌe emeḡe ubude, ebu ani ubuma kuruḡano furerarotaꞌaꞌe emeꞌe edeḡa.
\v 21 Rehano eme aḡuꞌa, ani nougenouge izidi ehamuꞌohe zu iniuꞌa ubumaḡa faineha. Nugo ḡadinoꞌi. Ani vaze boro ꞌahine, aneꞌa bare ḡoeriꞌuma.”
\v 22 Ani viꞌa moganiꞌa Iuda azaḡa boroboro rihoziroteꞌe uꞌano, ꞌouge reiro. Mazaḡa zeḡeꞌa raenaꞌa, “Iniuꞌa Iesuꞌe Keriso rae reine, ani nu'onu'o neḡanonoꞌo mae vaḡiniꞌuma,” rae ziro.
\v 23 Eꞌanoꞌo viꞌa moganiꞌa, “Aniꞌe vaze boro, eꞌanoꞌo ani ḡadinoꞌi,” rae reiro.
\p 
\v 24 Mada aheuḡano ze ibite ubuma kuruḡa reiroteꞌe vazeḡa hunadu niro, “Badiꞌa ubumao huga ḡoeroꞌi.\f + \fr 9:24 \fqa Badiꞌa ni mae ḡihinoꞌi. \f* Emeꞌe edeḡa, Iesuꞌe haḡai sauꞌa vazeḡa.”
\v 25 Aneꞌa naenaeziro, “E aḡuꞌa, aniꞌe haḡai sauꞌa vazeḡa ga mene, rehano e ḡau tibaꞌe edeḡa. Ibite e ubuma kuruḡa vazeḡa, rehano izidi ehamuꞌohe.”
\v 26 Zeḡeꞌa ḡadiniro, “Ani ḡa mazao nagini haḡaeha? Nougenouge faiꞌadu ubumaḡo raꞌaneha?”
\v 27 Aniꞌa naenaeziro, “E amahi zeha, rehano za mene egeha. Nougadu eḡe ḡoere bare igihi raꞌohe? Zae zuni ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa reihi raꞌehe?”
\p 
\v 28 ꞌOugadu ze ani rae sausauniro ebu niro, “Ḡaꞌe ane tahiꞌa, u emeꞌe Mose tahiꞌatahiꞌa!
\v 29 Eme Badiꞌaꞌa Mose ḡorenirotaꞌaꞌe edeḡa, rehano eme vaze aꞌe noumanoꞌo arirotaꞌaꞌe aḡuꞌa.”
\v 30 Vaze eꞌeꞌa naenaeziro, “E zaguzagauꞌohe! Aniꞌa ubumahe manoneha, rehano za ani noumanoꞌo arirotaꞌaꞌe aḡuꞌa!
\v 31 Emeꞌe edeḡa, Badiꞌaꞌe haḡai sauꞌa azaḡa ḡoereꞌe mene igiꞌohe, rehano iniu ane mazao kurauꞌeteꞌe zu ane urao haḡaeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ḡoereꞌe igiꞌohe.
\v 32 Badiꞌaꞌa raha ꞌadi haḡairoteꞌe madaḡanonoꞌo onao izidi, ubuma kuruḡano fureraroteꞌe vazeḡa fainiroteꞌe hariḡa vazeni ꞌahoga mene igiro.
\v 33 Vaze ꞌadiꞌe mene Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo reifone, ani ḡau ꞌahoga haḡaoga mene idaḡa reifo.”
\v 34 Zeḡeꞌa naenaeniro, “Ḡaꞌe fureraroteꞌe madaḡanonoꞌo haḡai sauꞌaniꞌa iriꞌaveꞌohe. Ḡaeꞌa eme ihofihi raꞌehe?” Ebu ze ani hegone buniro.
\s1 Vine moneo Ubuma Kuruḡa Azaḡa
\p 
\v 35 Iesuꞌa ze ubuma kuruḡa vazeḡa eꞌe hegone buniroteꞌe igiro. Eꞌanoꞌo ani vaḡadu hidirotene ḡadiniro, “Ḡa Vaze Ubuga mazao fieꞌehe?”
\v 36 Vaze eꞌeꞌa naenaeniro, “Vaze boro, aniꞌe iniu? Ḡa ihine, e ani mazao fiꞌuma.”
\v 37 Iesuꞌa niro, “Ḡaꞌa ani horoneha zu ani izidi ḡae teite ḡoereꞌohe.”
\v 38 Vaze eꞌeꞌa niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, e ḡae mazao fieꞌohe!” Ebu aneꞌa ḡuḡuradu ani mazao kuraro.
\v 39 Iesuꞌa niro, “Eḡeꞌa kotazoga veize raha ꞌadi ariro. Aꞌe ubuma kuruḡa azaḡaniꞌa ehamanoga veize, zu ehamuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ubumaꞌa kuranoga veize raꞌohe.”
\v 40 Ebu Iesu teite radiroteꞌe Farisea azaḡa nuꞌe ani ḡoere egadu niro, “Emeꞌe mene ubuma kuruḡa azaḡa!”
\v 41 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Za hube hune ubuma kuruḡa azaḡa reifone, Badiꞌaꞌa haḡaize sauꞌa rae modifo. Rehano zaꞌe ehamuꞌohe rae raꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, haḡaize sauꞌaꞌe mene rae modeꞌohe.”
\c 10
\s1 Mamoe Taufeꞌeteꞌe Vazeḡa Manoḡa
\p 
\v 1 Iesuꞌa reiro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, iniu ḡabiri ibihetaḡanonoꞌo mamoe habaꞌa mene diuḡadu ibi ꞌahogano sibire diuḡeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡonore vazeḡa.
\v 2 U ḡabiri ibihetaḡanonoꞌo diuḡeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe mamoe taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa.
\v 3 Ḡabiri ibihetaḡa taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa ani veize ibiheta vavaꞌohauꞌohe zu mamoeḡaꞌe ane ago igiꞌohe. Ebu aniꞌa mamoeḡa nizeo huzadu ibitozi buzeꞌohe.
\v 4 Huze buzatene aneꞌa ibitadu zeḡe niduꞌa ani hegoteꞌohe, mazaḡa ze ani agoꞌe edeḡa.
\v 5 Zeꞌe aḡuꞌa vazeḡa ḡaruna mene hegotiꞌuma zu ani mazaonoꞌo feraꞌuma, mazaḡa zeꞌe aḡuꞌa vazeḡa agoꞌe aḡuꞌa.”
\v 6 Iesuꞌa ḡoere ꞌouge rae idane ziro, rehano ze aniꞌa ziroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa huga mene ederiro.
\p 
\v 7 Eꞌanoꞌo Iesuꞌa bare ziro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, e mamoe ḡabiri ibihetaḡa.
\v 8 Eḡe zamao ibite ariroteꞌe azaḡaꞌe ḡonore azaḡa. Rehano mamoeꞌe zeḡe ḡoere mene egoziniro.
\v 9 Eꞌe ibiheta. Iniuꞌa eḡe mazaonoꞌo diuḡine, aniꞌe ḡabone hidiꞌuma. Ebu aniꞌe buau diuḡiꞌuma zu ogomu manoḡa hidiꞌuma.
\v 10 Ḡonore vazeḡaꞌe ḡonotafine zu zimifine ebu ruizifine areꞌohe. U eꞌe mamoe niduꞌa ḡabone hidadu zeḡe ḡabone niduꞌa zamaḡano manoḡaniꞌa iriꞌavoga veize ariro. \fig Mamoe ibihetaḡa|src="lb00014b.tif" size="col" ref="10:7-9"\fig*
\p 
\v 11 Eꞌe mamoe taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa manoḡa. Mamoe taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa manoḡaꞌe mamoeḡa uꞌano ḡaboneḡa aheteꞌohe.
\v 12 U hadi vaḡeꞌenaꞌa, gaueꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe mamoe mene taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa. Mamoeꞌe mene ani mamoe. Eꞌanoꞌo ani butu ḡuniḡaniꞌa aroga horoneꞌetene, mamoe niduꞌa mode ferauꞌohe. Ebu butu ḡuniḡaniꞌa mamoe agatozenadu niduꞌa avoavo oname ḡoureꞌohe.
\v 13 Aniꞌe hadi vaḡe gaueꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa radu mamoe mene faine taufeꞌe ꞌahine, ferauꞌohe.
\p 
\v 14 Eꞌe mamoe taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa manoḡa. Eꞌe mamoehe edeḡa zu zeꞌe e edeḡa.
\v 15 Aꞌe Mamaꞌa e edeḡa zu eꞌe Mama edeḡa heuḡa. E ḡabonehe mamoe veize aheteꞌohe.
\v 16 Mamoe ꞌahoga nuꞌe eḡe mazao, rehano zeꞌe ḡabiri ꞌahi zamaḡanoꞌe oꞌoꞌa. Zeḡe zuni eḡeꞌa zamaze ariꞌuma. Ze eḡe ḡoere igiꞌuma, ebu zeḡe niduꞌa tiburu radiꞌuma, zu vaze tibaniꞌa zeḡe taufiꞌuma.
\v 17 Mamaheꞌe eḡe zamare borofeꞌohe, mazaḡa e ḡabonehe bare meifine ḡabonehe aheteꞌohe.
\v 18 Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa eḡe ḡabone mene mae vaḡineꞌohe, rehano e eḡeꞌa bare ḡabonehe aheteꞌohe. E ḡabonehe aheteꞌeteꞌe zu bare maꞌeteꞌe gigiꞌaḡa meiro. Aꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa eḡe mazao, 'Haḡae hunoꞌi,' rae reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa.”
\p 
\v 19 Iesuꞌa ꞌouge reiroteꞌe uꞌano, Iuda azaḡaniꞌa zeḡe boꞌaḡano bare rovotiro.
\v 20 Zeḡe boꞌaḡano vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro, “Ani vine sauꞌaniꞌa ragano radu zamaroneḡaꞌe oꞌoꞌa. Za nougadu ani ḡoere igiꞌohe?”
\v 21 Rehano vaze nuꞌe ꞌahige rae reiro, “Ḡoere ꞌahiꞌe mene vine sauꞌaniꞌa ragano reiroteꞌe vazeḡa ḡoeꞌa. Vine sauꞌaniꞌa ubuma kuruḡa vazeḡa fainogaꞌe mene idaḡa.”
\s1 Iuda Azaḡa Boroboroꞌa Iesu Hezahoharo
\p 
\v 22 Ierusalemao Kuru Neḡa Giginiroteꞌe Muiḡa meiro, zu eꞌe madaḡaꞌe nahune madaḡa.
\v 23 Ebu Iesuꞌa kuru neḡa habaꞌano Solomona Ibi Zauhaḡano ragavinu.
\v 24 Ebu Iuda azaḡa boroboroꞌa gabaḡeḡenadu ḡadiniro, “Ḡa naniꞌa ḡoere huga ifiꞌuma? Zamafeꞌe ufeta doudeꞌohe. Ḡa Keriso roꞌidene, ḡoere rae dehenofoꞌi.”
\p 
\v 25 Ebu Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “E ziro, rehano za eḡe ḡoereꞌe mene mae ḡihineꞌohe. E eḡe Mama niḡano haḡaeꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa gigiꞌaꞌa eḡe moneo rae fureneꞌohe.
\v 26 Rehano za eḡe mene mamoe ꞌahine, eḡe mazao mene fieꞌohe.
\v 27 Eḡe mamoeꞌe agohe igiꞌohe. E ze edeḡa ebu ze e hegoteꞌohe.
\v 28 Eḡeꞌa ḡabone tuḡutuḡu zeḡe ziniꞌohe. Ze mene hune ruiziꞌuma ebu vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa eḡe ꞌevoreonoꞌo mene meiziꞌuma.
\v 29 Mamaheꞌa ze eḡe iniro. Aniꞌe ḡau niduꞌa ufeta vitine ḡihiꞌaḡa. Vazeni ꞌahoganiꞌa ze Mamahe ꞌevore mazaonoꞌo meizoga mene idaḡa.
\v 30 Eꞌe Mama teite tiba.”
\p 
\v 31 Ebu Iuda azaḡa boroboroꞌa bare hadi mae ḡihinadu matihi reiro.
\v 32 Rehano Iesuꞌa ziro, “E Mama gigiꞌaḡa hina haḡai manoḡa ḡehaḡa haḡadu ihoziro. Haḡai manoḡa eꞌe boꞌaḡano noꞌe haḡaiḡa uꞌano, za uḡuhe ruhihi raꞌohe?”
\v 33 Zeḡeꞌa naenaeniro, “Eme hadi hina ḡamihi raꞌetaꞌaꞌe mazaḡa mene ḡaeꞌa haḡai manoḡa haḡairo, rehano mazaḡa ḡa Badiꞌa rae sausauneꞌohe. Ḡaꞌe vaze tauḡi, rehano ḡa ḡaeꞌa bare Badiꞌa rae raꞌohe.”
\p 
\v 34 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Zae Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro, 'Badiꞌaꞌa raenaꞌa, “Zaꞌe badiꞌa.”'\x + \xo 10:34 \xt Salamo 82:6 \x*
\v 35 Badiꞌaꞌe ane ḡoere ziniroteꞌe azaḡa mazao, 'badiꞌa,' rae huziro. Ebu Buka Zaḡoḡaꞌe varadoga mene idaḡa.
\v 36 Eꞌe Mamaꞌa mae zaḡozaḡohadu raha ꞌahao tuḡuhiroteꞌe vazeḡa. E eḡeꞌa bare Badiꞌa Ubuga rae raꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, za eꞌa Badiꞌa rae sausauneꞌohe rae raꞌehe?
\v 37 E Mamahe gau mene haḡaoꞌidene, za eḡe mazao ago fioꞌi.
\v 38 U e Mamahe gau haḡaoꞌidene, za eḡe ḡoere mene mae ḡihineꞌe rehano, eḡeꞌa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa mae ḡihinoꞌi. ꞌOugine, Mamaꞌe eḡe teite zu eꞌe ane teite radiuꞌetaꞌaꞌe ederiꞌuma zu zamariꞌuma.”
\v 39 ꞌOugadu ze ani bare obone nuriro, rehano ani zeḡe ꞌevoreonoꞌo feraro.
\p 
\v 40 Ebu Iesuꞌa Ioridana duꞌura bare fare onamiro. Aꞌe Ioaneꞌa ibite vaze babatisozinuteꞌe habaꞌa. Iesuꞌe eꞌea radiro.
\v 41 Vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa ani vaḡe ariro ebu zeḡeꞌa bare ꞌahige rae reiro, “Ioaneꞌe haḡai nu badeḡa mene haḡairo, rehano aneꞌa vaze ꞌadi moneo reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa niduꞌaꞌe hube.”
\v 42 Ebu eꞌea vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa Iesu mazao firo.
\c 11
\s1 Lazaro Rune
\p 
\v 1 Vaze ꞌahoga, niḡa Lazaroꞌa radiunu. Ani uginiro ebu ezeḡa aheu, Maria zu Mareta teite Betania neḡano radiunu.
\v 2 Mariaꞌe Zuhiꞌa Boro oda rana dehoro hohoḡa manoḡa beꞌunadu iguḡa hina odaḡa zauhiroteꞌe roḡaeḡa. Ani ezeḡa Lazaroꞌe uginiro.
\v 3 Eꞌanoꞌo ezeḡa aheuꞌa vaze ꞌahoga Iesu vaḡe tuḡunadu niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, ḡaeꞌa zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ugiḡa.”
\v 4 Iesuꞌa hari eꞌe egadu ꞌahige rae reiro, “Ugiḡa eꞌe uꞌano, ani mene rudaꞌuma, rehano Badiꞌa ni mae ḡihinoga veize ꞌahiguḡaniꞌa fureraro. Ugi eꞌe uꞌano, Badiꞌa Ubuga ni mae ḡihiniꞌuma.”
\v 5 Iesuꞌe Mareta, negoḡa Maria zu ezeḡa Lazaro zamare borofiro.
\v 6 Rehano ani Lazaroꞌa uginiroteꞌe hariḡa igirotene, ani aneꞌa radiuꞌeteꞌe habaꞌano mada aheu bare radiro.
\p 
\v 7 Eꞌe enogano Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ziro, “Aroꞌi, Iudea habaꞌa bare onamihi.”
\v 8 Zeḡeꞌa niro, “Rabi, izidi Iuda azaḡa ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa hadi hina ḡamihi raha. Rehano ḡa eꞌe habaꞌa bare onamihi raꞌehe?”
\v 9 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Oꞌe. Mada tiba zamaḡano agaḡa madaḡa niduꞌaꞌe gaubanana aheu fare. Vazeꞌa agaḡa madaḡano ragavine mene uitiꞌuma, mazaḡa raha ꞌadi agazeꞌeteꞌe agaḡa horoneꞌohe.
\v 10 U ohore zamaḡano ragavine, ze uitiꞌuma, mazaḡa zeḡe mazao agaḡaꞌe oꞌoꞌa.”
\p 
\v 11 Aniꞌa ꞌouge reiroteꞌe enogano, bare ziro, “Emeḡe nabudi Lazaroꞌe bazeꞌohe. Rehano e ani vaḡe onamadu evaniꞌuma.”
\v 12 Ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa naenaeniro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, ani bazeꞌohe reine, ani manoriꞌuma.”
\v 13 Iesuꞌa Lazaro rune moneo ḡoeriro, rehano ze Iesu ḡoere egadu, “Lazaroꞌe huga bazeꞌohe,” rae zamariro.
\v 14 Eꞌanoꞌo Iesuꞌa dehene ziro, “Lazaroꞌe rudaneha.
\v 15 E ani teite mene radiroteꞌe uꞌano, matuꞌeꞌohe. Aꞌe zae veize raꞌohe, mazaḡa eꞌe uꞌano, za eḡe mazao fiꞌuma. Rehano izidi eme ani vaḡe onamihi.”
\v 16 Ebu Atoa\f + \fr 11:16 \fqa Didumo \f* rae huneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa, Tomasiꞌa Iesu tahiꞌa niduꞌa ziro, “Aroꞌi, emeḡe zuni ani teite rudafine onamihi.”
\s1 Iesuꞌe Ḡabone ebu Vaze Bare Ḡabozeꞌohe
\p 
\v 17 Iesuꞌa Betania neḡano hanitirotene, Lazaroꞌe amahi idu zamaḡano mada ḡazaḡa radiroteꞌe igiro.
\v 18 Betania neḡaꞌe Ierusalema uhiḡano, zu faḡaꞌe uḡidu kilomita mene vitinoga.
\v 19 Eꞌanoꞌo Iuda azaḡa ḡehaḡaniꞌa Mareta zu Maria vaḡe ariro, mazaḡa ezeze rune uꞌano zamaze namizihi reiro.
\p 
\v 20 Maretaꞌe Iesuꞌa areꞌeteꞌe igirotene, Iesu hidoga radu onamiro, u Mariaꞌe neo radiro.
\v 21 Ebu Maretaꞌa Iesu hidadu niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, ḡa ꞌaha reifone, ezeheꞌe mene rudafo.
\v 22 Rehano e edeḡa, izidi zuni ḡa Badiꞌa mazao nagini umidine aneꞌa ḡaniꞌuma.”
\v 23 Iesuꞌa niro, “Ezeḡoꞌe bare ḡabodiꞌuma.”
\v 24 Maretaꞌa niro, “E edeḡa, mada ḡonagano vaze niduꞌa runeonoꞌo bare iḡuneꞌeteꞌe madaḡano aniꞌe bare ḡabodiꞌuma.”
\v 25 Iesuꞌa niro, “Eꞌe rune azaḡa bare ḡabozeꞌohe, zu ḡabone ziniꞌohe. Iniu eḡe mazao fieꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe rudaune zuni, bare ḡabodiꞌuma.
\v 26 Ebu iniu ḡabodeꞌeteꞌe zu eḡe mazao fieꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe mene hune rudaꞌuma. Ḡa ḡoere ꞌahi mae ḡihineꞌehe?”
\v 27 Aneꞌa niro, “Oꞌe, Zuhiꞌa Boro, e ḡaꞌe Keriso ebu raha ꞌada ariꞌuma rae reiroteꞌe vazeḡa, Badiꞌa Ubuga rae mae ḡihineꞌohe.”
\p 
\v 28 Maretaꞌe ꞌouge reiroteꞌe enogano bare ne onamadu negoḡa Maria genaḡa zamahu onamiro ebu niro, “Ihore vazeḡaꞌe emeḡe haba haniteha. Aniꞌe ḡa ḡiaꞌihi raꞌohe.”
\v 29 Mariaꞌa ani ḡoere igirotene, ḡarihe iḡunadu Iesu vaḡe onamiro.
\v 30 Iesuꞌe ꞌize zeḡe ne mene diuḡadu Maretaꞌa ani hidiroteꞌe habaꞌano radiunu.
\v 31 Ne zamaḡano Maria namine radiuꞌeteꞌe Iuda azaḡaꞌe aneꞌa ḡarihe iḡunadu bua onamoga horoniro. Ebu zeḡe zuni ani hegote buaro, mazaḡa ze aniꞌa nianoga veize Lazaro idu onameꞌohe rae zamariro.
\p 
\v 32 Mariaꞌe Iesuꞌa radiuꞌeteꞌe habaꞌano feuradu ani horoniro. Ebu Iesu oda babaḡano ḡuḡuradu niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, ḡaꞌe ꞌaha reifone, eḡe ezeꞌe mene rudafo.”
\v 33 Iesuꞌa Maria zu ane teite ariroteꞌe Iuda azaḡaniꞌa niauꞌeteꞌe horonirotene, zamaḡa ariro zu adudaro.
\v 34 Ebu Iesuꞌa ḡadiziro, “Za Lazaro ahiꞌa nouma tiro?” Ze naenaeniro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, aradu ḡianoꞌi.”
\v 35 Hena Iesuꞌa niaro.
\v 36 ꞌOugadu Iuda azaḡaniꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro, “Ḡianoꞌi, ani Lazaro ufeta zamare borofiro!”
\v 37 Rehano zeḡe boꞌaḡano nuꞌe ꞌahige reiro, “Aniꞌe ubuma kuruḡa vazeḡa ubuma raꞌaniro. Rehano Lazaroꞌa mene rudafine ḡau ꞌahoga haḡaogaꞌe mene idararohe?”
\s1 Lazaro Bare Ḡaboniro
\p 
\v 38 Iesu zamaꞌe bare borofe areꞌenaꞌa, Lazaro idu onamiro. Iduḡaꞌe hoꞌoga boro zu ibihetaꞌe hadi boro ꞌahoga hina ꞌuiro.
\v 39 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Hadi ꞌahi mae vaḡinoꞌi.” ꞌOugirotene rune vazeḡa ezeḡa, Maretaꞌa niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, ani ahiriꞌe mada ḡazaḡa idu zamaḡano radeha, eꞌanoꞌo aniꞌe ufeta ḡezoḡa.”
\v 40 Iesuꞌa niro, “E ꞌahige ḡaha, 'Ḡa eḡe mazao fine, Badiꞌaꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune rae ederiꞌuma.'”
\p 
\v 41 ꞌOugadu ze hadi mae vaḡiniro. Ebu Iesuꞌa adure ḡohani ḡianadu reiro, “Mama, e ḡae mazao manoḡa tauḡi raꞌohe, mazaḡa ḡaeꞌa eḡe ḡoere abitoneha.
\v 42 E edeḡa, ḡa iḡaiḡa eḡe ḡoere abitoniꞌohe. Rehano ꞌada edauꞌeteꞌe azaḡa veize e ꞌahige raꞌohe. Ze ḡaꞌa e tuḡuhirotaꞌaꞌe mae ḡihinoga urateꞌohe.”
\v 43 Aneꞌa ꞌouge reiroteꞌe enogano ḡihau huaro, “Lazaro, bua aroꞌi!”
\v 44 Ebu rune vazeḡa ꞌai bua ariro! ꞌEvoꞌa zu odaḡa ꞌumiroteꞌe dabuaḡa kuiḡa ebu iraḡa ꞌumiroteꞌe dabuaḡaꞌe ꞌize ahiꞌano buaro. Iesuꞌa ziro, “Ani ragavifine dabuaḡa mae vaḡinoꞌi.” \fig Iesuꞌa Lazaro bare ḡaboniro|src="DN00459b.tif" size="col" ref="11:43-44"\fig*
\s1 Iesu Manoga veize Ḡoꞌaniro
\r (Mataio 26:1-5; Mareko 14:1-2; Luka 22:1-2)
\p 
\v 45 Ebu Maria vaḡe onamiroteꞌe Iuda azaḡa ḡehaḡaniꞌa Iesuꞌa nagini haḡairoteꞌe horonadu ani mazao firo.
\v 46 Rehano zeḡe boꞌaḡano nuꞌe Farisea azaḡa vaḡe onamadu Iesuꞌa nagini haḡairoteꞌe meꞌodoziniro.
\v 47 ꞌOugadu dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu Farisea azaḡaniꞌa Iuda azaḡa boroboro huzadu nu'onu'o boro meiro, ebu ze zeḡeꞌa bare ḡadimutitiro, “Eme nougiꞌuma? Vaze ꞌadi haḡai nu badeḡa ḡehaḡa haḡaeꞌohe.
\v 48 Eme aniꞌa ꞌahige haḡaoga ḡiane modine, vaze niduꞌa ani mazao fiꞌuma. Ebu Roma azaḡaniꞌa aradu emeḡe haba\f + \fr 11:48 \fqa emeḡe kuru neḡa \f* zu emeḡe haba azaḡa ruiziꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 49 Ebu zeḡe boꞌaḡano vaze ꞌahoga, niḡa Kaiafaꞌe eꞌe muriḡano dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa reiro. Aneꞌa ziro, “Zaꞌe ḡauni ꞌahoga zuni mene edereꞌohe!
\v 50 Vaze niduꞌa veize vaze tibaniꞌa rudanogaꞌe ufeta manoḡa, ebu Roma azaḡaniꞌa Iuda azaḡa niduꞌa ruizogaꞌe ufeta sauꞌa. Za aꞌe mene zamareꞌehe?”
\v 51 Ani ane zamaroneonoꞌo mene ꞌouge reiro. Aniꞌe eꞌe muriḡano dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa uꞌano, Badiꞌaꞌa ihonadu Iesuꞌe Iuda azaḡa niduꞌa veize rudatiteꞌe aneꞌa rae fureniro.
\v 52 Aꞌe mene Iuda azaḡa veize daꞌo, rehano haba nunu avoavo radiuꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌa ubugaubuga nuꞌozadu tiburanoga veize rae fureniro.
\v 53 Eꞌanoꞌo eꞌe madaḡanonoꞌo ze Iesu manoga ibiḡa ḡoꞌaniro.
\v 54 Eꞌe uꞌano, Iesuꞌe Iuda azaḡa boꞌaḡano hunioꞌe mene ragavinu. Aniꞌe eꞌe habaꞌa modadu haba bohaꞌa uhiḡano ne ꞌahoga, Efaraima onamiro ebu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa teite deꞌea radiro.
\p 
\v 55 Ebu Iuda azaḡa Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡaniꞌa hanitirotene, vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa neḡaneḡanonoꞌo Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa ꞌizema mougano Ierusalema itiro. Mazaḡa ze ibite itadu Iuda azaḡa goro idunaḡano Badiꞌa ubumao ze zeḡeꞌa bare dehezihi reiro.
\v 56 Ebu ze Iesu vaḡeꞌenaꞌa, kuru neḡa habaꞌano edanadu ḡadimutitiro, “Zaꞌe nouge rae zamareꞌohe? Aniꞌe Mui ꞌahi veize ariꞌuma ga mene?”
\v 57 Eꞌe madaḡano dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu Farisea azaḡaniꞌa Iesu obone tihi radu vaze niduꞌa riḡa ḡoreziro, “Iniuꞌa Iesuꞌe nouma radiuꞌetaꞌaꞌe ederoꞌidene, ihofoꞌi!”
\c 12
\s1 Mariaꞌa Iesu Oda rana Dehoro Hohoḡa Beuꞌoharo
\r (Mataio 26:6-13; Mareko 14:3-9)
\p 
\v 1 Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa veize mada fuꞌo tiba fare ꞌizema mougano, Iesuꞌa Betania neḡano feuriro. Aꞌe Iesuꞌa bare ḡaboniroteꞌe vazeḡa, Lazaroꞌa radiuꞌeteꞌe neḡa.
\v 2 Eꞌanoꞌo eꞌea Iesu veize ḡorava ogomuḡa ruhibiro. Maretaꞌa ogomu haḡairo ebu Lazaroꞌe Iesu teite ogomu fataḡa babaḡano tave ehoriroteꞌe azaḡa boꞌaḡano radiro.
\v 3 Ebu Mariaꞌa dehoro huga hohoḡa naeḡa boro, niḡa Nado bio komeꞌa iriꞌavonadu mae ariro. Ebu dehoro hohoḡa eꞌe Iesu oda rana beuꞌiro, ebu iguḡa hina zauhiro. Eꞌanoꞌo ne zamaḡanoꞌe dehoro hohoḡaniꞌa iriꞌaviro. \fig Mariaꞌa dehoro hohoḡa hina Iesu oda vuzuꞌiro|src="WA03839b.tif" size="col" ref="12:1-8"\fig*
\p 
\v 4 Rehano Iesu tahiꞌa ꞌahoga, vesuꞌu ani revohatiteꞌe tahiꞌaḡa ꞌahoga, Isakariota vazeḡa Iudaꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro,
\v 5 “Dehoro hohoḡa ꞌadi seronadu muri tiba gau hadiḡa\f + \fr 12:5 \fqa denari 300 \f* hidifo ebu eꞌe hadiḡaꞌe zahara azaḡa zinifo.”
\v 6 Aniꞌe mene zahara azaḡa zamariro, rehano aniꞌe ḡonore vazeḡa radu ꞌouge reiro. Aniꞌe zeḡe hadi fuseḡa taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa radu fuse zamaḡano ufiroteꞌe hadiḡa ane veize ḡonotaudo.
\v 7 Ebu Iesuꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro, “Roḡae ꞌahiꞌe ago gararoꞌi, mazaḡa aniꞌe e rudanadu guriteꞌe madaḡa veize dehoro ꞌadi ruhibeha.
\v 8 Zahara azaḡaꞌe iḡaiḡa zae teite radiꞌuma, u eꞌe iḡaiḡa zae teite mene radiꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 9 Iuda azaḡa ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa Iesuꞌa Betania neḡano radiuꞌeteꞌe igirotene, eꞌe neḡa onamiro. Aꞌe mene Iesu daꞌo ḡianoga veize, rehano aneꞌa rune azaḡa boꞌaḡano bare ḡaboniroteꞌe vazeḡa Lazaro zuni ḡianoga veize reiro.
\v 10 Eꞌanoꞌo dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡaꞌe Lazaro zuni matihi rae ḡoꞌaniro,
\v 11 mazaḡa Lazaro uꞌano, Iuda azaḡa ḡehaḡaniꞌa ze modadu Iesu vaḡe onamiro ebu ani mazao firo.
\s1 Ierusalema Diuḡiro
\r (Mataio 21:1-11; Mareko 11:1-11; Luka 19:28-40)
\p 
\v 12 Irarirotene, Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa veize Ierusalema itiroteꞌe vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa Iesuꞌe Ierusalema aroga igiro.
\v 13 Eꞌanoꞌo ze Sigi rouga\f + \fr 12:13 \fqa pamu ireḡa rouga \f* variꞌe madu ani hidoga veize onamiro. Ebu ze ḡihau huaro,
\q1 “Hosana!
\q1 Zuhiꞌa Boro niḡano areꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune!
\q1 Isaraela azaḡa kiniḡaꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune!”\x + \xo 12:13 \xt Salamo 118:25-26\x*
\p 
\v 14 Iesuꞌa doniki ubuga horonadu eꞌe rana tire ehoriro. Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro,
\q1 
\v 15 “Ierusalema azaḡa,\f + \fr 12:15 \fqa Sioni aboḡa \f* ago rihanoꞌi.
\q1 Ḡianoꞌi, zae kiniꞌa doniki ubuga rana ehoradu areꞌohe.”\x + \xo 12:15 \xt Zekaria 9:9\x*
\p 
\v 16 Eꞌe madaḡano Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe ꞌahiguḡa mene faine zamariro. Rehano Iesuꞌa runeonoꞌo bare ḡabodiroteꞌe enogano, Buka Zaḡoḡano ani moneo ꞌahiguḡa mirihiroteꞌe zu vazevazeꞌa ani mazao ꞌouge haḡairotaꞌaꞌe ederiro.
\p 
\v 17 Ebu Iesuꞌa iduonoꞌo Lazaro hunadu rune azaḡa boꞌaḡano bare ḡaboniroteꞌe madaḡano, ani teite radiroteꞌe vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa eꞌe hariḡa vaze mazao barebare rae fureniro.
\v 18 Ebu vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa Iesuꞌa haḡai nu badeḡa ꞌadi haḡairoteꞌe igiro ꞌahine, ze ani hidoga radu ane vaḡe onamiro.
\v 19 Eꞌanoꞌo Farisea azaḡaꞌe zeḡeꞌa bare neneḡaniro, “Ḡianoꞌi. ꞌAhiꞌe mene emeꞌa haḡaihi reiroteꞌe haḡaiḡa. Raha azaḡa niduꞌa ani hegote onamiro!”
\s1 Iesuꞌa Ane Rune moneo rae Fureniro
\p 
\v 20 Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡano Badiꞌa mazao kuranoga veize Ierusalema onamiroteꞌe azaḡa boꞌaḡano Giriki azaḡa nuꞌa radiunu.
\v 21 Giriki azaḡa eꞌeꞌa Galilea habaꞌa Betesaida vazeḡa Filipi vaḡe onamadu uminiro, “Vaze boro, emeꞌe Iesu ḡianihi raꞌohe.”
\v 22 Ebu Filipiꞌa onamadu Anderea niro, ebu anianine Iesu vaḡe onamadu ḡadiniro.
\v 23 Ebu Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Badiꞌaꞌa Vaze Ubugaꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune rae ihoziteꞌe madaḡaꞌe maha.
\v 24 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe. Vuidi maḡa rahao mene gurine, aniꞌe maḡa isoḡa radiꞌuma. Rehano ani rahao gurine, ḡehaḡaniꞌa hudaꞌuma.
\v 25 Iniuꞌa ane ḡabone zamare borofine, ḡabone tuḡutuḡu mene hidiꞌuma. Rehano iniuꞌa raha ꞌada ane ḡabone heꞌeheꞌenine, ḡabode radiꞌuma onamo radiu tuḡutuḡu.
\v 26 Iniuꞌa eḡe tuḡure vazeḡa reihi roꞌidene, eḡe hegotoꞌi. Eꞌe noꞌe habaꞌano radiune, eḡe tuḡure vazeḡa zuni eꞌea radiꞌuma. Eḡe tuḡure vazeḡaꞌe eḡe Mamaꞌa niguniꞌuma.
\p 
\v 27 Izidi eḡe zamaꞌe aduduꞌohe. E nagini reꞌuma? 'Mama, aduga madaḡa ꞌahaonoꞌo e ḡabohoꞌi,' rae reꞌuma ga? Mene, e aduga madaḡa ꞌahi mouga veize ariro.
\v 28 Mama, ḡae ni mae ḡihinoꞌi!” ꞌOugadu ago ꞌahoganiꞌa adureonoꞌo ꞌahige rae reiro, “Eḡeꞌa nihe mae ḡihineha zu bare mae ḡihiniꞌuma.”
\v 29 Vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa eꞌea ḡoere eꞌe egadu, “Viriꞌa fuꞌureꞌohe,” rae reiro. Ebu nuꞌe, “Tuḡure viganiꞌa ani mazao ḡoereha,” rae reiro.
\v 30 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Ago aꞌe mene eḡe veize, rehano zae veize ḡoereha.
\v 31 Izidiꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa raha ꞌadi azaḡa kotazeꞌeteꞌe madaḡa. Izidiꞌe raha ꞌadi zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa, Satani mae vaḡiniꞌuma.
\v 32 Rehano vazeꞌa rahaonoꞌo eḡe mae ḡihihine, eḡeꞌa vaze niduꞌa eḡe vaḡe hutube ariꞌuma.”
\v 33 Iesuꞌe aneꞌa nougenouge rudatiteꞌe moneo ihozifine ꞌouge rae reiro.
\p 
\v 34 Ebu vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa niro, “Buka Zaḡoḡanonoꞌo\f + \fr 12:34 \fqa Mose goro ḡoeꞌanonoꞌo \f* eme ꞌahige edereꞌohe, 'Kerisoꞌe radiu tuḡutuḡu.' Rehano ḡaꞌe nougadu, 'Vaze Ubugaꞌe rahaonoꞌo mae ḡihiniꞌuma,' rae raꞌohe? Vaze Ubugaꞌe iniu?”
\v 35 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Agaḡaꞌe mada tahiḡa bare zae teite radiꞌuma. Agaḡaꞌe zae teite radiuꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano oname onaoꞌi, ꞌougine zaꞌe uzaboꞌa mene ḡahiziꞌuma. Uzabo zamaḡano ragaveꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ani noꞌe onameꞌetaꞌaꞌe aḡuꞌa.
\v 36 Agaḡaꞌe zae teite radiuꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano agaḡa mazao fioꞌi, ꞌougine za agaḡa ubuga reꞌuma.” Iesuꞌa ꞌouge ziroteꞌe enogano, muhize onamadu zeḡe mazaonoꞌo uꞌuraro.
\s1 Iesu mazao Mene Fieꞌeteꞌe Azaḡa
\p 
\v 37 Iesuꞌa haḡai nu badeḡa ḡehaḡa vaze zamao haḡairo, rehano ze ꞌize ani mazao mene firo.
\v 38 Peroveta vazeḡa Isaiaꞌa reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaniꞌa hudaro,
\q1 “Zuhiꞌa Boro, emeḡeꞌa haramiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaꞌe vazeꞌa mene mae ḡihiniro.
\q2 Ḡaeꞌa gigiꞌaḡo ze ihoziro, rehano ze mene mae ḡihiniro.”\x + \xo 12:38 \xt Isaia 53:1\x*
\p 
\v 39 Nougadu ze Iesu mazao fioga mene idararoteꞌe moneo Isaiaꞌa ꞌahige bare rae reiro,
\q1 
\v 40 “Badiꞌaꞌa ubumaze kuruniro
\q2 zu zeḡe zama ꞌuiro.
\q1 Eꞌe uꞌano, ze ubumaze hina horoneꞌe rehano, hugaꞌe mene horoniꞌuma,
\q2 zu zamaze hina mene faine zamariꞌuma.
\q1 Aꞌe, ze eḡe vaḡe ḡihure baradu mene manoroga veize raꞌohe.”\x + \xo 12:40 \xt Isaia 6:10\x*
\p 
\v 41 Isaiaꞌa ꞌahige rae reirotaꞌaꞌe mazaḡa ani Iesuꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune rae ederiro zu ani moneo ḡoeriro.
\p 
\v 42 U vaze ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa boꞌaḡano vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa Iesu mazao firo. Rehano ze ani mazao fieꞌetaꞌaꞌe vaze ꞌahoga mene niro, mazaḡa Farisea azaḡaniꞌa nu'onu'o neḡanonoꞌo ze mae buziꞌuma radu riharo.
\v 43 Ze vazeꞌa ze niguzeꞌetaꞌaꞌe ufeta zamariro, rehano Badiꞌaꞌa ze niguzeꞌetaꞌaꞌe mene zamariro.
\p 
\v 44 Ebu Iesuꞌa agoḡa boro hina ḡihau ḡoeriro, “Iniu eḡe mazao fieꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe mazao daꞌo mene fieꞌohe, rehano eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe vazeḡa mazao fieꞌohe.
\v 45 Ebu iniu eḡe ḡiaheꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe vazeḡa ḡianeꞌohe.
\v 46 Agaḡa teige, e raha ꞌahi ariro. Aꞌe eḡe mazao fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe uzabo zamaḡano mene radoga veize raꞌohe.
\p 
\v 47 Iniu eḡe ḡoere egadu mene hegotine zuni, e ani mene kotaniꞌuma. Mazaḡa eꞌe raha azaḡa kotazoga veize mene ariro, rehano ḡabozoga veize ariro.
\v 48 Eḡe hezahohiꞌeteꞌe zu eḡe ḡoere mene mae ḡihineꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa kotaneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ꞌahoga. Mada ḡonagano eḡeꞌa rateꞌe ḡoeꞌa ꞌadi hina ani kotaniꞌuma.
\v 49 E eḡe edeḡano mene ḡoeriro, rehano eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe Mamaheꞌa e nagini rouga zu nouge rae rouga ihohiro.
\v 50 E edeḡa, ani goro ḡoeꞌaniꞌa ḡabone tuḡutuḡu ibiḡano ibitoziꞌohe. Eꞌanoꞌo e Mamaꞌa nagini ihiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa daꞌo raꞌohe.”
\c 13
\s1 Iesuꞌa Ane Tahiꞌatahiꞌa Oda Vuzuꞌiro
\p 
\v 1 Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa ꞌizema mougano, Iesuꞌe aneꞌa raha ꞌadi modadu Mama vaḡe ititeꞌe madaḡa meirotaꞌaꞌe ederiro. Ebu aneꞌa raha ꞌada ane hegoteꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zamare borofiro, onamo ani rudatiteꞌe madaḡa meiro.
\v 2 Ḡoravaḡano ze ogomu tiburu aunu. Diaboloꞌa Isakariota vazeḡa Simona ubuga, Iuda zamaḡa amahi tutunadu Iesu revohatihi reiro.
\v 3 Iesuꞌe ederiro, Moganiꞌa ḡau niduꞌa ani ꞌevora tiro ebu aneꞌa Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo aradu bare Badiꞌa vaḡe itiꞌuma.
\v 4 Eꞌanoꞌo ani ogauꞌeteꞌe habaꞌanonoꞌo iḡunadu raga dabuaḡa mae vaḡine tiro, ebu ahiri zauheꞌeteꞌe dabuaḡa madu gabaꞌiḡano autiro.
\v 5 Ebu siuva duꞌuḡano vu beuꞌadu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa oda vuzuꞌiro, zu autiroteꞌe dabuaḡa hina zauhiro.
\p 
\v 6 Iesuꞌa Simona Petero vaḡirotene, Peteroꞌa niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, ḡa eḡe oda vuzuꞌihi raꞌehe?”
\v 7 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Eḡeꞌa nagini haḡaeꞌetaꞌaꞌe ḡa izidiꞌe aḡuꞌa, rehano vesuꞌu ederiꞌuma.”
\v 8 Peteroꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro, “Ḡa eḡe odaꞌe mene hune vuzuꞌiꞌuma!” Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Eḡeꞌa ḡae oda mene vuzuꞌine, ḡaꞌe eḡe mene tahiꞌa reꞌuma.”
\v 9 Simona Peteroꞌa niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, eḡe oda daꞌo mene, rehano ꞌevorehe ebu vadinihe zuni vuzuꞌoꞌi.”
\v 10 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Viriroteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe odaḡa daꞌo vuzuꞌeꞌohe. Ani ahiꞌaꞌe niduꞌa deheḡa. Ebu zaꞌe deheḡa, rehano zae niduꞌa boꞌaḡano tibaꞌe mene deheḡa.”
\v 11 Iesuꞌe iniuꞌa ani revohatiteꞌe ederiro, eꞌanoꞌo, “Zae boꞌaḡano tibaꞌe mene deheḡa,” rae reiro. \fig Iesuꞌa Petero odaḡa vuzuꞌiro|src="cn01799B.tif" size="col" ref="13:4-11"\fig*
\p 
\v 12 Iesuꞌa odaze vuzuꞌe hauḡirotene, raga dabuaḡa bare haḡadu ogomu fataḡa uhiḡano ehoriro. Ebu aneꞌa ziro, “Za eꞌa zae veize haḡateꞌe haḡaiḡa hugaꞌe edeḡahe?
\v 13 Za eḡe mazao ihore vazeḡa zu Zuhiꞌa Boro rae huheꞌohe. Zaꞌa raꞌetaꞌaꞌe hube, eꞌe ꞌuguḡa vazeḡa.
\v 14 Eꞌe zae Zuhiꞌa Boro ebu ihore vazeḡa, rehano zae oda vuzuꞌeha. Eꞌanoꞌo zae zuni ꞌahoganiꞌa ꞌahoga oda vuzuꞌiꞌuma.
\v 15 Eḡeꞌa zae veize haḡateꞌe teige, zae zuni haḡaifine e ꞌahige haḡadu ihozeha.
\v 16 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe. Tuḡure vazeḡaꞌe ane zuhiꞌa mene vitinoga, ebu iniuꞌa tuḡuniroteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ani tuḡuniroteꞌe vazeḡa mene vitinoga.
\v 17 Za eꞌa izidi haḡataꞌaꞌe ederadu nize mae ovoeꞌenaꞌa vaze danazine, matuꞌe rudaꞌuma.”
\s1 Iesu Revohatiteꞌe Vazeḡa
\r (Mataio 26:20-25; Mareko 14:17-21; Luka 22:21-23)
\p 
\v 18 “E zae niduꞌa mazao mene ḡoereꞌohe. E eḡeꞌa ohotiroteꞌe azaḡaꞌe edeḡa. Rehano Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiroteꞌeꞌa hudaꞌuma, 'Eḡe ogomu tiburu auꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa ḡihuradu e agirohiro.'\x + \xo 13:18 \xt Salamo 41:9\x*
\v 19 ꞌUguḡaniꞌa ꞌizema fureranogano izidi eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, mazaḡa ꞌuguḡaniꞌa fureratiteꞌe madaḡano eḡeꞌa eꞌe iniu rae ihoziroteꞌe zaeꞌa mae ḡihinifine raꞌohe.
\v 20 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, iniu eḡeꞌa tuḡuneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa mae ḡihineꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe mae ḡihiheꞌohe. Ebu iniu eḡe mae ḡihiheꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe vazeḡa mae ḡihineꞌohe.”
\p 
\v 21 Iesuꞌa ḡoere ꞌadi reirotene, zamaḡaniꞌa adudaro ebu ꞌahige rae fureniro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, zae boꞌaḡano vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa eḡe revoniꞌuma.”
\v 22 Ebu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe aniꞌa iniu moneo reirotaꞌaꞌe mene ederadu ze zeḡeꞌa bare ḡiatitiro.
\v 23 Iesu zamarone tahiꞌaḡaniꞌa Iesu uhiḡano tave ehore radiro.
\v 24 Eꞌanoꞌo Simona Peteroꞌa ubumaḡa hina tahiꞌa eꞌe niro, “Ani iniu moneo raꞌeteꞌe ḡadinoꞌi.”
\p 
\v 25 Eꞌanoꞌo ani Iesu mazao aroranadu ḡadiniro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, aꞌe iniu?”
\v 26 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Eꞌa ꞌuvahu odoga tahiḡa siuvao taradu hauꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa revoniꞌuma.” Ebu aniꞌa ꞌuvahu odoga tahiḡa taradu Isakariota vazeḡa Simona ubuga, Iuda haro.
\v 27 Ebu Iudaꞌa ꞌuvahu odoga eꞌe meirotene, Sataniꞌa zamaḡa diuḡiro. Ebu Iesuꞌa niro, “Ḡaꞌa haḡaiteꞌe haḡaiḡaꞌe ḡarihe haḡaoꞌi.”
\v 28 Eꞌea ogau radiroteꞌe azaḡa boꞌaḡano vazeni ꞌahoga zuni Iesuꞌe nougadu Iuda mazao ꞌouge rae reiroteꞌe mene ederiro.
\v 29 Iudaꞌe hadize taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa uꞌano, Iesu tahiꞌa nuꞌe ꞌahige zamariro, “Mui veize eme ura ḡauḡa nu hoitoga veize ga zahara azaḡa ḡau nu zenoga veize Iesuꞌa Iuda umineha.”
\v 30 Iudaꞌa ꞌuvahu odoga eꞌe madu zogone buaro. Aꞌe ohere zamaḡano.
\s1 Zamarotitoꞌi
\p 
\v 31 Iudaꞌa buarotene Iesuꞌa ziro, “Izidi Vaze Ubuga mae ḡihineꞌohe ebu ani uꞌano Badiꞌa mae ḡihineꞌohe.
\v 32 Ubuga uꞌano Badiꞌa mae ḡihinine, Badiꞌaꞌe aneꞌa bare Ubuga mae ḡihiniꞌuma, ebu aneꞌa zogone ꞌougiꞌuma.
\p 
\v 33 Eḡe tahiꞌatahiꞌa, e zae teite mada tahiḡa daꞌo radiꞌuma. Za eḡe vaḡiꞌuma, rehano ibite Iuda azaḡa boroboro ziroteꞌe teige, za idane ziꞌohe, 'Eḡeꞌa onamiteꞌe habaꞌa zaꞌe aroga mene idaḡa.'
\v 34 E goro ḡoeꞌa iziga ziniꞌohe. Zaeꞌa zamarotitoꞌi. Eḡeꞌa za zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe teige, zae zuni zamarotitoꞌi.
\v 35 Zaeꞌa zamarotitine, vaze niduꞌa eꞌe horonadu zaꞌe eḡe tahiꞌatahiꞌa rae ederiꞌuma.”
\s1 Peteroꞌa Iesu Oꞌoniꞌuma rae Reiro
\r (Mataio 26:31-35; Mareko 14:27-31; Luka 22:31-34)
\p 
\v 36 Simona Peteroꞌa Iesu ḡadiniro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, ḡa noꞌe onamiꞌuma?” Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Eḡeꞌa onamiteꞌe habaꞌaꞌe ḡaꞌa hegotoga izidi mene idaḡa. Rehano vesuꞌu eḡe hegotiꞌuma.”
\v 37 Peteroꞌa niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, e nougadu izidi ḡa hegotogaꞌe mene idaḡa? Eḡeꞌa ḡae veize ḡabonehe zuni ahetiꞌuma.”
\v 38 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Ḡa eḡe veize ḡaboneḡo ahetiꞌumahe? Eḡeꞌa hube hune ḡaꞌohe, ꞌizema kokorokuꞌa uganogano ḡa ḡae uḡidu eḡe oꞌohiꞌuma.”
\c 14
\s1 Iesuꞌe Mama Vaḡe Onameꞌeteꞌe Ibiḡa
\p 
\v 1 Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ziro, “Ago zamare adudanoꞌi. Badiꞌa mazao fioꞌi ebu eḡe mazao zuni fioꞌi.
\v 2 Eḡe Mama neoꞌe radone habaꞌa ḡehaḡa. Aꞌe hube mene reifone, e ꞌahi mene reifo. E zae veize haba ꞌahoga ruhibe touga radu onamiꞌuma.
\v 3 Onamadu zae veize haba ꞌahoga ruhibine, e bare ariꞌuma, ebu eḡe teite radifine zamazadu zaꞌe eḡe habao radiꞌuma.
\v 4 Eꞌa onamiteꞌe habaꞌa ibiḡaꞌe zaꞌe edeḡa.”
\p 
\v 5 Tomasiꞌa Iesu niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, eme ḡaꞌa noꞌe onamiꞌumaꞌe aḡuꞌa. Eme nougenouge ibi eꞌe ederiꞌuma?”
\v 6 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Eꞌe Mama vaḡe onameꞌeteꞌe ibiḡa, zu ḡoere huga ihozeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa, zu ḡabone tuḡutuḡu ziniꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa. Eḡe mazaonoꞌo mene reine, vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa Mama vaḡe onamogaꞌe mene idaḡa.
\v 7 Za hube hune e ederine, eḡe Mama zuni ederiꞌuma.\f + \fr 14:7 \fqa Za e hube hune ederifone, eḡe Mama zuni ederifo. \f* Izidionoꞌo onamo zaꞌe ani edereꞌohe ebu ani horoniro.”
\p 
\v 8 Filipiꞌa niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, Mama ihofoꞌi. Eme eꞌe daꞌo urateꞌohe.”
\v 9 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Eꞌe mada boro hune zae teite radiunu. Rehano Filipi, ḡa e aḡuꞌahe? Iniu eḡe horohiroteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe Mama zuni horoniro. Ḡa nougadu, 'Mama ihofoꞌi,' rae raꞌohe?
\v 10 Ḡa eꞌe Mama teite tiburaroteꞌe zu Mamaꞌe eḡe teite tiburaroteꞌe mene mae ḡihineꞌehe? Eḡeꞌa ziꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌaꞌe eḡe edeḡano mene raꞌohe, rehano eḡe teite tiburanadu radiuꞌeteꞌe Mamaheꞌa ane gau haḡaeꞌohe.
\v 11 Eḡe mazao fioꞌi. Eꞌe Mama teite tiburaroteꞌe zu Mamaꞌe eḡe teite tiburaroteꞌe mae ḡihinoꞌi. Eꞌe mae ḡihinoga mene idaḡa roꞌidene, eḡeꞌa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe haḡai gigiꞌaḡa horonadu eḡe ḡoere mae ḡihinoꞌi.
\v 12 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe. Iniu eḡe mazao fieꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa eḡeꞌa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa zuni haḡaiꞌuma, ebu deꞌeguḡa ufeta vitine haḡai ḡihiꞌaḡa haḡaiꞌuma, mazaḡa e Mama vaḡe onamiꞌuma.
\v 13 Ebu za eḡe niḡano nagini umidine, eḡeꞌa ꞌouge haḡaiꞌuma. Aꞌe Ubuga uꞌano Badiꞌa ni mae ḡihinifine raꞌohe.
\v 14 Za eḡe niḡano nagini umidine, eḡeꞌa ꞌouge haḡaiꞌuma.”
\s1 Vine Zaḡoḡa moneo Ihoziro
\p 
\v 15 “Za eḡe zamare borofoꞌidene, eḡe goro ḡoeꞌa hegotoꞌi.
\v 16 Eḡeꞌa Mama uminadu aneꞌa za danazeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa zae mazao tuḡuniꞌuma, zu aniꞌe zae teite radiꞌuma onamo tuḡutuḡu.
\v 17 Aniꞌe Vine Zaḡoḡa. Ani Badiꞌa moneo ḡoere huga ihozeꞌohe. Raha ꞌadi azaḡaniꞌa ani mene horoneꞌohe, zu ani mene edereꞌe ꞌahine, ani mae ḡihinogaꞌe mene idaḡa. Rehano zaꞌe ani edeḡa, mazaḡa aniꞌe zae teite radiuꞌohe zu zae teite tiburaꞌuma.
\p 
\v 18 E zaꞌe butu ega teige mene modiꞌuma, rehano zae vaḡe ariꞌuma.
\v 19 Mada tahiḡa enogano raha ꞌadi azaḡaniꞌa e mene bare horohiꞌuma. Rehano zaꞌe e horohiꞌuma, mazaḡa eꞌe bare ḡabodiꞌuma ꞌahine, zae zuni ḡabodiꞌuma.
\v 20 Eꞌe madaḡano zaꞌe ederiꞌuma, e eḡe Mama teite tiburaro, zu za eḡe teite tiburaro, ebu e zae teite tiburaro.
\v 21 Iniu eḡe goro ḡoeꞌa mae ḡihinadu eḡe hegoteꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa. Iniu eḡe zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe Mamaꞌa ani zamare borofiꞌuma, ebu eḡeꞌa ani zamare borofiꞌuma, zu ani mazao eḡeꞌa fureraꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 22 Ebu mene Isakariota vazeḡa, Iuda ꞌahoganiꞌa Iesu niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, ḡaꞌe eme mazaoꞌe fureratihi, rehano raha azaḡa mazaoꞌe mene fureratihi raꞌohe. Nougadu ꞌouge raꞌohe?”
\v 23 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Iniuꞌa eḡe zamare borofine, eḡe ḡoere hegotiꞌuma, zu eḡe Mamaꞌa ani zamare borofiꞌuma. Ebu Mamahe zu eḡeꞌa ani vaḡe onamadu ani teite ne tibano radiꞌuma.
\v 24 Rehano iniu e mene zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe ḡoere mene hegoteꞌohe. Zaeꞌa eḡe mazaonoꞌo igiꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa ꞌadiꞌe eḡe mene ḡoere, rehano eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe Mamahe ḡoere.
\p 
\v 25 E zae teite radiuꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano ḡoere ꞌahi zeha.
\v 26 Rehano Mamaꞌa eḡe niḡano za danazeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa, Vine Zaḡoḡa tuḡuniꞌuma, zu Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ḡau niduꞌa ihoziꞌuma. Ebu aniꞌe eꞌa ziroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa niduꞌa zaeꞌa zamarifine ibitoziꞌuma.
\v 27 E zama roḡeḡa zae teite modeꞌohe. E eḡe zama roḡeḡa ziniꞌohe. Eḡeꞌa ziniꞌeteꞌe zama roḡeḡaꞌe mene raha azaḡaniꞌa ziniꞌeteꞌe heuḡa. Zamaze ago adudanoꞌi, zu ago rihanoꞌi.
\v 28 E ꞌahige rae zirotaꞌaꞌe za igiro, 'Eꞌe zae muhize onamiꞌuma zu zae vaḡe bare ariꞌuma.' Zaꞌa e zamare borofifone, e Mama vaḡe onameꞌeteꞌe uꞌano zaeꞌa matuꞌifo, mazaḡa Mamaꞌe eḡe vitihe ufeta ḡihiꞌa hune.
\v 29 ꞌIzema eꞌeguḡaniꞌa fureranogano izidi eꞌa ihozeha. Aꞌe, eꞌeguḡaniꞌa fureraune, za eḡeꞌa ziroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa mae ḡihinifine raꞌohe.
\v 30 E zae teite mene faḡa ḡoeriꞌuma, mazaḡa raha zuhiꞌaḡa, Sataniꞌa eḡe agirohifine areꞌohe. Rehano aniꞌe eḡe raharahaheꞌeteꞌe inaraḡaꞌe oꞌoꞌa.
\v 31 U raha azaḡaꞌe eḡeꞌa Mama zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe zu Mamaꞌa tuḡuhadu e ḡabonehe aheteꞌetaꞌaꞌe ederiꞌuma. Iḡunoꞌi, haba ꞌahi modihi.”
\c 15
\s1 Vaini Ireḡa ebu Ezaga
\p 
\v 1 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Eꞌe vaini ireḡa huga, ebu eḡe Mamaꞌe vaini mebaḡa taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa.
\v 2 Eḡe rana kamadu mene hudauꞌeteꞌe ezaga niduꞌaꞌe aneꞌa variꞌe modeꞌohe. U hudauꞌeteꞌe ezagaꞌe ufeta ḡehaḡaniꞌa hudanoga veize aneꞌa rirahe idaneꞌohe.
\v 3 Eḡeꞌa ziroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa uꞌano, zaꞌe amahi deheraro.
\v 4 Eḡe teite tiburanadu radoꞌi, ꞌougine eḡe zuni zae teite tiburanadu radiꞌuma. Ezagaꞌe vaini ireḡano mene kamine, ani aneꞌa bare hudanogaꞌe mene idaḡa. Eꞌe teige, za eḡe teite mene tiburanadu radiune, za zaeꞌa bare hudanogaꞌe mene idaḡa. \fig Vaini ezaga zu vaini maḡa|src="HK00109B.TIF" size="col" ref="15:1-8"\fig*
\p 
\v 5 Eꞌe vaini ireḡa zu zaꞌe ezaga. Iniu eḡe teite tiburanadu radiune zu e ani teite tiburanadu radiune, aniꞌe ḡeharu hudaꞌuma. Mazaḡa za eḡe muhihine, ḡau ꞌahoga haḡaogaꞌe mene idaḡa.
\v 6 Iniu eḡe teite mene tiburanadu radiuꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ezaga variꞌe modadu rorauꞌeteꞌe teigeꞌohe. Ezaga ꞌuguḡaꞌe vazeꞌa nuꞌonadu ire rogao feune hufi haoneꞌohe.
\v 7 Zaꞌe eḡe teite tiburanadu radoꞌidene zu eḡe ḡoere hegotoꞌidene, za nagini urateꞌeteꞌe umidoꞌi, ꞌougine hidiꞌuma.
\v 8 Zaꞌa ḡeharu hudanadu zaꞌe eḡe tahiꞌatahiꞌa rae vazevaze ihozine, zeꞌa eḡe Mama mae ḡihiniꞌuma.
\p 
\v 9 Mamaꞌa eḡe zamare borofiroteꞌe teige, eḡe zuni za zamare borofiro. Zaꞌe eḡe zamarone azaḡa rouga veize, eḡe teite tiburanadu radiuꞌenoꞌi.
\v 10 E eḡe Mama goro ḡoeꞌa hegotadu aniꞌa e zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe teige, zaeꞌa eḡe goro ḡoeꞌa hegotine, eḡeꞌa za zamare borofiꞌuma.
\v 11 E ḡoere ꞌahi zeataꞌaꞌe, eḡe matuꞌuꞌe zae teite radadu zae matuꞌuꞌa iriꞌavoga veize raꞌohe.
\v 12 Eḡe goro ḡoeꞌaꞌe ꞌahi eꞌe: Eḡeꞌa za zamare borofiroteꞌe teige, zaeꞌa zamarotitoꞌi.
\v 13 Iniuꞌa ane vaze veize ane ḡabone ahetine, aꞌe vaze zamarone ḡihiꞌa hune ebu zamarone nunu vitinoga.
\v 14 Za eꞌa ziꞌeteꞌe goro ḡoeꞌa hegotine, eḡe vaze raꞌohe.
\v 15 E zaꞌe tuḡure azaḡa rae mene bare huziꞌuma, mazaḡa tuḡure azaḡaꞌe zuhiꞌazeꞌa nagini haḡaeꞌeteꞌe mene edereꞌohe. Rehano zaꞌe eḡe vaze rae huzeha, mazaḡa e eḡe Mama mazaonoꞌo igiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa niduꞌa ihoziro.
\v 16 Zaeꞌa e mene ohotiro, rehano eḡeꞌa za huzadu ohotiro. Eꞌanoꞌo zaeꞌa onamadu hudaꞌuma zu zae hugaꞌe mene hauḡiꞌuma. ꞌOugine, eḡe niḡano zaꞌa Mama mazao nagini umineꞌeteꞌe aneꞌa ziniꞌuma.
\v 17 Eḡe goro ḡoeꞌaꞌe ꞌahi eꞌe: Zaeꞌa zamarotitoꞌi.”
\s1 Raha Azaḡaniꞌa Iesu Tahiꞌatahiꞌa Heꞌeheꞌezeꞌohe
\p 
\v 18 “Raha azaḡaniꞌa za heꞌeheꞌezoꞌidene, zeꞌa ibite e heꞌeheꞌehirotaꞌaꞌe ederoꞌi.
\v 19 Zaꞌe raha azaḡa moneo reifone, ze zaꞌe zeḡe mone azaḡa radu za zamare borofifo. Rehano zaꞌe mene raha azaḡa moneo ꞌahine, zu eḡeꞌa za raha azaḡa mazaonoꞌo zamazadu ohotiro ꞌahine, zeꞌe za heꞌeheꞌezeꞌohe.
\v 20 Eꞌa ziroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa ꞌahi zamaroꞌi, 'Tuḡure vazeḡaꞌe ane zuhiꞌa mene vitinoga.' Ze e sausauhine, zae zuni sausauziꞌuma. Ebu ze eḡe ihore egohaune, zae ihore zuni egohaꞌuma.
\v 21 Zaꞌe eḡe none uꞌano zu zeꞌe eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe vazeḡa aḡuꞌa uꞌano, zeꞌa zae mazao ꞌouge haḡaiꞌuma.
\v 22 Eꞌa aradu ze mene zifone, zeꞌe haḡaize sauꞌa uꞌano zamaze mene adudafo. Rehano izidiꞌe ze haḡaize sauꞌa moneo ḡoere nunu rougaꞌe mene idaḡa.
\v 23 Iniu eḡe heꞌeheꞌeheꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe Mama zuni heꞌeheꞌeneꞌohe.
\v 24 Eꞌa zeḡe boꞌaḡano vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa mene haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡa mene haḡaifone, ze haḡaize sauꞌa uꞌano zamaze mene adudafo. Izidi ze eḡeꞌa haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡa gigiꞌa ꞌahiguḡa horoniro rehano, eḡe zu eḡe Mama heꞌeheꞌefiro.
\v 25 ꞌOugadu zeḡe Buka Zaḡoḡano\f + \fr 15:25 \fqa zeḡe goro ḡoeꞌano \f* mirihiroteꞌeꞌa hudaro, 'Zeꞌa mazaḡa oꞌoꞌano e heꞌeheꞌehiro.'\x + \xo 15:25 \xt Salamo 35:19, 69:4\x*
\p 
\v 26 Eꞌa Mama mazaonoꞌo zae mazao tuḡuniteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe zae danazeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa, zu Mama mazaonoꞌo aradu ḡoere huga ihozeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa. Aniꞌe Vine Zaḡoḡa. Aniꞌa arine, eḡe moneo rae fureniꞌuma.
\v 27 Ebu zae zuni eḡe moneo rae fureniꞌuma, mazaḡa zaꞌe ḡadaheḡanonoꞌo eḡe teite radiro.”
\c 16
\p 
\v 1 “Eꞌa ḡoere ꞌahi zeataꞌaꞌe zaeꞌa eḡe mazao fieꞌeteꞌe mene modoga veize raꞌohe.
\v 2 Ze nu'onu'o neḡanonoꞌo zae mae vaḡiziꞌuma. Ebu mada ꞌahoga meine, zae zimiꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe zeḡeꞌa bare Badiꞌa veize gaueꞌohe rae zamariꞌuma.
\v 3 Ze ꞌuguḡa haḡaiꞌuma, mazaḡa zeꞌe Mama zu e aḡuꞌa.
\v 4 E ḡoere ꞌahi zeataꞌaꞌe ꞌuguḡaniꞌa fureraune, za eḡeꞌa ziroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa zamaroga veize raꞌohe. E ḡoere ꞌahi ḡadaheḡano mene ziro, mazaḡa e zae teite radiro.”
\s1 Vine Zaḡoḡa Gauḡa
\p 
\v 5 “Izidi e eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe vazeḡa vaḡe onamiꞌuma. Rehano zae boꞌaḡano vazeni ꞌahoganiꞌa, 'Ḡa noꞌe onamiꞌuma?' rae mene ḡadiheꞌohe.
\v 6 Mazaḡa e ḡoere ꞌahi zeateꞌe uꞌano, zamaze are rudauꞌohe.
\v 7 Rehano eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, e za muhizeꞌetaꞌaꞌe zae veizeꞌe ufeta manoḡa. Mazaḡa e mene muhizine, danazeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa zae vaḡe mene ariꞌuma. Rehano e za muhizine, eḡeꞌa ani zae vaḡe tuḡuniꞌuma.
\v 8 Aniꞌa arine, haḡai sauꞌa moneo, vaze duduḡa moneo ebu kota moneo raha azaḡaꞌe veꞌoḡa rae fureniꞌuma.
\v 9 Haḡai sauꞌa moneo rae fureneꞌetaꞌaꞌe mazaḡa ze eḡe mazao mene fieꞌohe.
\v 10 Vaze duduḡa moneo fureneꞌetaꞌaꞌe mazaḡa eꞌe Mama vaḡe onamiꞌuma ebu za e mene bare horohiꞌuma.
\v 11 Ebu kota moneo rae fureneꞌetaꞌaꞌe mazaḡa raha ꞌadi azaḡa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa, Satani kotaniro.
\p 
\v 12 E za zihi raꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌaꞌe ḡehaḡa, rehano izidi zaꞌe faine zamarogaꞌe mene idaḡa.
\v 13 Rehano ḡoere huga ihozeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa, Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa arine, aniꞌa zae ibitozeadu zaeꞌa ḡoere huga niduꞌa ederiꞌuma. Aniꞌe ane edeḡano mene ḡoeriꞌuma, rehano Mama mazao igiꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa daꞌo reꞌuma. Ebu zama moneo naginiꞌa fureratiteꞌe ziꞌuma.
\v 14 Aniꞌa eꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune rae ihoziꞌuma, mazaḡa aniꞌe eḡe ḡoere madu ziꞌuma.
\v 15 Ḡau niduꞌaꞌe Mama mazao, ebu ani ḡau niduꞌaꞌe eḡe ḡau. Eꞌanoꞌo e ꞌahige rae zeha, 'Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa eḡe ḡoere madu za ihoziꞌuma.'
\v 16 Mada tahiḡa ḡarugano za e mene bare horohiꞌuma, ebu mada tahiḡa ḡarugano e bare horohiꞌuma.”
\s1 Zamaze Areꞌetaꞌaꞌe Ḡihuradu Bare Matuꞌiꞌuma
\p 
\v 17 Iesu tahiꞌa nuꞌa neneḡaniro, “Ani ḡoere hugaꞌe nagini? Ani ꞌahige raꞌohe, 'Mada tahiḡa ḡarugano za e mene bare horohiꞌuma, ebu mada tahiḡa ḡarugano e bare horohiꞌuma,' ebu 'Mazaḡa e Mama vaḡe onamiꞌuma.'”
\v 18 Ze zeḡeꞌa bare ḡadimutitiro, “'Mada tahiḡa ḡarugano,' rae rataꞌaꞌe hugaꞌe nagini? Eme aniꞌa nagini ḡoereꞌetaꞌaꞌe aḡuꞌa.”
\p 
\v 19 Iesuꞌe ze ane ḡoere moneo ḡadinihi reirotaꞌaꞌe ederadu ziro, “E ꞌahige zeha, 'Mada tahiḡa ḡarugano za e mene bare horohiꞌuma, ebu mada tahiḡa ḡarugano e bare horohiꞌuma.' Zaꞌe ḡoere ꞌahi huga moneo ḡadimutiteꞌehe?
\v 20 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, zaꞌe niau ḡoinahiꞌuma, u raha azaḡaꞌe matuꞌiꞌuma. Zaꞌe zamaze ariꞌuma, rehano zamaze areꞌetaꞌaꞌe ḡihuradu matuꞌiꞌuma.
\v 21 Roḡae ꞌahoganiꞌa ene fureneꞌetene zamaze aduduꞌohe, mazaḡa gigiꞌa boro meiteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa maha. Rehano ani ene furenatene, ani gigiꞌa aḡutuꞌohe, mazaḡa eneꞌa rahao fureranadu matuꞌeꞌohe.
\v 22 Eꞌe teige, izidi zaꞌe zamaze areꞌohe, rehano e za bare ḡiaziꞌuma ebu zaꞌe matuiꞌuma. Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa za matuꞌu ꞌahi mene meiniꞌuma.
\v 23 Eꞌe madaḡano zaꞌe ḡadimu ꞌahoga mene ḡadihiꞌuma.\f + \fr 16:23 \fqa zaꞌe ḡau ꞌahoga eḡe mazao mene umidiꞌuma \f* Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, eḡe niḡano Mama nagini uminine, aneꞌa ziniꞌuma.
\v 24 Ibite onao izidi eḡe niḡano za Badiꞌa mazao ḡau ꞌahoga mene uminiro. Uminoꞌi, ꞌougine hidiꞌuma ebu za matuꞌuꞌa iriꞌaviꞌuma.
\p 
\v 25 E hari idaidaḡa hina ḡoreziro. Rehano mada ꞌahoga meine, hari idaidaḡa hina mene bare ḡoreziꞌuma, ebu Mama moneo dehene ziꞌuma.
\v 26 Eꞌe madaḡanoꞌe za eḡe niḡano Mama mazao uminiꞌuma. Eḡeꞌa zae veize Mama uminiꞌuma rae mene ziꞌohe.
\v 27 Zaꞌe eḡe zamare borofiroteꞌe zu za eꞌa Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo ariroteꞌe mae ḡihiniroteꞌe uꞌano, Mamaꞌe aneꞌa bare za zamare borofeꞌohe.
\v 28 Eꞌe Mama mazaonoꞌo raha ꞌahi ariro. Izidi e raha ꞌahi modadu Mama vaḡe bare onamiꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 29 Ebu Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa reiro, “Izidi ḡa dehene ḡoereꞌohe ebu hari idaidaḡa mene raꞌohe.
\v 30 Izidi eme edereha, ḡaꞌe ḡau niduꞌa edeḡa zu ḡa vaze ḡadimu ibite ederadu ze bare ḡadiꞌoga mene urateꞌohe. Eꞌe uꞌano, eme ḡaꞌa Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo ariroteꞌe mae ḡihineꞌohe.”
\v 31 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Izidi zaꞌe eḡe mazao fieꞌehe?
\v 32 Rehano mada ꞌahoganiꞌa areꞌohe, ebu izidi maha. Eꞌe madaḡano za tibatiba neze uꞌa rovote ḡouriꞌuma ebu eḡe daꞌo muhihiꞌuma. Rehano eꞌe mene eḡe daꞌo, mazaḡa eḡe Mamaꞌe eḡe teite radiuꞌohe.
\v 33 E ḡoere ꞌahi zeataꞌaꞌe za eḡe teite tiburanadu zamaze roḡenoga veize raꞌohe. Raha ꞌada za aduga hideꞌohe, rehano inaroꞌi! Eḡeꞌa raha ꞌadi gigiꞌaḡa raharahaniro.”
\c 17
\s1 Iesuꞌa Ane veize Kuraro
\p 
\v 1 Iesuꞌa ḡoere ꞌahi ziroteꞌe enogano, adure ḡohani ḡianadu kuraro, “Mama, madaḡaꞌe maha. Ubugoꞌa ḡaꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune rae ihozifine, ḡaeꞌa Ubugoꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune rae ihozoꞌi.
\v 2 Mazaḡa ḡaeꞌa Ubuga haroteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa ḡabone tuḡutuḡu zenoga veize, vaze niduꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe gigiꞌaḡa Ubuga haro.
\v 3 Ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hideꞌeteꞌe ibiḡaꞌe vazeꞌa ḡa, Badiꞌa tibuhuga ebu ḡaeꞌa tuḡuniroteꞌe vazeḡa, Iesu Keriso edereꞌeteꞌe raꞌohe.
\v 4 Ḡaeꞌa iniroteꞌe gauḡaꞌe eḡeꞌa hauḡiro. ꞌOugadu e raha ꞌada ḡaꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune rae ihoziro.
\v 5 Mama, raha zu aduga ꞌizema haḡaogano niheꞌe niḡo teite mae ḡihiniroteꞌe teige, izidi zuni niheꞌe niḡo teite mae ḡihinoꞌi.”
\s1 Iesuꞌa Ane Tahiꞌatahiꞌa veize Kuraro
\p 
\v 6 “E ḡaꞌa raha ꞌadao iniroteꞌe azaḡa mazao ḡae moneo rae fureniro. Zeꞌe ḡae tahiꞌatahiꞌa rae reiro, ebu ḡaeꞌa ze iniro, zu ze ḡae ḡoere hegotiro.
\v 7 Izidi ze ḡaꞌa iniroteꞌe ḡauḡa niduꞌaꞌe ḡae mazaonoꞌo arirotaꞌaꞌe edeḡa.
\v 8 Mazaḡa ḡaꞌa ihiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa eḡeꞌa ziro ebu zeḡeꞌa mae ḡihiniro. Ze eḡeꞌa ḡae mazaonoꞌo arirotaꞌaꞌe hube hune ederiro, zu ḡaeꞌa eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe mae ḡihiniro.
\v 9 E zeḡe veize kurauꞌohe. E raha azaḡa veize mene kurauꞌohe, rehano ḡaeꞌa iniroteꞌe azaḡa veize kurauꞌohe, mazaḡa zeꞌe ḡae tahiꞌatahiꞌa.
\v 10 Eḡe ḡau niduꞌaꞌe ḡae ḡau, ebu ḡae ḡau niduꞌaꞌe eḡe ḡau. Ze eꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune rae raꞌohe.
\v 11 Eꞌe raha ꞌada mene bare radiꞌuma ebu ḡae vaḡe amiꞌuma. Rehano zeꞌe raha ꞌada radiꞌuma. Mama Zaḡoḡa, ḡa niḡo iniro. Ḡae niḡano ze biroꞌi ebu ḡa eḡe teite tiburaroteꞌe teige, zeḡe niduꞌa mae tibuzoꞌi.
\v 12 E zeḡe teite radiuꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano ḡaeꞌa iniroteꞌe niḡa inaraḡa hina ze faine biriro zu taufiro, eꞌanoꞌo zeḡe niduꞌa mene dauḡiro. Rehano tiba daꞌo ruineꞌeteꞌe ibiḡa uꞌa diuḡiro. ꞌOugadu Buka Zaḡoḡano mirihiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaniꞌa hudaro.
\p 
\v 13 Izidi e ḡae vaḡe amiꞌuma. Eꞌe raha ꞌada zeḡe veize ꞌahige kurauꞌohe, mazaḡa e matuꞌe rudauꞌeteꞌe teige, zeḡe zuni matuꞌuꞌa iriꞌavozoga veize raꞌohe.
\v 14 E ḡoereḡo ze ziniro, rehano raha azaḡaniꞌa ze heꞌeheꞌeziro, mazaḡa eꞌe mene raha azaḡa moneo teige, zeꞌe mene raha azaḡa moneo raꞌohe.
\v 15 E ḡaꞌa ze rahaonoꞌo zamaze vaḡizoga veize mene umiꞌeꞌohe, rehano Satani mazaonoꞌo ze biroga veize umiꞌeꞌohe.
\v 16 Eꞌe mene raha azaḡa moneo teige, zeḡe zuni mene raha azaḡa moneo raꞌohe.
\v 17 Ze ḡoere huga hina zaḡozaḡozoꞌi. Ḡae ḡoereꞌe huga.
\v 18 Ḡaeꞌa e raha ꞌada tuḡuhiroteꞌe teige, eḡeꞌa ze raha azaḡa mazao tuḡuziro.
\v 19 Zeḡe veize e eḡeꞌa bare zaḡozaḡoheꞌohe, mazaḡa zeḡe zuni ḡoere huga hina zaḡozaḡozoga veize raꞌohe.”
\s1 Fieꞌeteꞌe Azaḡa veize Kuraro
\p 
\v 20 “E eḡe tahiꞌatahiꞌa veize daꞌo mene kurauꞌohe, rehano ze ḡoere egadu eḡe mazao fiteꞌe azaḡa veize zuni kurauꞌohe.
\v 21 Mama, ḡa eḡe teite tiburaroteꞌe zu e ḡae teite tiburaroteꞌe teige, zeḡe niduꞌa tiburafine kurauꞌohe. Ebu zeḡe zuni emeḡe teite tiburanadu raha azaḡaniꞌa ḡa eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe mae ḡihinoga veize kurauꞌohe.
\v 22 Ḡa eꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune rae ihoziroteꞌe teige, eḡe zuni zeꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune rae ihoziro, mazaḡa emeꞌe tiburaroteꞌe teige, zeḡe zuni tiburafine raꞌohe.
\v 23 E zeḡe teite tiburaro zu ḡa eḡe teite tiburaro. E zeḡe niduꞌa hube hune tiburanoga veize kurauꞌohe. Mazaḡa ḡaeꞌa e tuḡuhiroteꞌe ebu e zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe teige, ḡaeꞌa zeḡe zuni zamare borofeꞌetaꞌaꞌe raha azaḡaniꞌa ederifine raꞌohe.
\v 24 Mama, e ḡaeꞌa iniroteꞌe azaḡaꞌe eḡeꞌa radiuꞌeteꞌe habaꞌano eḡe teite radoga urateꞌohe. Ebu ꞌizema raha zu adure haḡaogano ḡaeꞌa eḡe zamare borofadu ḡa eꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune rae reirotaꞌaꞌe zeḡe zuni ederoga urateꞌohe.
\p 
\v 25 Mama duduḡa hune, raha azaḡaꞌe ḡa aḡuꞌa, rehano e ḡaꞌe edeḡa. Ebu eḡe tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe ḡaeꞌa eḡe tuḡuhirotaꞌaꞌe edeḡa.
\v 26 E zeḡe mazao ḡa ihoziro ebu barebare ihoziꞌuma. Aꞌe ḡaꞌa e zamare borofiroteꞌe teige, zeḡe zuni vaze ꞌahogaꞌahoga zamare borofoga zu e zeḡe teite tiburanoga veize raꞌohe.”
\c 18
\s1 Iesu Obone Tiro
\r (Mataio 26:47-56; Mareko 14:43-50; Luka 22:47-53)
\p 
\v 1 Iesuꞌa kuraroteꞌe enogano, ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa teite Kiderona doꞌoḡa moneafa onamiro. Eꞌea olivi ireḡa mebaḡa ꞌahoga eꞌe, ebu ani ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa teite eꞌe mebaḡa diuḡiro.
\v 2 Iesu revoharoteꞌe vazeḡa, Iuda zuni eꞌe habaꞌa ederiro, mazaḡa Iesuꞌa ḡae ḡehaḡa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa teite deꞌea nuꞌoraro.
\v 3 Eꞌanoꞌo Iudaꞌa Roma uti azaḡa, ebu dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu Farisea azaḡaniꞌa tuḡuziroteꞌe kuru neḡa uti azaḡa teite ariro. Ze ihure nunu zu uti ḡauḡa madu meba eꞌe diuḡiro.
\p 
\v 4 Iesuꞌe ane mazao naginiꞌa fureratiteꞌe ederadu zeḡe vaḡe onamiro ebu ḡadiziro, “Zaꞌe iniu vaḡeꞌohe?”
\v 5 Zeḡeꞌa naenaeniro, “Nazareta vazeḡa Iesu.” Ebu aniꞌa ziro, “Aꞌe eḡe.” Ani revoharoteꞌe vazeḡa, Iudaꞌe zeḡe teite deꞌea edau radiro.
\v 6 Iesuꞌa, “Aꞌe eḡe,” rae zirotene, ze suve ḡouradu rahao higau bauriro.
\v 7 Ebu Iesuꞌa bare ḡadiziro, “Zaꞌe iniu vaḡeꞌohe?” Zeꞌa niro, “Nazareta vazeḡa Iesu.”
\v 8 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “E zeha, aꞌe eḡe. Za e vaḡoꞌidene, eḡe tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe ahete modoꞌi.”
\v 9 Aniꞌa ꞌouge reirotaꞌaꞌe ibite ꞌahige kuraroteꞌeꞌa hudanoga veize reiro, “E ḡaeꞌa iniroteꞌe azaḡa boꞌaḡano tiba zuni mene dauniro.”
\p 
\v 10 Eꞌe madaḡano Simona Peteroꞌe benisiḡeta. Aneꞌa eꞌe ahase bunadu dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa tuḡure vazeḡa udirotene, edaꞌe teḡaḡa variꞌe butiro. Tuḡure vazeḡa niḡaꞌe Malokusi.
\v 11 ꞌOugadu Iesuꞌa Petero niro, “Benisiḡo bare iḡuꞌano ofoꞌi! Eḡe Mamaꞌa iniroteꞌe bioḡa ꞌahi eḡeꞌa gage huniꞌuma.”
\s1 Iesuꞌe Anasi vaḡe Tutune Onamiro
\r (Mataio 26:57-58; Mareko 14:53-54; Luka 22:54)
\p 
\v 12 Roma uti azaḡa zu uti vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa ebu kuru neḡa ḡianeꞌeteꞌe Iuda uti azaḡaniꞌa Iesu obone teadu autiro.
\v 13 Ebu ze ani Anasi vaḡe ibite tutune onamiro. Anasiꞌe Kaiafa emoḡa zu Kaiafaꞌe eꞌe muriḡano dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa.
\v 14 Kaiafaꞌe ibite Iuda azaḡa boroboro mazao ꞌahige iraduguziro, “Vaze niduꞌa veize vaze tibaniꞌa rudauneꞌe ufeta manoḡa.”
\s1 Peteroꞌa Iesu Oꞌoniro
\r (Mataio 26:69-70; Mareko 14:66-68; Luka 22:55-57)
\p 
\v 15 Simona Petero zu Iesu tahiꞌa ꞌahoganiꞌa Iesu hegote onamiro. Tahiꞌa eꞌeꞌa dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa ederadu Iesu teite dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa ne habaꞌa diuḡiro.
\v 16 Rehano Peteroꞌe ibiheta enogano edau radiro. Eꞌanoꞌo dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa edereꞌeteꞌe tahiꞌaḡa eꞌeꞌa buanadu ibiheta taufeꞌeteꞌe roḡaeḡa ḡoreniro, ebu Petero mae zouniro.
\v 17 ꞌOugirotene, ibiheta taufeꞌeteꞌe roḡaeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa Petero niro, “Vaze ꞌomo tahiꞌatahiꞌa boꞌaḡano ḡae zuni tahiꞌa ꞌahogahe?” Aneꞌa naenaeniro, “Eꞌe mene.”
\v 18 Eꞌe madaḡanoꞌe nahune, eꞌanoꞌo tuḡure azaḡa zu kuru neḡa uti azaḡaniꞌa ahirize giginoga radu ire roga hufiro, ebu ire roga gabaḡeḡenadu idiro. Petero zuni ahiꞌa gigineꞌenaꞌa, zeḡe teite edau radiro.
\s1 Anasiꞌa Iesu Ḡadiniro
\r (Mataio 26:59-66; Mareko 14:55-64; Luka 22:66-71)
\p 
\v 19 Eꞌe madaḡano dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaniꞌa Iesu mazao ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa zu ane ihore moneo ḡadiniro.
\v 20 Ebu Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “E hunio vaze niduꞌa mazao ḡoeriro. Iuda azaḡa niduꞌa nuꞌoruꞌeteꞌe kuru neḡa ga nuꞌonuꞌo neḡa zamaḡano iḡaiḡa ihoziro. E ḡoere ꞌahoga mene ꞌuꞌuru reiro.
\v 21 Ḡa nougadu e ḡadiheꞌohe? Eḡe ḡoere igiroteꞌe azaḡa ḡadizoꞌi. Ze eꞌa nagini reirotaꞌaꞌe edeḡa.”
\v 22 Iesuꞌa ꞌouge reirotene, kuru neḡa uti vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa ani uhiḡano edanadu iraḡano faꞌoniro ebu niro, “Ḡa dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa mene gubaneꞌohe!”
\v 23 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “E ḡoere ꞌahoga veꞌore roꞌidene, naginiꞌe veꞌoḡa rae furenoꞌi. Rehano e ḡoere huga roꞌidene, nougadu irahe faꞌoneha?”
\v 24 Ebu Anasiꞌa Iesu ꞌevore ꞌize utoga zamaḡano dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa, Kaiafa vaḡe tuḡuniro.
\s1 Peteroꞌa Iesu Bare Oꞌoniro
\r (Mataio 26:71-75; Mareko 14:69-72; Luka 22:58-62)
\p 
\v 25 Simona Peteroꞌa edanadu ire roga genaḡano ide radiroteꞌea, vaze nuꞌa ḡadiniro, “Ḡaꞌe Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌa boꞌaḡano ꞌahoga, oꞌehe?” Rehano aneꞌa oꞌoniro, “Eꞌe mene.”
\v 26 Dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa tuḡure vazeḡa ꞌahogaꞌe Peteroꞌa teḡaḡa variꞌiroteꞌe vazeḡa nabuga. Aneꞌa niro, “Eḡeꞌa ḡa ani teite olivi ireḡa mebaḡano radiuꞌeteꞌe horoꞌeha.”
\v 27 Peteroꞌa bare oꞌoniro. Aneꞌa ꞌouge reirotene, kokorokuꞌa ugaro.
\s1 Iesu Pilato vaḡe Tutune Onamiro
\r (Mataio 27:1-2, 11-14; Mareko 15:1-5; Luka 23:1-5)
\p 
\v 28 Ebu Iuda azaḡa boroboroꞌa Iesu Kaiafa mazaonoꞌo Roma gavana vazeḡa neḡa tutune onamiro. Aꞌe Oherebau uzeuze reiro. Zeꞌe Roma gavana ne zamaḡa mene diuḡiro. Mazaḡa aniꞌe Badiꞌa aḡuꞌa vazeḡa radu, ane ne diuḡine ze toradanadu Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa anoga mene idaḡa rae zamariro.
\v 29 Eꞌanoꞌo Pilatoꞌa zeḡe vaḡe bua aradu ḡoreziro, “Vaze ꞌadiꞌe nagini haḡadu za aniꞌe veꞌoḡa rae raꞌohe?”
\v 30 Ze naenaeniro, “Vaze ꞌahiꞌe mene vaze sauꞌa reifone, emeꞌa ani ḡae ꞌevoreo mene riꞌinifo.”
\v 31 Pilatoꞌa ziro, “Zaeꞌa ani tutune onamadu zae goro hina kotanoꞌi.” Iuda azaḡa boroboroꞌa naenaeniro, “Eme, Iuda azaḡaꞌe vaze ꞌahoga runeo tuḡunogaꞌe mene idaḡa.”
\v 32 ꞌOugadu Iesuꞌa nougenouge rudatiteꞌe moneo reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaniꞌa hudaro.
\p 
\v 33 Pilatoꞌa ane ne bare diuḡadu Iesu huniro ebu ḡadiniro, “Ḡaꞌe Iuda azaḡa kinihe?”
\v 34 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Ḡadimu ꞌadiꞌe ḡae mazaonoꞌo ga vaze nuꞌa eḡe moneo ḡeiro?”
\v 35 Pilatoꞌa naenaeniro, “Eꞌe mene Iuda vazeḡa. Ḡae haba azaḡa zu dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡaniꞌa eḡe ꞌevoreo riꞌiꞌeha. Ḡa nagini haḡairo?”
\v 36 Iesuꞌa niro, “Eꞌe mene raha ꞌadi zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe kiniḡa. Eꞌe raha ꞌadi zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe kiniḡa reifone, eḡe tuḡure azaḡaniꞌa Iuda azaḡa boroboro utitozenadu zeḡe ꞌevoreo eḡe riꞌihoga gararifo. Eḡeꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe habaꞌaꞌe mene raha ꞌadi, rehano haba ꞌahoga.”
\p 
\v 37 Pilatoꞌa niro, “Tena ḡaꞌe kinihe?” Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Ḡa ḡaeꞌa bare eꞌe kini raꞌohe. Aꞌe hube. E ḡoere huga rae furenoga veize fureraro zu raha ꞌahi ariro. Iniu ḡoere huga hegoteꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe eḡe ḡoere igiꞌohe.”
\v 38 Pilatoꞌa ḡadiniro, “Ḡoere hugaꞌe nagini?”
\s1 Iesu Runeo Tuḡuniro
\r (Mataio 27:15-31; Mareko 15:6-20; Luka 23:13-25)
\p Pilatoꞌa ꞌouge reiroteꞌe enogano, Iuda azaḡa boroboro vaḡe bare buanadu ziro, “E sauꞌa ꞌahoga ani mazaonoꞌo mene horoneha.
\v 39 Rehano Iuda azaḡa haḡai idunaḡano, Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡano e zae veize ḡuꞌa vazeḡa ꞌahoga tuḡune buneꞌohe. Za eꞌa Iuda azaḡa kini tuḡune bunoga urateꞌehe?”
\v 40 Ze bare ḡihau huaro, “Ani mene, rehano Barabasi mae bunoꞌi!” Barabasiꞌe ḡonore vazeḡa.
\c 19
\s1 Iesu Satauro Tuḡuniro
\p 
\v 1 Eꞌanoꞌo Pilatoꞌa Iesu zamahu onamadu uti azaḡaniꞌa masiniro.
\v 2 Ebu uti azaḡaniꞌa ire ezaga meigameiga mae ḡurunadu kini vadiga adiriḡa teige, vadigano redoharo ebu dabua kanaḡa vidoharo.
\v 3 Ebu ze barebare ane vaḡe aradu ḡirihoharo, “Iuda azaḡa kini, nigunihi!” Ebu ze iraḡano faꞌoniro.
\p 
\v 4 Pilatoꞌa bare buanadu Iuda azaḡa boroboro ziro, “Ḡianoꞌi. E Iesu zamahu zae mazao buniꞌuma. ꞌOugine, za eḡeꞌa ane mazaonoꞌo sauꞌani ꞌahoga mene horonataꞌaꞌe ederiꞌuma.”
\v 5 Ebu Iesuꞌa ire ezaga meigameiga vadigano zu dabua kanaḡaḡeta bua ariro. Pilatoꞌa ziro, “Ḡianoꞌi, vaze aꞌe ꞌadi eꞌe!”
\v 6 Dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu kuru neḡa uti azaḡaniꞌa Iesu horonirotene, ze ḡihau huaro, “Ani satauronoꞌi! Satauronoꞌi!” Pilatoꞌa ziro, “Zaeꞌa tutune onamadu satauronoꞌi. Eꞌe ani mazaonoꞌo veꞌoḡani ꞌahoga mene horoneha.”
\v 7 Iuda azaḡa boroboroꞌa naenaeniro, “Emeḡe goro ḡoeꞌa idunaḡano aniꞌe rudaꞌuma, mazaḡa ani aneꞌa bare Badiꞌa Ubuga rae reiro.”
\p 
\v 8 Pilatoꞌa zeḡe ḡoere igirotene, ufeta riharo.
\v 9 Ebu ane ne bare diuḡadu Iesu ḡadiniro, “Ḡaꞌe noumanoꞌo ariro?” Rehano Iesuꞌa mene naenaeniro.
\v 10 Pilatoꞌa niro, “Ḡa mene ḡorehiꞌumahe? Ḡa tuḡuꞌe buḡaditeꞌe ga satauroḡaditeꞌe gigiꞌaḡaꞌe eḡeꞌa meiro. Ḡa mene edereꞌehe?”
\v 11 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Badiꞌaꞌa e sausauheꞌeteꞌe gigiꞌaḡa mene ḡanifone, ḡa e sausauhoga mene idarafo. Eꞌanoꞌo ḡae ꞌevoreo riꞌihateꞌe vazeḡa sauꞌaꞌe ufeta boro, aꞌe ḡae sauꞌa vitinoga.”
\p 
\v 12 Iesu ḡoere uꞌano, Pilatoꞌa ani tuḡune bunihi rae inariro. Rehano Iuda azaḡa boroboroꞌa houhoune niro, “Ḡa vaze ꞌahi tuḡune bunine, ḡaꞌe mene Roma kiniḡa mone vazeḡa. Iniuꞌa ane bare kini rae reine, aniꞌe Roma kiniḡa agirohauꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa.”
\v 13 Pilatoꞌa ḡoere eꞌe igirotene, Iesu zamahu bunadu kota habaꞌano ehoriro. Kota vazeḡa ehoroḡa habaꞌaꞌe Vatava hina Ruruḡiro rae huniroteꞌe habaꞌano tiro. Aꞌe Heberu ḡoeꞌano Gabata rae huniro.
\p 
\v 14 Eꞌe madaḡaꞌe Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa ꞌizema mougano, ruhibeꞌeteꞌe madaḡa zu madai kirikiri. Pilatoꞌa Iuda azaḡa ziro, “Ḡianoꞌi, zae kiniꞌe ꞌadi eꞌe.”
\v 15 Zeḡeꞌa huaro, “Manoꞌi! Manoꞌi! Satauronoꞌi!” Pilatoꞌa ḡadiziro, “E zae kini satauroniꞌumahe?” Dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡaniꞌa naenaeniro, “Emeḡe kini ꞌahogaꞌe oꞌoꞌa, rehano Roma kiniḡa daꞌo.”
\v 16 Eꞌanoꞌo Pilatoꞌa Iesu satauronoga veize zeḡe ꞌevoreo riꞌiniro.
\s1 Iesu Satauroniro
\r (Mataio 27:32-44; Mareko 15:21-32; Luka 23:26-43)
\p Ebu uti azaḡaniꞌa Iesu tutune onamiro.
\v 17 Iesuꞌa ane satauro odoheꞌenaꞌa, Vadini Isiḡa rae huneꞌeteꞌe habaꞌa onamiro. Aꞌe Heberu ḡoeꞌano Gologota rae huniro.
\v 18 Eꞌea ze Iesu satauroniro. Vaze aheu zuni ane edaꞌe moneo ebu kauri moneo satauroziro, u Iesuꞌe nemao satauroniro.
\p 
\v 19 Pilatoꞌa Iesu haḡai sauꞌaꞌe nagini rae ihozifine, ire rafaḡa rana mirihadu satauro rana tiro. Aꞌe ꞌahige rae mirihiro, “NAZARETA VAZEḠA IESU, IUDA AZAḠ KINI.”
\v 20 Mirihirotaꞌaꞌe Iuda azaḡa ḡehaḡaniꞌa meꞌodiro. Mazaḡa Iesu satauroniroteꞌe habaꞌaꞌe Ierusalema uhiḡano, ebu aꞌe Heberu ḡoeꞌano, Roma ḡoeꞌano, zu Giriki ḡoeꞌano mirihiro.
\v 21 Eꞌanoꞌo dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡaniꞌa Pilato niro, “'Iuda Azaḡa Kini,' rae ago mirihoꞌi, rehano 'Eꞌe Iuda Azaḡa Kini,' rae mirihoꞌi.”
\v 22 Pilatoꞌa naenaeziro, “E eḡeꞌa mirihihi rae raꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa miriheha.”
\p 
\v 23 Ebu Iesu satauronirotene, uti azaḡaniꞌa Iesu raga dabuaḡa madu ḡazaḡano rovoniro, ebu zeḡeꞌa tibatiba meiro. Ze zizuni dabuaḡa zuni meiro. Aꞌe hitanaonoꞌo oda ḡuzu dabuaḡa tiba zu mene variꞌe turiniroteꞌe dabuaḡa.
\v 24 Eꞌanoꞌo uti azaḡaniꞌa neneḡaniro, “ꞌAdiꞌe mene zigiꞌuma. Kaḡusi arahoḡa arahadu iniuꞌa meiteꞌe ḡianiꞌuma.” ꞌOugadu Buka Zaḡoḡano mirihiroteꞌeꞌa hudaro,
\q1 “Ze eḡe raga dabuaḡa ḡahugotitiro,
\q2 ebu zizuni dabuaḡaꞌe kaḡusi arahoḡa arahadu meiro.”\x + \xo 19:24 \xt Salamo 22:18\x*
\m Eꞌanoꞌo uti azaḡaniꞌa ꞌouge haḡairo.
\p 
\v 25 Iesu satauro uhiḡano Iesu viꞌa, viꞌa negoḡa, Kolopasi inuga Maria, ebu Magadala roḡaeḡa Mariaꞌa edau radiro.
\v 26 Iesuꞌa viꞌa zu ane zamarone tahiꞌaḡa viꞌa uhiḡano edauꞌeteꞌe horozirotene, viꞌa niro, “Roḡae boro, aniꞌe ḡae ubugo.”
\v 27 Ebu Iesuꞌa tahiꞌa eꞌe niro, “Aniꞌe ḡae viꞌu.” Eꞌe madaḡanonoꞌo tahiꞌa eꞌeꞌa Iesu viꞌa tutune ane ne onamadu taufiro.
\s1 Iesu Rune
\r (Mataio 27:45-56; Mareko 15:33-41; Luka 23:44-49)
\p 
\v 28 Eꞌe enogano, Iesuꞌe ani gauḡa niduꞌa izidi hauḡataꞌaꞌe ederiro. Ebu Buka Zaḡoḡano mirihiroteꞌeꞌa hudanoga veize ꞌahige rae reiro, “E irinehe moꞌoheha.”\x + \xo 19:28 \xt Salamo 69:21\x*
\v 29 Eꞌea vaini vuḡa ḡiḡiꞌa ḡoḡoreḡa ꞌahoga eꞌe. Eꞌanoꞌo ze vu romane zouneꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa madu vaini vuḡa ḡiḡiꞌa iriꞌavoniro, ebu Gubu somoriḡa rana teadu ani mazaneo ite tiro.
\v 30 Iesuꞌa vaini vuḡa ḡiḡiꞌaḡa gagadu ꞌahige rae reiro, “Eḡe gau niduꞌa hauḡeha.” Ebu vadiga ḡuḡuradu iriga riꞌiro.
\p 
\v 31 Eꞌe madaḡaꞌe Bana Madaḡa ruhibeꞌeteꞌe madaḡa, ebu irarirotene Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa zamaḡano Bana Madaḡa boro reiro. Iuda azaḡaniꞌa Bana Madaḡano rune ahiꞌa satauro rana modoga mene uratiro ꞌahine, rune azaḡa odaze vahegadu ahirize satauronoꞌo mae vaḡinoga veize Pilato uminiro.
\v 32 Eꞌanoꞌo uti azaḡaniꞌa onamadu Iesu teite satauroniroteꞌe vazeḡa ibiꞌa odaḡa vahegiro, ebu vaze ꞌahoga odaḡa vahegiro.
\v 33 Rehano ze Iesu vaḡe onamirotene, ani amahi rudanoga horoniro, eꞌanoꞌo odaḡa mene vahegiro.
\v 34 Rehano uti vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa garaḡota hina rebeḡano ḡounadu ru zu vuꞌa zogone sore buaro.
\v 35 (Aꞌe eꞌeguḡa horoniroteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa rae fureniroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa. Aniꞌa rae fureniroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaꞌe huga. Ani aneꞌa ḡoere huga ziꞌetaꞌaꞌe edereꞌohe, ebu zae zuni mae ḡihinifine rae fureneꞌohe.)
\p 
\v 36 ꞌAhiguḡaniꞌa Buka Zaḡoḡano mirihiroteꞌeꞌa hudanoga veize fureraro, “Isiga tiba zuni mene vahegaꞌuma.”\x + \xo 19:36 \xt Vaḡiniro 12:46; Naba 9:12; Salamo 34:20\x*
\v 37 Ebu Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae reiro, “Zeḡeꞌa ḡouniroteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe zeḡeꞌa ḡianiꞌuma.”\x + \xo 19:37 \xt Zekaria 12:10\x*
\s1 Iesu Guriro
\r (Mataio 27:57-61; Mareko 15:42-47; Luka 23:50-56)
\p 
\v 38 Eꞌe enogano Arimate vazeḡa, Iosefaꞌa Pilato vaḡe onamadu Iesu ahiri satauronoꞌo mae bunoga veize uminiro. Aniꞌe Iesu tahiꞌa ꞌahoga, rehano eꞌe moneo vaze ꞌahoga mene ihoniro, mazaḡa aniꞌe Iuda azaḡa boroboro rihoziro. Pilatoꞌa, “Idaḡa,” rae reirotene, ani onamadu Iesu ahiri mae onamiro.
\v 39 Nikodemoꞌe ibite ohere Iesu vaḡe onamiroteꞌe vazeḡa. Ani zuni Iosefa teite onamiro. Aniꞌe murava hohoḡa aloe teite mirunadu odohe ariro. Aꞌe 34 kilo heuḡa.
\v 40 Ebu Iuda azaḡa rune gureꞌeteꞌe ibiḡano, ze Iesu ahiri madu miruniroteꞌe ḡauḡaꞌe dabua manoḡa kuiḡa teite ꞌumiro.
\v 41 Iesu satauroniroteꞌe habaꞌano kaka mebaḡa ꞌahoga eꞌe, ebu eꞌea vatava iduḡa ꞌahoga eꞌe. Aꞌe rune vazeḡani ꞌahoga ꞌizema tiroteꞌe iduḡa iziga.
\v 42 Eꞌe madaḡanoꞌe Iuda azaḡaniꞌa Bana Madaḡa veize ruhibeꞌeteꞌe madaḡa ebu idu aꞌe zeḡe uhiḡano ꞌahine, ze Iesu ahiriꞌe eꞌe zamaḡano tiro. \fig Iesu rune ahiꞌa odohe onamadu iduo tiro|src="DN00494b.tif" size="col" ref="19:38-42"\fig*
\c 20
\s1 Iesuꞌa Bare Ḡabodiro
\r (Mataio 28:1-10; Mareko 16:1-8; Luka 24:1-2)
\p 
\v 1 Fura oherebau uzeuze ꞌize uzaboḡano, Magadala roḡaeḡa Mariaꞌa idu onamiro ebu idu ꞌuiroteꞌe hadiḡa boro kiune vaḡinoga horoniro.
\v 2 Eꞌanoꞌo aneꞌa Simona Petero zu Iesu zamarone tahiꞌaḡa vaḡe dure onamadu ziro, “Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa Zuhiꞌa Boro ahiri iduonoꞌo mae vaḡineha. Ze ani noꞌe habaꞌano teataꞌaꞌe eme aḡuꞌa!”
\v 3 Ebu Petero zu Iesu zamarone tahiꞌaḡaniꞌa iḡunadu idu habaꞌa uꞌa onamiro.
\v 4 Anianine dure onamirotene, tahiꞌa eꞌeꞌa ḡihau duradu Petero vitine iduo ibite feuriro.
\v 5 Ani ḡuḡuradu idu zamaḡa ḡianirotene, Iesu ꞌumiroteꞌe dabuaḡa kuiḡa daꞌo deꞌea radoga horoniro, rehano aniꞌe mene diuḡiro.
\v 6 Simona Petero zuni ani hegote feuri ariro. Ani idu zamaḡa diuḡirotene, Iesu ahiri ꞌumiroteꞌe dabuaḡa kuiḡaꞌe deꞌea radoga horoniro,
\v 7 ebu Iesu vadiga ꞌumiroteꞌe dabuaḡa horoniro. Rehano vadiga dabuaḡaꞌe ḡuadu ahiri ꞌumiroteꞌe dabuaḡa kuiḡanonoꞌo avo tiro.
\v 8 Ebu ibite iduo feuriroteꞌe tahiꞌaḡaniꞌa diuḡiro. Ane zuni horonadu Maria ḡoere mae ḡihiniro.
\v 9 Rehano ze Buka Zaḡoḡano Iesuꞌa rune azaḡa boꞌaḡano bare iḡuniꞌuma rae reiroteꞌe ꞌize mene zamariro.
\v 10 Ebu Iesu tahiꞌa aheuꞌa baradu neze onamiro.
\s1 Iesuꞌa Magadala Roḡaeḡa Maria mazao Fureraro
\r (Mareko 16:9-11)
\p 
\v 11 Rehano Mariaꞌa idu enogano edanadu niau radiro. Aniꞌa niauꞌenaꞌa, idu zamaḡa dire ḡianiro.
\v 12 Ebu dabua ꞌuruḡa vidaroteꞌe tuḡure viga aheu horoziro. Ze Iesu ahiri bazune tiroteꞌe habaꞌano ehore radiunu. Tuḡure viga ꞌahogaꞌe vadiga ḡoha ebu ꞌahogaꞌe odaḡa ḡuzuo radiunu.
\v 13 Ze Maria ḡadiniro, “Roḡae, ḡa nougadu niauꞌohe?” Aniꞌa naenaeziro, “Vazeꞌa eḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro mae vaḡineha. Ze nouma teataꞌaꞌe e aḡuꞌa.”
\p 
\v 14 Ebu Mariaꞌa tehirotene, Iesuꞌa edau radoga horoniro, rehano aꞌe Iesu rae mene ederiro.
\v 15 Iesuꞌa ḡadiniro, “Roḡae, ḡa nougadu niauꞌohe? Ḡa iniu vaḡeꞌohe?” Mariaꞌa aniꞌe kaka mebaḡa ḡianeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa rae zamaradu niro, “Vaze boro, ḡaꞌa ani ahiri mae onameha roꞌidene, nouma teateꞌe ehoꞌi, ꞌougine eḡeꞌa meꞌuma.”
\v 16 Iesuꞌa niro, “Maria.” Mariaꞌa tehadu Heberu ḡoeꞌano niro, “Raboni!” (Eꞌe ḡoeꞌa hugaꞌe Ihore vazeḡa.)
\v 17 Iesuꞌa niro, “Ago obohoꞌi, mazaḡa e ꞌize Mama vaḡe mene iteha. Ḡa eḡe tahiꞌatahiꞌa\f + \fr 20:17 \fqa eḡe nego duḡuru \f* vaḡe onamadu ꞌahige ihozoꞌi, 'Eꞌe Mama vaḡe itiꞌuma. Aniꞌe eḡe Mama zuni zae Moze, eḡe Badiꞌa zuni zae Badiꞌa.'”
\v 18 Eꞌanoꞌo Magadala roḡaeḡa Mariaꞌa Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌa vaḡe onamadu ihoziro, “E Zuhiꞌa Boro horoneha!” Ebu ani Iesuꞌa niroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa ziro.
\s1 Iesuꞌa Ane Tahiꞌatahiꞌa mazao Fureraro
\r (Mataio 28:16-20; Mareko 16:14-18; Luka 24:36-49)
\p 
\v 19 Eꞌe furaḡa ḡoravaḡano Iesu tahiꞌa niduꞌa nuꞌorarotene, ze ne ibihetaḡa niduꞌa hararo, mazaḡa Iuda azaḡa rihoziro. Eꞌe madaḡano Iesuꞌa diuḡi ariro ebu zeḡe boꞌaḡano edanadu ziro, “Zama roḡeḡaꞌe zae teite radoꞌi.”
\v 20 Aneꞌa ḡoere eꞌe ziroteꞌe enogano ꞌevoꞌa zu rebeḡa ihoziro. Ebu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa Zuhiꞌa Boro horonadu ze matuꞌe rudaro.
\p 
\v 21 Ebu Iesuꞌa bare ziro, “Zama roḡeḡa zae teite radiuꞌenoꞌi. Mamaꞌa eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe teige, e za tuḡuzeꞌohe.”
\v 22 Ebu Iesuꞌa zeḡe rana irine hodadu ziro, “Vine Zaḡoḡa moꞌi.
\v 23 Zaꞌa vaze ꞌahoga haḡai sauꞌa rae modine, Badiꞌaꞌa ane haḡai sauꞌa rae modiꞌuma. U zaꞌa vaze ꞌahoga haḡai sauꞌa mene rae modine, Badiꞌaꞌa ane haḡai sauꞌa mene rae modiꞌuma.”
\s1 Tomasi mazao Fureraro
\p 
\v 24 Iesu tahiꞌa gaubanana aheu fare boꞌaḡano tahiꞌa ꞌahogaꞌe Tomasi, niḡa ꞌahogaꞌe Atoꞌa.\f + \fr 20:24 \fqa Didumo \f* Aniꞌe Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa vaḡe arirotene, zeḡe teite mene radiro.
\v 25 Eꞌanoꞌo Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa niro, “Eme Zuhiꞌa Boro horoneha.” Rehano aniꞌa naenaeziro, “E ani ꞌevore ikoko iḡuꞌa horonine, ebu eḡe ꞌevore huduꞌa ane ꞌevore ikoko iḡuꞌano surubine, zu eḡe ꞌevore ane rebe iḡuꞌano surubine, zae ḡoere mae ḡihiniꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 26 Fura tiba enogano Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa ne zamaḡano bare radiro, ebu Tomasi zuni zeḡe teite radiro. Zeḡe ne ibihetaꞌe haranoga, rehano Iesuꞌa diuḡadu zeḡe boꞌaḡano edaro ebu ziro, “Zama roḡeḡa zae teite radoꞌi.”
\v 27 Ebu aniꞌa Tomasi niro, “ꞌEvoꞌo huduꞌa ꞌaha teadu ꞌevorehe ḡianoꞌi, ebu ꞌevoꞌo ꞌeinadu rebeheo suruboꞌi. Zamaḡo ago ꞌadaꞌadoꞌi, rehano fioꞌi.”
\v 28 Tomasiꞌa naenaeniro, “Eḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro, eḡe Badiꞌa!”
\v 29 Iesuꞌa niro, “Ḡa eḡe horoheha ꞌahine, eḡe mazao fieꞌehe? E mene horohadu eḡe mazao fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe matuꞌeꞌohe.”
\s1 Ioaneꞌa Nagini veize Buka ꞌAhi Mirihiroteꞌe moneo Ḡoeriro
\p 
\v 30 Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa zamao haḡai nu badeḡa nunu haḡairo. Eꞌe niduꞌa buka ꞌahi zamaḡano mene mirihiro.
\v 31 Rehano e ꞌahige mirihirotaꞌaꞌe zaeꞌa Iesuꞌe Keriso, Badiꞌa Ubuga rae mae ḡihinifine, ebu ani mazao fiadu ani niḡano ḡabone hidifine raꞌohe.
\c 21
\s1 Iesuꞌa Ane Tahiꞌa Fuꞌo Aheu Fare mazao Fureraro
\p 
\v 1 Eꞌe enogano Iesuꞌa Tiberia\f + \fr 21:1 \ft Galilea\f* duꞌuraḡano ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa mazao bare fureraro. Eꞌe hariḡaꞌe ꞌahiguḡa.
\v 2 Simona Petero, Atoa\f + \fr 21:2 \fqa Didumo \f* rae huneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa Tomasi, Galilea habaꞌano Kana neḡa vazeḡa Natanaela, Zebedeo ubuga aheu, ebu Iesu tahiꞌa aheuꞌa deꞌea nuꞌoranadu radiro.
\v 3 Simona Peteroꞌa ziro, “E reꞌevi onameꞌohe.” Zeḡeꞌa niro, “Emeḡe zuni ḡae teite onamiꞌuma.” Eꞌanoꞌo ze onamadu ḡasio tiriro. Rehano eꞌe oheꞌano ḡozoneni ꞌahoga mene maro.
\p 
\v 4 Irarirotene, oherebau uzeuze Iesuꞌa hesao edaro, rehano ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe aꞌe Iesu rae mene ederiro.
\v 5 Ebu aniꞌa ḡadiziro, “Eḡe vaze, za ḡozoneni ꞌahoga mene manahe?” Zeꞌa naenaeniro, “Mene maneha.”
\v 6 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Ḡasize edaꞌe naeo reꞌevaze ꞌeinoꞌi, ꞌougine za ḡozone nu maꞌuma.” Ze reꞌeva ꞌeinirotene, reꞌevaze bare hegogaꞌe mene idararo, mazaḡa reꞌevaꞌe ḡozoneꞌa ufeta iriꞌaviro.
\v 7 Ebu Iesu zamarone tahiꞌaḡaniꞌa Petero niro, “Aꞌe Zuhiꞌa Boro!” Peteroꞌa dabuaḡa fuhiꞌadu reꞌevinu. Aniꞌa, “Aꞌe Zuhiꞌa Boro,” rae igirotene, raga dabuaḡa bare vidanadu vuo rafate buaro ebu hesa mone ḡemabe onamiro.
\v 8 U tahiꞌa ꞌahogaꞌahogaꞌe ḡozoneꞌa iriꞌaviroteꞌe reꞌevaḡa obone teadu ahaseꞌenaꞌa, ḡasio hesa mone onamiro. Mazaḡa zeꞌe gabaonoꞌo mene faḡa, 90 mita daꞌo.
\p 
\v 9 Ze hesao buarotene, ḡeꞌare rana ḡozone rafohoga zu ꞌuvahu odoga horoniro.
\v 10 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Za iziduꞌu manateꞌe ḡozoneḡa nu mae aroꞌi.”
\v 11 Eꞌanoꞌo Simona Peteroꞌa ḡasio tiradu ḡozone boroboroꞌa iriꞌaviroteꞌe reꞌevaḡa ahasiro ebu gabao tiro. Ḡozone niduꞌaꞌe 153. Ḡozoneꞌe ḡehaḡa bagaḡa rehano, reꞌevaꞌe mene zigaro.
\v 12 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Aradu oherebau ogomuḡa anoꞌi.” Rehano zeḡe boꞌaḡano ꞌahoga zuni ani mazao, “Ḡa iniu?” rae mene ḡadine nuriro, mazaḡa ze aniꞌe Zuhiꞌa Boro rae ederiro.
\v 13 Iesuꞌa onamadu ꞌuvahu odoga meiro ebu ze ziniro. Ḡozone zu madu ziniro.
\v 14 ꞌAdiꞌe Iesuꞌa rune azaḡa boꞌaḡano bare ḡabodiroteꞌe enogano ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa mazao ḡae uḡiduḡa fureraroteꞌe madaḡa reiro. \fig Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa teite ogaro|src="44_John21:9-13_JesusCookingMeal.jpg" size="col" ref="21:9-13"\fig*
\s1 Iesuꞌa Petero Ḡae Uḡidu Ḡadiniro
\p 
\v 15 Ze ogau hauḡirotene, Iesuꞌa Simona Petero ḡadiniro, “Ioane ubuga Simona, ḡa e zamare borofeꞌehe? ꞌAhi duḡuruꞌa e zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe vitizogahe?” Peteroꞌa niro, “Oꞌe, Zuhiꞌa Boro, ḡa eḡeꞌa ḡa zamare borofeꞌetaꞌaꞌe edeḡa.” Iesuꞌa niro, “Eḡe mamoe ubugaubuga ḡubuzoꞌi.”
\v 16 Iesuꞌa ḡae aheuḡa niro, “Ioane ubuga Simona, ḡa e zamare borofeꞌehe?” Peteroꞌa niro, “Oꞌe, Zuhiꞌa Boro, ḡa eꞌa ḡa zamare borofeꞌetaꞌaꞌe edeḡa.” Iesuꞌa niro, “Eḡe mamoe taufoꞌi.”
\v 17 Iesuꞌa ḡae uḡiduḡa niro, “Ioane ubuga Simona, ḡa e zamare borofeꞌehe?” Iesuꞌa ḡae uḡiduḡa, “Ḡa e zamare borofeꞌehe?” rae ḡadiniro ꞌahine, Peteroꞌe zamaḡaniꞌa adudanadu niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, ḡa ḡau niduꞌa edeḡa. Eḡeꞌa ḡa zamare borofeꞌetaꞌaꞌe ḡa edeḡa.” Iesuꞌa niro, “Eḡe mamoe ḡubuzoꞌi.
\v 18 E hube hune ḡaꞌohe. Ḡaꞌe tahiꞌa iziga madaḡanoꞌe ḡa ḡaeꞌa bare dabuaḡo vidanadu ḡaeꞌa uratiroteꞌe habaꞌa onamido. Rehano ḡa vourine, vazeꞌa ꞌevoꞌo ꞌeinadu dabua vidoḡaniꞌuma ebu ḡaeꞌa mene urateꞌeteꞌe habaꞌa tutuꞌe onamiꞌuma.”
\v 19 Iesuꞌe ꞌahi ḡoeꞌa hina Peteroꞌa nougenouge rudanadu Badiꞌa ni mae ḡihiniteꞌe moneo dehene ihoziro. Ebu Iesuꞌa Petero niro, “Eḡe hegotoꞌi.”
\p 
\v 20 Ebu Peteroꞌa tehadu Iesu zamarone tahiꞌaḡaniꞌa anianine hegoteꞌeteꞌe horoniro. Aniꞌe ibite ḡorava ogomu anogano Iesu mazao aroranadu, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, iniuꞌa revoḡaniꞌuma?” rae ḡadiniroteꞌe vazeḡa.
\v 21 Peteroꞌa ani horonirotene, Iesu ḡadiniro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, tahiꞌa ꞌadiꞌe nougiꞌuma?”
\v 22 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Aniꞌe izidionoꞌo onamo eḡeꞌa bare ariteꞌe madaḡano ḡabode radoga e uratoꞌidene zuni, ḡa ani moneo ago zamaroꞌi. Ḡaꞌe eḡe hegotoꞌi!”
\v 23 Eꞌanoꞌo Iesu ḡoere ꞌadiꞌe Iesu hegoteꞌeteꞌe azaḡa boꞌaḡano bororanadu ze tahiꞌa aꞌe mene rudaꞌuma rae reiro. Rehano Iesuꞌa aniꞌe mene rudaꞌuma rae mene niro, rehano ꞌahige daꞌo reiro, “Aniꞌe izidionoꞌo onamo eḡeꞌa bare ariteꞌe madaḡano ḡabode radoga e uratoꞌidene zuni, ḡa ani moneoꞌe ago zamaroꞌi.”
\s1 Ḡoere Ḡonaga
\p 
\v 24 Eꞌe ꞌahiguḡa horonadu rae fureneꞌeteꞌe ebu mirihiroteꞌe tahiꞌaḡa. Emeḡe niduꞌa edeḡa, eḡeꞌa rae fureneꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌaꞌe huga.
\v 25 Iesuꞌa haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡa nunuꞌe ḡehaḡa. Eḡe zamarone, Iesu haḡaiḡa niduꞌa hune mirihine, buka aꞌe ufeta ḡehaḡa reꞌuma, ebu raha ꞌada buka eꞌe niduꞌa titeꞌe habaꞌaꞌe oꞌoꞌa reꞌuma. 
